INSERT INTO `juego` VALUES (18,582,'Tarisland','A cross-platform MMORPG developed by Level Infinite and Published by Tencent.','Tarisland is a free-to-play cross-platform MMORPG developed by Level Infinite and Published by Tencent. \r\n\r\nAvailable on PC and mobile devices, the game allows players to easily move between both, taking the game with them when they can’t be at their desk. The game is designed to appeal to players of MMOs like World of Warcraft, offering players nine playable classes and 18 specializations.\r\n\r\nEach class features an extensive talent tree system and can be customized. Players of existing MMOs will be familiar with the standard tank, DPS, and healer lineup, necessary for the game’s classic raid and dungeon system. Explore a vast game world and solve mysteries. Pick up various trades such as gathering, mining, and crafting, and sell your items on the auction house.','MMORPG','Windows','Tencent','Level Infinite','2024-06-22','Windows 10 64-bit','Intel Core i5-4590 or AMD FX-8350','8 GB','Nvidia GeForce GTX 960 or AMD Radeon R9 280','20 GB'),(19,540,'Overwatch 2','A hero-focused first-person team shooter from Blizzard Entertainment.','The tale of the hero organization Overwatch continues in Overwatch 2. This new take on the popular team shooter changes up things a little with five-man teams, redefined classes, and new playable characters. With the adjustment to 5v5, players now have more individual impact than in the previous game.\r\n\r\nChallenge yourself in all-new modes. Take control of a robot with your team in Push and take it to the enemy base before the enemy can take it from you. Explore all new areas, including iconic real-world cities such as New York, Rome, Monte Carlo, Toronto, and more.\r\n\r\nOverwatch 2 features an update schedule that drops new content every nine weeks. It also boasts a regular battle pass – both free and premium. This is where some of the game’s characters will be obtained.','Shooter','Windows','Activision Blizzard','Blizzard Entertainment','2022-10-04','Windows 10 64-bit ','Intel Core i3 or AMD Phenom X3 8650','6 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 600 series, AMD Radeon HD 7000 series','50 GB'),(20,516,'PUBG: BATTLEGROUNDS','Get into the action in one of the longest running battle royale games PUBG Battlegrounds.','Get into the action in one of the longest running battle royale games PUBG Battlegrounds. Originally titled PlayerUnknown’s Battlegrounds, the game has been offering players the full battle royale experience in a more realistic setting since 2017. Test yourself against 99 other players on seven different maps using whatever weapons you can find. Just be sure to be the last one standing, because that’s the only way to win.\r\n\r\nGo it alone or play with friends in groups of two or four. Start out with only the clothes on your back, loot buildings, towns, and other locations to obtain the equipment you need. This includes weapons, armor, vehicles, and more. If you want the really good gear – and it’s likely you do – you’ll have to take some risks and head to the more dangerous zones on the map.\r\n\r\nAs is generally the case with the battle royale formula, PUBG’s map shrinks over time, herding all players into a random location where they will eventually have no choice but to engage each other or risk taking damage outside the restricted area. At the same time, random areas of the map will be bombed. So, players must be aware of both events and do their best to avoid them.\r\n\r\nPUBG Battlegrounds is free-to-play and offers players purchasable items in the form of cosmetics. These do not impact game play.\r\n','Shooter','Windows','KRAFTON, Inc.','KRAFTON, Inc.','2022-01-12','64-bit Windows 7, Windows 8.1, Windows 10','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','8 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','40 GB available space'),(21,508,'Enlisted','Get ready to command your own World War II military squad in Gaijin and Darkflow Software’s MMO squad-based shooter Enlisted. ','Get ready to command your own World War II military squad in Gaijin and Darkflow Software’s squad-based shooter Enlisted. Play as an infantry squad leader, tank crew, or even an aircraft pilot in a game where everything from the uniforms and weapons to the vehicles are designed with historical accuracy in mind.\r\n\r\nIn Enlisted, players can train an equip their squad with weapons and other useful items before taking them into battle. Players control one soldier in their squad at a time, and have the ability to switch when a part of the squad has been defeated. When one solider is under player control, the rest are controlled by AI that obeys player orders.\r\n\r\nPlayers have access to four different campaigns, each associated with a specific real-world battle. In each instance the squads, weaponry, vehicles and more will appropriately correspond to each location and date. The game offers hundreds of realistic weapons as well as vehicles that World War II buffs will be familiar with. \r\n\r\nAs for the squads, players have access to 12 different kinds of specialists. In addition to the soldiers that spawn naturally, players can recruit additional ones.','Shooter','Windows','Gaijin Entertainment','Darkflow Software','2021-04-08','Windows 7 / 8 / 10 64bit','Intel Core i3 or better','8 GB','Nvidia GeForce 660, AMD Radeon series 78XX or better','12GB'),(22,345,'Forge of Empires','A free to play 2D browser-based online strategy game, become the leader and raise your city.','Forge of Empires is a free to play 2D browser-based online strategy game that gives players the chance to make their unique city-state into an imperial powerhouse. Everyone has dreamt of building their own empire at some point or another, and Forge of Empires can bring that dream to life.\r\n\r\nPlayers will watch as their civilizations in Forge of Empires begin in the Stone Age and advance all the way into the Industrial Age. The campaign mode is single player and brings players a unique in-depth experience that allows them to use military action, skilled diplomacy, and cunning strategy to achieve their goals.\r\n\r\nMoreover, players in Forge of Empires choose where everything goes, setting up their civilization according to their whims and desires. Any buildings they want and where they want them are ultimately up to them.\r\n\r\nThe greatest feature of Forge of Empires is its wide availability. Players can access Forge of Empires from their Browsers, Apple iOS, Android App, and even on Facebook. It’s only fitting that a game that can create an empire reaches across a multitude of platforms.','Strategy','Web Browser','InnoGames','InnoGames','2012-04-17',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(23,590,'Throne And Liberty','A free-to-play multi-platorm MMORPG from NCSoft and Amazon Games.','Throne and Liberty is a free-to-play multi-platform MMORPG from NCSoft and Amazon Games. The open-world game features large-scale PvPvE in which players can explore everything from sprawling plains to mountain peaks.\r\n\r\nTo survive, players will need to be able to adapt and make decisions based on weather, time of day, and – of course – what other players are doing. The ultimate goal is to claim the throne by defeating Kazar. To do this, players will need to make use of the ability to transform and take the battle to not just the land, but also the sea and air.\r\n\r\nThe game features cross-play bringing together players on PC, Xbox Series X}S, and PlayStation 5. Players on the PS5 can choose to disable cross-play. It’s also worth noting that cross-progression is not supported.','MMORPG','Windows','Amazon Games','NCSoft','2024-10-01','Windows 10（64-bit)','Intel Core i5-6500','8 GB RAM','NVIDIA Geforce GTX960','63 GB available space'),(24,475,'Genshin Impact','If you’ve been looking for a game to scratch that open-world action RPG itch, one with perhaps a bit of Asian flair, then you’re going to want to check out miHoYo’s Genshin Impact.','If you’ve been looking for a game to scratch that open-world ARPG itch, one with perhaps a bit of Asian flair, then you’re going to want to check out miHoYo’s Genshin Impact. The developer, known previously for Honkai Impact 3rd, take players to the world of Teyvat, a vast open-world designed for extended exploration. Players not only explore dungeons, but climb mountains, trees, and buildings to discover all kinds of secrets. \r\n\r\nOf course, the main character doesn’t travel alone. Instead, players build a four-player group out of over 20 characters that can be swapped out to create the best group for any particular mission. The characters, each with different skills filling out the classic RPG types as well as distinct elemental focuses, can be obtained via gameplay or the game’s gacha mechanics – as is gear. Both characters and gear are upgraded in the game via the in depth crafting system.\r\n\r\nIn addition, the game offers players an adventurer system that provides them with even more to do, be it daily quests, small favors for the locals, or big continent-traveling quests. The adventurer system also rewards players for their activities with a wide variety of items.\r\n\r\nGenshin Impact is available to players on PC, PlayStation 4, and mobile devices. It also features a multiplayer mode allowing up to four players to play together and cross-play across all four platforms, however, PlayStation 4 does not allow for cross-progression.','Action RPG','Windows','miHoYo','miHoYo','2020-09-28','Windows 7 SP1 64-bit','Intel Core i7 or equivalent','16 GB','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1060 6GB or better','30 GB'),(25,523,'Fall Guys','Play the most competitive massively multiplayer party royale game featuring beans ever for free on a variety of platforms. ','Play the most competitive massively multiplayer party royale game featuring beans ever for free on a variety of platforms. Mediatonic’s obstacle course-style game Fall Guys offers players all the excitement of being in a Japanese-style game show – only as a bean and with less chance of severe injury.\r\n\r\nMake your way through the obstacle course as quickly as possible while avoiding all the dangers, and everyone else who’d like to take you out and take your spot at the top. Make the run by yourself or work together in teams… until you don’t need your friends any more, that is. Run across spinning tubes with holes in them. Dodge big blades and big balls. Break your way through doors.\r\n And do it all in style, with your choice of bean-shaped costumes.\r\n\r\nPlayers can join their friends across several platforms including PlayStation, Xbox, Nintendo Switch, and PC (via the Epic Games Store).\r\n','Battle Royale','Windows','Mediatonic','Mediatonic','2020-08-04','Windows 10 64bit','Intel Core i5 or AMD equivalent','8 GB RAM','NVIDIA GTX 660 or AMD Radeon HD 7950','2 GB available space'),(26,340,'Game Of Thrones Winter Is Coming','A free-to-play browser-based RTS based on the George R.R. Martin novels and popular HBO series.','Game of Thrones Winter is Coming is a free-to-play browser-based RTS based on the George R.R. Martin novels and popular HBO series. In the game developed by YOOZOOGames, player take on the role of a Westeros lord set on putting a stop to the wars between the Seven Kingdoms.\r\n\r\nThe game is built in Unity and offers players a balanced mix of strategy and RP. Players build bases, grow their kingdom, train armies, and recruit characters from the show, all while living within the story set forth in the TV series.','Strategy','Web Browser','GTArcade','YOOZOO Games ','2019-11-14',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(27,380,'Dark Orbit Reloaded','A browser-based 3D space-combat MMO with a massive playerbase!','Dark Orbit Reloaded is a browser based 3d space-combat MMO with a massive playerbase and endless customization. originally launched in 2006, Dark Orbit was recently revamped with 3d graphics, new interface and new maps.\r\n\r\nBigpoint games give players the freedom to explore the vast cosmos and engage in fierce PvP combat across the stars. Players in DarkOrbit will start by choosing a company to work for – the Earth Industries Corporation, the Mars Mining Operations, or the Venus Resources Unlimited – and carry out their work throughout the galaxy. Each corporation has their own unique view, base of operations, and the players within each are as varied as the stars.\r\n\r\nIn DarkOrbit, players from rival factions won’t be your only threat. Aliens prowl among the planets and you must fight them in order to thrive and survive for your sake and the company whose banner you operate under.\r\n\r\nThough DarkOrbit only features ten different models of spaceship, the options to customize them are only as limited as you want them to be. Fight to obtain wealth and upgrade your vessel in order to decimate other players in pitched PvP game modes.\r\n\r\nChoose your faction and ready your spaceship’s thrusters and weapons in DarkOrbit. The galaxy is waiting for you to conquer it, but only the most cunning and well-equipped will succeed.','Shooter','Web Browser','Bigpoint','Bigpoint','2006-12-11',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(28,517,'Lost Ark','Smilegate’s free-to-play multiplayer ARPG is a massive adventure filled with lands waiting to be explored, people waiting to be met, and an ancient evil waiting to be destroyed.','Smilegate’s free-to-play multiplayer ARPG is a massive adventure filled with lands waiting to be explored, people waiting to be met, and an ancient evil waiting to be destroyed. In Lost Ark, players enter the world of Arkesia and embark on a journey across several lands in a quest to locate the Ark of Legends. Stop the demon Kazeros and his army before they seize control. And hurry, the demons are searching for the Ark too.\r\n\r\nChoose to play as one of several classes ranging from the sword-wielding warrior to a mage or even the gunner – each with several advanced class options. Play alone or with friends (or acquaintances) to explore seven vast continents filled with strange cultures and creatures. Fight in PvP, explore dungeons, and work together in raids. Decide what you like to do best and go for it – but don’t forget to save the world.\r\n\r\nLost Ark offers an easy-to-learn system with plenty of room to customize. Use the game’s ‘Tripod’ system to unlock up to three tiers of customization for each ability and create the combat style that works best for you.\r\n\r\nAs for other features, Lost Ark offers crafting, guilds, and other systems players expect from online games. Whatever you want to do, it’s up to you.\r\n','ARPG','Windows','Amazon Games','Smilegate RPG','2022-02-11','Windows 10 (64-bit only)','Intel i3 or AMD Ryzen 3','8 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 460 / AMD HD6850','50 GB available space'),(29,573,'Titan Revenge','A 3D Norse-themed browser MMORPG developed and published by Game Hollywood Games','Titan Revenge is a Norse-themed browser MMORPG developed and published by Game Hollywood Games. Set in a world facing an apocalypse, the game casts players as the hero, taking on mythical beasts and gods. \r\n\r\nPlayers choose from three classes, Knight, Mage, or Archer. The game uses an “Ethereal System” that grants players more skills in addition to their class skills as they turn into an Angel or a Titan. This transformation even increases their damage and HP and is used during battle. The game features a mix of social systems: Destiny, Friends, and Alliance. It also includes a marriage system.\r\n\r\nAs far as battle content goes, players can fight in cross-server Arena as well as the Imperial War and Archangel War. Also included are a variety of battle modes ranging from 1v1 to Cross-server Faction battles.','MMORPG','Web Browser','Game Hollywood Games','Game Hollywood Games','2023-12-20',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(30,521,'Diablo Immortal','Built for mobile and also released on PC, Diablo Immortal fills in the gaps between Diablo II and III in an MMOARPG environment.','The demon fighting doesn’t have to stop when you walk away from the computer thanks to Blizzard Entertainment’s Diablo Immortal. Built for mobile and also released on PC, the game fills in the gaps between Diablo II and III in an MMOARPG environment.\r\n\r\nDiablo Immortal picks up following the presumed death of the Archangel Tyrael, during which time mankind must deal with the fallout. One of the many problems are the fragments of the shattered Worldstone spread across the land, waiting for Diablo’s underlings to collect them in an attempt to bring about his return.\r\n\r\nPlayers can choose from one of six classes in Diablo Immortal. These are the classic Barbarian, the Crusader, the Demon Hunter, the Monk, the Necromancer, and the Wizard. All six classes features their own unique skills and abilities.\r\n\r\nThe game also introduces six new bosses, ranging from The Skeleton King to the Glacial Colossus. Each offers players a unique challenge, and all are found in places filled with danger. So, players will want to be well prepared before taking them on.\r\n','MMOARPG','Windows','Blizzard Entertainment','Blizzard Entertainment','2022-06-02','Windows 7 / Windows 8 / Windows 10 / Windows 11 (64-bit)','Intel Core i3 or AMD FX-8100','4 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 460, ATI Radeon HD 6850 or Intel HD Graphics 530','?'),(31,522,'Flyff Universe','Get the full Flyff experience on any platform with the free-to-play browser-based MMORPG Flyff Universe.','Players can now get the full Flyff experience on any platform with the browser-based Flyff Universe. The cross-platform game from Gala Lab allows players to access the world of Madrigal from anywhere, whether it be PC, phone, or tablet. As long as it has a browser, players are good to go.\r\n\r\nFlyff Universe is an enhanced version of the original free-to-play MMORPG, featuring a new graphics engine with antialiasing, post-processing, advanced shaders, and more. The game also offers new quality of life changes with the developers monitoring things to make sure everything is operating as it should. But it hasn’t all changed, a lot of old school elements still exist in Flyff Universe, including PK, catchers, and gold icons.\r\n\r\nThe game offers players plenty of places to explore. Among these are the peaceful village of Flaris, the despair filled Mars Dungeon, Saint Morning – the home of Sain City, and the Iblis Temple. \r\n','MMORPG','Web Browser','Gala Lab','Gala Lab','2022-06-14',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(32,511,'Phantasy Star Online 2 New Genesis','The legacy of Phantasy Star Online 2 continues a thousand years later!','The legacy of Phantasy Star Online 2 continues a thousand years later, as the next generation of ARKS operatives join forces with a race known as the Meteorn on the planet Halpha to defend against a new threat, The Dolls. Phantasy Star Online 2: New Genesis is an open world online RPG featuring a day-night cycles, weather effects, and a revamped battle system. It also introduces ways to travel no in the previous game, including gliding. All of this is built on a new graphics engine. \r\n\r\nDespite its differences from PSO2, the games are still connected, with players being able to move back and forth via the client. Players of the original can even bring characters already created in the original game, as well as certain items into New Genesis. For those who played the original game, New Genesis will be familiar in a lot of ways. The games have similar interfaces, quest types and other features. They both also share the same class types, and as with the original game, players will use Mags in combat. \r\n\r\nPlayers just entering the Phantasy Star Online 2 universe through New Genesis will also be able to take advantage of its relationship with the original game. The games share the same client and players can move between them and even collect gear from the original game to use in NGS.\r\n','MMORPG','Windows','Sega','Sega','2021-06-09','Windows 8.1','Intel Core i5-9400 ','8 GB','GeForce GTX 950 or Radeon R9 285','100 GB'),(33,455,'Eternal Fury','A free-to-play ARPG from R2 Games!','Eternal Fury is a free-to-play ARPG from R2 Games. The game is an HTML 5 port of a mobile game developed by Game Hollywood. In it, take part in a classic struggle of good vs evil, interacting with characters based on Norse mythology.\r\n\r\nOne of the features of Eternal Fury is that players are given an opportunity to build their own kingdom, using it as a base of operations. Of course, they also need to defend it. They\'ll be competing with other players for land and resources, and also fighting against them in everything from castle raids to arena PvP.\r\n\r\nAs should be expected in this type of game, there is a guild system that allows players to band together, taking on different tasks together and sharing the rewards.','MMORPG','Web Browser','R2 Games','R2 Games','2019-05-21',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(34,5,'Crossout','A post-apocalyptic MMO vehicle combat game! ','Crossout is a free to play post-apocalyptic MMO vehicle combat game! Gaijin Entertainment is taking the vehicular multiplayer shooter genre full gear with Crossout.\r\n\r\nFollowing the double catastrophes of a failed genetic testing project and an alien invasion, players are thrown into a wasteland world not unlike that of Mad Max. The harsh, post-apocalyptic terrain of Crossout forces players to build and customize their vehicles to fight and endure the elements and other players. Hunker down in the in-game Workshop and use the countless parts earned in battle to craft a formidable death machine capable of laying waste to opponents.\r\n\r\nWeapons in Crossout range from roof-mounted miniguns to vehicular chainsaws and everything in between the player can imagine. But combat isn’t all there is to Crossout. The in-game economy is driven by the players, allowing them to trade the parts they’ve earned with one another to craft stronger, pitiless, machines. Vehicles in Crossout must be strong, for the damage a vehicle takes in battle will affect its performance. And when the enemy is charging with a vehicle-mounted powerdrill, peak performance is everything.  Crossout is everything players looking for the post-apocalyptic vehicular warfare experience could possibly want. Find a vehicle and turn it into a death-spitting chariot of war!','Shooter','Windows','Targem','Gaijin','2017-05-30',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(35,560,'Palia','A cozy MMO with homebuilding and some adventure.','Enter the world of Palia, a cozy MMO from Singularity Six. Explore the world, uncover mysteries, and build your new home. Palia is filled with everything from fields and forests to beaches and mountains, and players can explore it all. Gather the necessary materials, set up your garden, craft the things you need, and build your home making it bigger as you progress.\r\n\r\nExplore Palia not just for materials needed to craft and build, but also to solve the mysteries of the world, including what happened to the humans that lived there 1,000 years ago. Befriend the villagers, build relationships, and maybe even find a partner.\r\n\r\nPalia is different from most MMOs in that it’s not combat-centric. The only weapons players have are those they will use for hunting. If you’re looking for something low-stress with adventure thrown in. This is it.','MMORPG','Windows','Singularity Six','Singularity Six','2023-08-10','Windows 10 64-bit or higher','Intel Core i5-4670K / AMD FX-8350 CPU or equivalent','4GB','GeForce GTX 660 / Radeon R9 270 or equivalent','16GB'),(36,458,'League of Angels - Heaven\'s Fury','A free-to-play, browser-based fantasy online action RPG based loosely on Western mythology!','League of Angels - Heaven’s Fury is a free-to-play, browser-based fantasy online action RPG based loosely on Western mythology. Players in the roles of mages, archers, or dragoons gather “Angels” based on both angels of the Christian faith and gods of pagan pantheons together and return the heavens to their former glory. This is the latest game in a long franchise and features many of the things players have come to expect based on previous titles.\r\n\r\nThe game’s story begins at the beginning of the universe, when everything is born from Chaos. The Chaos gave birth to the mother of the Earth as well as the gods of Hell, darkness, night, and love. However, what once was came to an end when the king of the gods, Zeus, sought to prevent the prophesied  fall of the gods by opening Pandora’s Box. Upon doing so, he unwittingly corrupted himself and became a slave to demons, causing the world to fall into disarray. Humans and gods all suffered.\r\n\r\nThe only solution now is for someone pure to bring the holy angels together and save the world.\r\n','MMORPG','Web Browser','Gtarcade','Yoozoo Games','2020-01-09',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(37,595,'Brighter Shores','A point-and-click MMORPG from RuneScape\'s creator, Andrew Gower.','A point-and-click style MMORPG from Andrew Gower, the creator of RuneScape. Brighter Shores offers players hundreds of hours of gameplay in a fantasy universe. \r\n\r\nPlayers begin their story as a new recruits in the Hopeport town guard where they find themselves forced to deal with problems caused by a harbor storm and local goblins. Discovering magic sources, players will become one of three classes: Cryoknight, Guardian, or Hammermage. They’ll need these powers to stop the corrupting forces in the Hopeforest.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the three classes, Brighter Shores has a long list of professions players can take on. These include fisher, chef, miner, merchant, blacksmith, and more. The game features plenty of story content and places to explore. That said, only Hopeport and Hopeforest are available for free. Players will need to purchase the Premium pass to access additional places. The pass also offers players a unique character name, exclusive offer dyes, and player-to-player trading.','MMORPG','Windows','Fen Research LTD','Fen Research LTD','2024-11-06','Windows 10/11',' Intel i3 or AMD equivalent','8 GB RAM','DirectX 11 capable graphics with at least 2GB RAM','2 GB available space'),(38,529,'Tower of Fantasy','Tower of Fantasy is a 3D open-world RPG, anime-style sci-fi MMO RPG game with unique characters and beautiful open vistas!','Tower of Fantasy is a 3D open-world RPG, anime-style sci-fi MMO RPG game with unique characters and beautiful open vistas!\r\n\r\nPack your gear and head to the lush planet of Aida, mankind’s last bastion after depleting Earth’s resources to near-inhabitability. In addition to be a viable world, Aida is also located near the path of the comet Mara, which contains an energy known as “Omnium”. To capture this energy, the people built the tower of Omnium, an act that resulted in a catastrophic disaster.\r\n\r\nIn Tower of Fantasy, players will explore the post-catastrophy world of Aida, taking in an open world filled with stunning nature and impressive structures. Play as a selection of characters, each armed with their own unique weapons, and take on the world with your friends. Take the time to learn about your characters, because you’ll need to know who can do what in order to build the best parties and defeat your enemies.\r\n','MMORPG','Windows','Level Infinite','Hotta Studio','2022-08-10','Windows 7 SP1 64-bit','Intel Core i5 or equivalent','8 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GT 1030','25 GB'),(39,515,'Halo Infinite','For the first time ever, a free-to-play Halo experience is available in the form of Halo Infinite’s multiplayer.','For the first time ever, a free-to-play Halo experience is available in the form of Halo Infinite’s multiplayer. 343 Industries and Xbox Game Studios made the multiplayer version of the game available separately from the full story campaign, which is available to purchase for $60 to allow everyone to get in on the action. With the multiplayer, players can take part in two different modes: Arena and Big Team Battle. The first returns to Halo’s multiplayer roots with on-map equipment and 4-player squads. Big Team Battle allows players to mix and match weapons, vehicles and equipment to create a unique combat experience.\r\n\r\nThe game also offers players the ability to customize their Spartan with cosmetic items. Of course, those with the campaign will have access to extra options. Even more can be found in the game’s battle pass which also introduces new modes and maps, as well as community-focused content.\r\n','Shooter','Windows','Xbox Game Studios','343 Industries','2021-11-15','Windows 10 RS5 x64','AMD Ryzen 5 1600 or Intel i5-4440','8 GB RAM','AMD RX 570 or Nvidia GTX 1050 Ti','50 GB available space'),(40,466,'Valorant','Test your mettle in Riot Games’ character-based FPS shooter Valorant.','Test your mettle in Riot Games’ character-based FPS shooter Valorant. Boasting over 10 Agents (the game’s characters) and several map options, Valorant pits players against each other in 5v5 matchups. Players won’t just use guns but also special, sometimes paranormal, abilities. Agents come from all around t he world, each bringing something unique to one of the four classes. Each has four abilities – some gun-oriented, and others tied to their unique skills.\r\n\r\nThe game’s maps range from the desert-like split map, to a monastery, to a city, and finally an old European town. Some of the maps are focused on destruction, while others feature verticality or are dedicated to gameplay like site control.\r\n\r\nPlayers also have a rather large arsenal of weapons to work with ranging from a knife to pistols, shotguns, automatic weapons, and the like.','Shooter','Windows','Riot Games','Riot Games','2020-06-02','Windows 7/8/10','Intel Core 2 Duo E8400','4 GB RAM','Intel HD 4000','?'),(41,467,'Phantasy Star Online 2','Welcome to ARKS, and elite task force searching dangerous planets for the corrupted Falspawn in Phantasy Star 2 Online, Sega’s popular, free-to-play sci-fi MMORPG.','Welcome to ARKS, and elite task force searching dangerous planets for the corrupted Falspawn in Phantasy Star 2 Online, Sega’s popular, free-to-play sci-fi MMORPG available on PC (and Xbox One). Featuring four races with different characteristics and status as well as nine classes, PSO2 offers players a great deal of character customization – particularly with the addition of eighteen different weapons that can be enhanced using cosmic energy known as Photons. \r\n\r\nThe game offers players a wide variety of settings ranging from the ARKS ship to different planets filled with different forms of life. The ARKS ship is home to the ARKS, and the place to go to not only get gear and pick up missions, but also simply hang out. Players can even take advantage of personal quarters, a cafe, and a casino. There’s even a bit of nightlife with things like concerts from characters from other Ips. Each of the planets boast their own region types and unique flora and fauna. Explore  ruins, underground tunnels, forests, and more. And uncover all kinds of mysteries.\r\n','MMORPG','Windows','SEGA','SEGA','2020-05-27','Windows 10 Version 18362.0 and higher (64-bit)','Intel Core 2 Duo E6300 or above','2 GB or greater','NVIDIA GeForce 7800 GT, AMD RADEON HD2900 XT','80 GB (NTFS file system)'),(42,452,'Call Of Duty: Warzone','A standalone free-to-play battle royale and modes accessible via Call of Duty: Modern Warfare.','Call of Duty: Warzone is both a standalone free-to-play battle royale and modes accessible via Call of Duty: Modern Warfare. Warzone features two modes — the general 150-player battle royle, and “Plunder”. The latter mode is described as a “race to deposit the most Cash”. In both modes players can both earn and loot cash to be used when purchasing in-match equipment, field upgrades, and more. Both cash and XP are earned in a variety of ways, including completing contracts.\r\n\r\nAn interesting feature of the game is one that allows players who have been killed in a match to rejoin it by winning a 1v1 match against other felled players in the Gulag.\r\n\r\nOf course, being a battle royale, the game does offer a battle pass. The pass offers players new weapons, playable characters, Call of Duty points, blueprints, and more. Players can also earn plenty of new items by completing objectives offered with the pass.','Shooter','Windows','Activision','Infinity Ward','2020-03-10','Windows 7 64-Bit (SP1) or Windows 10 64-Bit','Intel Core i3-4340 or AMD FX-6300','8GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 670 / GeForce GTX 1650 or Radeon HD 7950','175GB HD space'),(43,21,'Destiny 2','A free-to-play multiplayer Sci-Fi MMOFPS from Bungie.','Get ready to explore the solar system in Bungie’s Destiny 2. The game, available on PS4 and PC, has made the leap to free-to-play — and Steam.\r\n\r\nThis new free version is what player have come to expect from the buy-to-play game, including all of the game’s story, access to all the guardian classes, a selection of multiplayer activities and plenty of new gear.\r\n\r\nDestiny 2 is set in a sci-fi universe where players must take up the roles of Guardians and protect what’s left of Earth from alien attackers — specifically a race known as the Cabal. The story picks up following a successful attack by the Cabal, during which the Guardians have been stripped of their power and must find a way to regain it.\r\n\r\nTem up with friends,take on everything from basic story missions to 3-player strikes and 6-player raids. Enjoy in-game events and challenge other players in different PvP modes, including the traditional deathmatch.\r\n\r\nThe game does include a few purchase options — including the most current expansion and varying amounts of silver for purchasing in-game items.','Shooter','Windows','Bungie','Bungie','2019-10-01','Windows Vista or newer ','Core 2 Duo 2.4G or better','2 GB RAM','GeForce 9800 GTX+ or Radeon HD 4850','10 GB available space'),(44,57,'Fortnite','A free-to-play, standalone mode of Epic Game\'s Fortnite. ','Fortnite Battle Royale is a free-to-play, standalone mode of Epic Game’s Fortnite. The game offers players one giant map that will accommodate 100-player is an all-out PvP battle. Like the game it is spun off from, it also features the ability to build structures and a destructable environment. There’s also a battle bus.\r\n\r\nAlso like the main Fortnite game, Battle Royale is available on several platforms, including PC, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One.\r\n\r\nPlayers of other battle royale style games will be able to jump into Fortnite Battle Royale easily. Similar to other games, players are dropped onto an island where they’re tasked with gathering weapons and supplies while eliminating the competition. To make things a bit more difficult, the map size will shrink over time — thanks to a storm — pushing players closer to each other and eliminating their ability to hide. Last man standing wins the battle.','Shooter','Windows','Epic Games','Epic Games','2017-09-26','Window 7 or later','Intel HD 4000','4 GB','Core i3 2.4','Not defined'),(45,449,'Albion Online','A free-to-play cross-platform sandbox MMO developed and published by Sandbox Interactive GmbH. ','Albion Online is a free-to-play cross-platform sandbox MMO developed and published by Sandbox Interactive GmbH. The game is built around a classless combat system and a player-driven economy. The combat system allows players to swap between playstyles by simply switching gear, allowing them to test out new weapons, armor and more. Skills are improved by crafting and using items.\r\n\r\nPlayers control the economy, buying and selling everything from basic tools and clothes to weapons — almost all of which are crafted by the players. Not only are the items crafted, but they’re built in player-constructed buildings created from resources gathered by players. From bottom to top, everything requires players.\r\n\r\nThe game also allows players to claim their own land, be it a city plot, farm, or island. Of course, there’s also plenty of adventure and battles.','MMORPG','Windows','Sandbox Interactive GmbH','Sandbox Interactive GmbH','2017-07-17','Windows 7, 8 or 10 (64-bit)','Intel/AMD CPU with SSE2','4 GB RAM','Graphics card with DirectX 10 support or better','2 GB available space'),(46,350,'Goodgame Empire','A free to play medieval strategy browser game. Build you own castle and create a powerful army! ','Raise your kingdom from nothing in Goodgame Empire, a free-to-play browser based strategy MMO from Goodgame! In Goodgame Empire, you will gather resources and build your thriving kingdom into a major power on the in-game world map.\r\n\r\nWith over 60 buildings to choose from within the game, Goodgame Empire allows you to make a kingdom based on your personal preferences. Even your mighty castle can be personalized to reflect your tastes and desires. And with weekly updates bringing brand new content, there’s no shortage of new styles to try.\r\n\r\nBut kingdom is complete without an army? In Goodgame Empire, players will have access to over 50 unique military units that they can recruit and customize to take part in battles across four kingdoms in a unique and engaging battle system.\r\n\r\nBut you are not the only king in Goodgame Empire. There are over 70 million players worldwide and it is up to you to decide whether to forge alliances with them or wage war upon to them. There is much to do in order to ensure your kingdom thrives in Goodgame Empire, but it all starts with you and where you build your kingdom.','Strategy','Web Browser','Goodgame Studios','Goodgame Studios','2011-08-14',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(47,427,'Drakensang Online','A free to play browser-based top-down hack-and-slash 3D MMORPG similar to games in the Diablo series.','Drakensang Online is a free to play browser-based top-down hack-and-slash 3D MMORPG, players of Blizzard’s Diablo series will no doubt find the gameplay of Drakensang Online familiar. This browser MMORPG offers much despite its relative obscurity.\r\n\r\nDrakensang Online boasts only four character classes, but they benefit from being well-balanced between one another without feeling scaled-down. Leveling up and buying new in-game merchandise is easy since currency is dropped by defeated monsters, making those new items accessible that much faster.\r\n\r\nDrakensang Online also boasts impressive graphics for itself, with a smooth feel that is rarely found in a browser-based MMORPG. Of course, Drakensang Online needs these smooth graphics as the combat and action within is fast-paced and adrenaline-fueled as players engage hordes of enemies in gripping battles.\r\n\r\nThe PvP arena in Drakensang Online also gives players the chance to engage one another in combat for fun, rewards, and greater experience. The lack of downloading and the free-to-play nature of Drakensang Online combined with its Diablo feel make it an engaging game for gamers of all varieties to play.','MMORPG','Web Browser','Bigpoint','Bigpoint','2011-08-08',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(48,606,'Steel Hunters','A post-apocalyptic extraction shooter with giant mechs.','In a post-apocalyptic world, mechanical giants known as Hunters are used to fight for resources on an abandoned Earth. In Wargaming’s extraction shooter Steel Hunters, players play as one of these hunters, each with its own playstyle, weapons, gear, and mods. Each also has its own unique progression system. As players perfect playing as their Hunter of choice, they can find ways to use their skills in conjunction with their teammates.\r\n\r\nDuring gameplay, players collect boosters to gain an advantage over their opponents. In addition, the game offers players a full giant mech feel by allowing them to smash through buildings and other structures. It’s probably a good thing no one is still living on Earth. Players will also have to contend with the game’s AI in PvE encounters as they try to make their way to the extraction point.','Shooter','Windows','Wargaming ','Wargaming','2025-04-02','Windows 10 64-bit','Intel Core i5 8400 / AMD Ryzen 5 2600','16 GB ','NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2060 / AMD Radeon Vega 64','32 GB'),(49,603,'War Robots: Frontiers','A multiplayer mech game set in a planetary system light years from Earth.','My.games’ multiplayer mech shooter War Robots: Frontiers offers players the ability to build the perfect mech and take it into combat. The game offers a variety of modes. Of course, there’s Team Deathmatch and Last Robot Standing – both of which do what they say on the tin. Players can also test their skills taking and keeping control points in War Rush. And, for the truly competitive, players have the option of working their way up through the ranks in Leagues.\r\n\r\nThe game offers a customizable experience, allowing players to build the perfect mech. The machines can be customized down to pilots, weapons, abilities, and looks. Those who go want to do the most damage can make use of power-ups known as Titans. These are uniquely armed and can do quite a bit of damage.\r\n\r\nWar Robots: Frontiers takes place on the worlds of a planetary system known as Wild Ten. Maps include a freezing planetoid, mines, secret research bases, and more.','Shooter','Windows','My.games','My.games','2025-03-04','Windows 10 64-bit','Intel Core i5-3470 @ 3.20GHz','8 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 660 3GB VRAM','10 GB available space'),(50,601,'Delta Force','A free-to-play team-based tactical shooter.','The Delta Force series returns as a free-to-play modern tactical shooter from Team Jade. The game features different play modes, including one based on the 2002 movie Black Hawk Down. The other modes consist of a 32v32 PvP mode named Warfare and an Operations mode that sends players behind enemy lines.\r\n\r\nThe Black Hawk Down mode is a recreation of the mode from Delta Force: Black Hawk Down. It retells events from Mogadishu in Unreal Engine 5 and features non-stop action and drama.\r\n\r\nWarfare offers players 32v32 player PvP across five different maps. The mode includes dozens of weapons, and various gameplay modes, and is updated regularly. Gameplay takes place on land and via land and sea, and players can take on a variety of roles.\r\n\r\nIn Operations, players team up in 3-person squads to take on AI-controlled mercenari9es, bosses, and other players. The game offers players a highly customizable armory, allowing the modification of weapons as well as vehicles.','Shooter','Windows','TiMi Studio Group','Team Jade','2024-12-04','Windows 10 64 bit','Intel Core i3-4150 / AMD FX-6300','8 GB RAM','Nvidia Geforce GTX 660 / AMD HD 7870 / Intel Arc A380','60 GB available space'),(51,597,'Strinova','A third-person tactical shooter that features the unique mechanic of allowing players to switch between three-dimensional and two-dimensional forms.','Developed and published by iDreamSky, Strinova is a third-person tactical shooter that features the unique mechanic of allowing players to switch between three-dimensional and two-dimensional forms. This mechanic makes for interesting gameplay by allowing players to move through spaces they otherwise would not be able to – like paper sliding between cracks.\r\n\r\nThe game makes use of this mechanic with multilayered maps featuring a variety of game modes, including Demolition and Team Deathmatch. As for appearance, the developers smartly used an anime style, meaning characters look good in two or three dimensions. So players don’t have to worry about their character looking weird while sliding between gaps in walls.','Shooter','Windows','iDreamSky','iDreamSky','2024-11-21','Windows 7/8/10/11 64bit','Intel Core i3-4170','4 GB RAM','Nvidia GeForce GT 730, AMD R7 240','25 GB available space'),(52,598,'SUPERVIVE','Combine MOBAs, battle royales, and hero shooters into one fast paced game hand you have SUPERVIVE.','Theorycraft Games’ SUPERVIVE takes MOBAs, battle royales, and hero shooters and combines them all into one fast-paced experience. \r\n\r\nThe game is built as an open-ended sandbox where players will not only shoot at each other, but jump, glide, bounce, punch, and more. It offers several game modes for teams of varying sizes, including a “squads” battle royale with four players on each team, a duos battle royale, a 4v4 arena, and even some special event modes.\r\n\r\nAs for playable characters, SUPERVIVE offers more than sixteen to choose from. Among these is a mecha-suited pirate hunter, a flamethrower-armed fox, and a lightning-powered anarchist.\r\n\r\nSUPERVIVE is free-to-play and promises to add more content on a very regular basis. In fact, the Steam page states that the list of features will grow “every week”. So there will be plenty for players to keep players coming back time and again.','MOBA','Windows','Theorycraft Games','Theorycraft Games','2024-11-20','Windows 10 64-bit build 1909.1350 or newer','Intel i5-4440 (3.1GHz) - AMD Ryzen 3 3100 (3.6GHz) - 4 physical cores','8 GB RAM','GeForce GTX 980ti or equivalent','8 GB available space'),(53,592,'Starborne: Frontiers','A tactical autobattler set 400 years in the future.','Set 400 years from now, in a future where the Earth is dead, tactical autobattler Starborne Frontiers puts players in command of one of ten warring factions trying to carry out its agenda. The new home of mankind, the Frontier, is being consumed by the Abyss. In addition to carrying out their faction’s goals, players must uncover the secrets of that Aybss and stop it from destroying everything.\r\n\r\nStarborne Frontiers features four game modes: PvE Content, PvP Arena, The Vault, and the Abyss. The Vault requires players to join an alliance in order to raid it for resources. The Abyss is an exploration mode filled with secrets.\r\n\r\nThe game features more than 100 ships that can be customized with weapons, shields, and software. Players will want to think strategically when equipping these items in order to defeat their enemies.','Strategy','Windows','Solid Clouds hf.','Solid Clouds hf.','2024-10-14','Windows 10 and later (64-bit only)','Intel Core i3 / AMD Athlon',' 3 GB RAM','Intel / AMD Radeon / Nvidia GeForce','5 GB available space'),(54,593,'Return Alive','A free-to-play top-down tactical shooter.','A free-to-play, top-down tactical shooter game, Return Alive casts players in the role of a survivor in an apocalyptic world where they must fight for resources, technology, and energy in the wilderness. \r\n\r\nThe game offers players a variety of modes including battlegrounds and matches among others. In each mode, players will collect weapons and items, enhancing stats as they go along. They’ll also collect a Battlesuit that changes their appearance in addition to improving their stats.\r\n\r\nReturn Alive allows players to select their own skill effects as they progress. This, combined with equipment options allows players to customize their playstyle. The game’s matchmaking is designed so that players should expect to be paired with opponents equal to or slightly higher than their own skill level.','Shooter','Windows','KOG','KOG','2024-10-23','Windows 10 (64Bit)','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','8 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','30 GB available space'),(55,587,'Spectre Divide','A 3v3 tactical shooter developed and published by Mountaintop Studios in partnership with former pro gamer shroud,','Spectre Divide is a 3v3 tactical shooter developed and published by Mountaintop Studios in partnership with former pro gamer shroud, The game introduces a “Duality” mechanic that allows players to control two bodies on the map – a main body and a second body called a “Spectre”. The latter can be placed where the player feels they will be most useful. Then they can swap between the two bodies on the fly. This will allow the player to achieve more in the game, covering two sites at once.\r\n\r\nWith shroud’s input, Mountaintop has been able to fine-tune the game and make it ideal for competitive play. The game features “true-to-crosshair accuracy that allows players to shoot on the move. Twenty different weapons can be combined to customize gameplay to the trailer, and eight Sponsor kits offer unique load-outs to appeal to various playstyles.\r\n\r\nPlayers can rank up as a team or on their own or take part in casual and custom play. In addition to the normal 3v3 matches, the game also includes a weekly “Crews” mode that pits teams of fifty to sixty players against each other.','Shooter','Windows','Mountaintop Studios','Mountaintop Studios','2024-09-03','Windows 10 Home','Intel Core i5 (4th Generation or newer) OR AMD Ryzen 5',' 8 GB RAM',' Nvidia GTX 1080-Ti OR AMD RX 6700-XT','20 GB available space'),(56,588,'Vigor','A free-to-play looter shooter from the developers of Operation Flashpoint and the Arma series.','Vigor is available on PC (via Steam) and consoles. Developed and published by Bohemia Interactive, the game is set in the Outlands – all that’s left of a post-apocalyptic Norway in the early 90s.\r\n\r\nThe game features several modes: Encounters, Shootout, and Elimination. The former is a high-stakes mode where players will need to extract resources to build and upgrade their shelter while avoiding death. Shootout is a deathmatch where players are on their own. Elimination is a 5v5 round-based team fight.\r\n\r\nIn Vigor, players can make their Outlanders uniquely theirs with a variety of cosmetic sets ranging from military to non-military. In addition, shelters are more than just something players throw up quickly during Encounters. Permanent shelters also exist outside the mode. These can be upgraded and are where players will craft, generate currency, and more.','Shooter','Windows','Bohemia Interactive ','Bohemia Interactive','2024-09-18','Windows 10','Intel Core i3-8100 / AMD Ryzen 3 1300X','8 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 680 / AMD Radeon R9 280','18 GB available space'),(57,602,'Smite 2','The free-to-play Unreal Engine 5-powered sequel to the popular third-person MOBA','Smite 2 is an updated version of Titan Forge Games\' popular MOBA made using Unreal Engine 5. Featuring all your favorite gods from the original Smite, the third-person game combines hero shooter combat with a 5v5 MOBA. The game requires players to be strategic and stealthy. They will also need to work together with teammates to use combo abilities.\r\n\r\nThe game features full cross-play and cross-progression. It offers auto-build and auto-level features to help players get into the game while also offering everything fans of MOBAs enjoy about the game. Players can master map control, tactics, and more as they fight in a variety of modes. The most dedicated will be able to climb their way through the leader boards in Ranked and earn impressive rewards, including cross-gen skins.\r\n\r\nLike its predecessor, Smite 2 is free-to-play and available on PC via Steam as well as consoles.','MOBA','Windows','Hi-Rez Studios','Titan Forge Games','2024-08-27','Windows 10 64-bit','Intel Core i5-9400F / AMD Ryzen 3750H',' 8 GB RAM',' NVIDIA GTX 1050 / AMD RX 560 / Intel Arc A380','30 GB available space'),(58,583,'The First Descendant','A free-to-play third-person co-op looter shooter developed and published by Nexon.','The First Descendant is a free-to-play third-person 4-player co-op looter-shooter developed and published by Nexon. Featuring a variety of characters and equipment, the game is designed with excitement in mind. Each character has unique skill sets. They can also make use of grappling hooks in combat and can combine their skills with unique weapons to create their own battle style.\r\n\r\nEach character has access to 3 guns, 4 secondary accessories, and a selection of sub-weapons. There are also items used to enhance player characters or their gear.\r\n\r\nPlay scenarios or world missions in order to level. Work together to take on massive bosses. Challenge yourself with increasingly difficult tasks. The First Descendant is available via Xbox, PlayStation, and PC via Steam.','Shooter