ipe from far away, or just roll in for close-quarter combat. \r\n\r\nThe game also features a changing landscape with buildings hit by bombs crumbling or ships sinking. This means players can eliminate things that might otherwise block their line of sight. That’s gonna make the whole hiding behind – or on – a wall thing that much more difficult.','Shooter','Windows','Nexon Games Co., LTC','Nexon','2023-05-18','64-bit Windows 8','3.0 GHz Quad Core CPU','8 GB ','GeForce GTX 960 or Radeon R7 370','15 GB'),(85,552,'Jected - Rivals','A free-to-play game mixing extreme sports with destructible vehicles and a unique ejection mechanic.','Jected – Rivals is a free-to-play game that mixes extreme sports, destructible vehicles, and speed in 18-player matches. To survive in this game, players will need to make use of a special ejection mechanic that will allow them to launch themselves out of their vehicles and into the sky. The trick is learning how to optimize this mechanic and get the lead on everyone else.\r\n\r\nPlayers have a variety of vehicles to choose from – finding the one that best fits their playstyle. Choices range from supercars to SUVs, and more. And each can be tailored to the player’s preferences.\r\n\r\nThe jetwing mechanic allows players to free themselves from the confines of their vehicle and easily move over or around obstacles. It can even be paired with a selection of gadgets like a grappling hook.','Sports','Windows','THQ Nordic','PowWow Entertainment','2023-05-04','Windows 10 64 Bit','Quad Core 4 GHZ','8 GB','NVidia GTX 1060','8 GB'),(86,557,'Ethyrial: Echoes of Yore','A old-school MMORPG set in a world on the brink of Civil War','Ethyrial: Echoes of Yore is an old-school, hardcore MMORPG set in a world on the brink of civil war. Nobles have wrested control from an imperial council and now fight for power and cults work to implement their own plans for the world. Add to that the creatures that pose a threat and you can see the world of Irumesa is a dangerous place.\r\n\r\nEthyrial allows players to build a character using an expansive character and class system. They’ll need to do their best with the build and be willing to work with others because if they die, they’re permanently dead.\r\n\r\nThe game features a large world to explore, filled with treasure and secrets. In addition, it has room for players to claim property and build whatever they desire. Learn crafting, explore the game’s ongoing story, and more.','MMORPG','Windows',' Gellyberry Studios',' Gellyberry Studios','2023-05-01','Windows 7,8,10','Intel i5-6600K, or AMD Ryzen 5 3600, 3.5GHz','8 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1070, 8GB or AMD Radeon RX 590, 8GB','20 GB available space'),(87,605,'Honkai: Star Rail','A free-to-play sci-fantasy game from HoYoVerse','Join the ranks of the Nameless and step aboard the Astral Express to follow the path the Aeon Akivili once tread. HoYoVerse’s Honkai: Star Rail begins on a space station where the main character, known as the Trailblazer, is woken during an invasion. Missing they’re memory, the Trailblazer is invited to join the crew of the Astral Express, where they may search for answers as they traverse different worlds.\r\n\r\nEach world is associated with a different god-like entity, or Aeon, and as the Trailblazer visits each world, they acquire new abilities related to that Aeon. This typically aids them in dealing with disasters caused by objects called “Stellarons”, also known as the Cancer of All Worlds.\r\n\r\nThe Trailblazer carries one of these Stellarons inside themselves, and as they travel, they endeavor to learn more about it and solve the mystery of their missing past.\r\n\r\nAs Honkai: Star Rail is a gacha game, players can roll on many of the characters they meet throughout their travels. As with Star Rail’s sister game Genshin Impact, these characters boast elemental abilities of varying types, each related to one of the game’s Aeons. Weapons and other power-up items are rolled on as well.\r\n\r\nHonkai: Star Rail’s gameplay includes repeatable fights required to obtain leveling materials as well as mini-games and regular events.','RPG','Windows','HoYoVerse','HoYoVerse','2023-04-26','Windows 7 65-Bit','Intel Core i3','6 GB','Nvidia GeForce GTX 650 or better','53 GB'),(88,547,'Warlander','A medieval-style combat game with a selection of modes and characters.','Warlander is a third-person multiplayer game that combines a Medival-style setting with fantasy items and abilities – and robots. The gameplay is made of skirmishes and castle siege warfare with as many as 100 players and features classes like Warriors, Clerics, and Mages. Players don’t only rely on their class powers in combat, however. They can also make use of siege weapons.\r\n\r\nThe game features two combat modes: 2 army and 5 army, and combines gameplay styles of MOBAs, battle royales, 3rd person hack-and-slash, ranged combat, and strategic diplomacy. Players either defend castles or take to the battlefield to fight the enemy, capture towers, and more. They’ll need to use both their siege weapons and spells well in order to win.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the many gameplay features, Warlander features a sizeable roster of class-based characters. Each has its own customizable equipment, skills, and even emotes.','MOBA','Windows','Plaion','Toylogic Inc.','2023-01-24','Windows 10 64-bit','Intel Core i5-7400 @3.00 GHz / AMD FX-600 Six-Core','4 GB','GeForce GTX 960, 4GB/Radeon RX 56 4GB','10 GB'),(89,594,'Stalcraft: X','A free-to-play MMOFPS set in an open-world.','Stalcraft: X is an open-world MMOFPS set in the Chernobyl Exclusion Zone. The game combines PvP and PvE, with activities like artifact hunting, mutant slaying, quests, and faction wars. It also offers “session modes” for those who don’t have a lot of time to spend in the game.\r\n\r\nDespite being an MMO, the game avoids the leveling mechanic associated with the genre in favor of players progressing by obtaining equipment. This can be done in a variety of ways, including purchasing it from other players. In fact, one thing Stalcraft: X does take from the MMO genre is the economy, which allows players to become merchants.\r\n\r\nStalcraft: X is free-to-play. Players can support the game either via a play-for-time system or by purchasing cosmetics. That said, all items can be obtained by playing the game. Cash purchases will just allow players to get things sooner.','Shooter','Windows','EXBO','EXBO','2022-12-09','Windows 10 64-bit / Windows 11 64-bit','Intel Core i5 3470 / AMD FX-6300','4 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 750 Ti / AMD Radeon RX 560 / Intel Arc A310','50 GB available space'),(90,545,'Fangs','A 4v4 MOBA with hero-specific strategies.','Fangs is a 4v4 MOBA with a customizable experience developed and published by Hidden Leaf Games. Players can unlock and alternate hero-specific augments to make their hero their own. The game boasts a diverse cast of characters, both in background and style. The developer’s intention is for players to really find a hero that resonates with them.\r\n\r\nThe game’s customization system allows players to change augments for each round, assuring that their own personal style can complement that of their teammates. Augments offer players the chance to boost abilities – a little more healing here, a little more damage there.\r\n\r\nFangs is designed to be fast-paced, cutting out a lot of the stuff that causes other MOBA matches to drag out. It focuses on teamwork with the ultimate goal being that players feel like part of a community. The game is also intended to be friendly to new players and veterans and is described as “easy to learn and hard to master”.','MOBA','Windows','Hidden Leaf Games','Hidden Leaf Games','2022-11-30','Windows 7 and up','Intel Core i5-4430 or AMD FX-6300','20 GB','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB or AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','20 GB'),(91,549,'Summoners War: Chronicles','A multi-platform ARPG set in the Summoners War universe.','Help the King of Rahil defend his kingdom against a massive conspiracy set in the Summoners War Universe. In Summoners War: Chronicles, players become a Rahil Guard and explore the world with a summoned companion. The ARPG offers players a look at what decision led to the world as seen in the original Summoners War game, Sky Arena. Players can choose to play one of three Summoners: Orbia, Kina, and Cleaf. They, along with their summoned companion will explore the continents and fight the darkness.\r\n\r\nEach of the three summoners has its own unique role and skill set. These roles are enhanced by the ability to summon a team of monsters. And there are plenty to choose from – more than 350. Players will need to manage both their own combat and that of the monsters in real time in order to successfully explore the world.\r\n\r\nSummoners War: Chronicles can be played on mobile devices and PC.','MMORPG','Windows','Com2uS','Com2uS','2022-11-09','Windows 10','Intel Core i5-6400','8 GB','Nvidia GTX 960','10 GB'),(92,541,'Marvel Snap','A fast paced strategy card game set in the Marvel universe.','Take all your favorite Marvel heroes, give them super cute forms, put them in a strategic card battler game and you have Marvel Snap. As indicated by the name, the game is intended to be played in a snap – not the kind that Thanos used to eliminate half the world’s population, but the kind that means you can play a quick game anytime. In fact, any time you have three minutes or more to spare, you can get a game in.\r\n\r\nNot only does the game feature many familiar faces from the Marvel universe, it also boasts more than 50 locations many fans will recognize. Each locale is more than just a change in appearance, they also change how the game is played, adjusting abilities. New locations will be introduced weekly, and players will need to flex their problem-solving skills in order to make the best of them.\r\n\r\nThe game is also designed for risk-takers. “Snap” doesn’t just mean the game is fast. It’s also a mechanic that allows players to raise the stakes of a match and potentially double their rewards.','Card Game','Windows','Nuverse','Second Dinner Studios, Inc.','2022-10-18','Windows 7 (SP1+)','Intel Core i5-650 or AMD Phenom II X4 965','4 GB','Nvidia GeForce GTX 650 or AMD Radeon HD HD 6950','4 GB'),(93,542,'World Boss','An experimental FPS based on io and roguelike gameplay.','Win the World Boss crown in Fresh and LazerBeam’s casual FPS, World Boss. This new shooter pits sixteen players against each other in a game inspired by io games and roguelikes. It’s intended to be a more accessible multiplayer shooter for everyone.\r\n\r\nWorld Boss focuses on skill and experimentation. Game matches take place in semi-persistent lobbies. There, players will fight, level up, and make use of custom arsenals and perks in order to gain the upper hand and make it to the top of the leaderboard.\r\n\r\nThe game is designed with casual players in mind, skipping the queues and putting them directly into arenas, and streamlining combat to get players right into the action. Players can create their own builds by unlocking weapons and abilities each time they level up, even combining features from different weapons.','Shooter','Windows','Playside','Playside','2022-10-19','Windows 10','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD Athalon Silver PRO 3125GE','8 GB','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radion R7 370 2GB','6 GB'),(94,536,'Omega Strikers','A 3v3 socccer-style game with knockouts.','Grab two of your closest friends and team up in epic 3v3 soccer-style matches in Odyssey Interactive\'s Omega Strikers. The co-op PvP game pits two teams of three against each other in fast-paced matches where they both try to knock out their opponents and score goals soccer-style.\r\n\r\nSimilar to MOBAs and shooters, Omega Strikers features a growing roster of playable characters, including a well-armored hamster. Each character can be unlocked through gameplay and players have several play options to choose from. These include unranked, ranked, and private lobbies. The game also launched with a selection of maps. More maps and modes are planned for later release.\r\n\r\nThe game offers cosmetics and battle passes for monetization. There are no loot boxes or purchasable power boosts. The game will also feature seasons that will add new playable characters, stages, unlockables, and more.','Sports','Windows','Odyssey Interactive','Odyssey Interactive','2022-09-16','Windows 7 and up','Intel Core i5-4430 or AMD FX-6300','8 GB','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 or AMD Radeon R7 370','4 GB'),(95,537,'Gundam Evolution','A 6v6 team-based shooter based on the Gundam multiverse','Embrace your love of shooter and all thing Gundam, because Bandai Namco\'s Gundam Evolution is here for you. Gundam fans everywhere get to live out their dreams of hopping into a Gundam suit and taking on the enemy in this 6v6 game featuring Units from across the different Gundam universes. Each suit has its own set of skills and abilities, as well as HP levels – because some are just beefier than others.\r\n\r\nIn addition to their unique stats, the Units all feature a Thrust system that allows them to cover long distances quickly and a Dash ability for an additional acceleration boost. They also offer players access to G-Maneuver effects. These are unique to each Unit and can be activated with the G-Maneuver Meter hits 100%.\r\n\r\nGundam Evolution is currently available for free on Steam. It boasts a very positive rating on the platform, so Gundam fans will want to give it a peek.','Shooter','Windows','Bandai Namco','Bandai Namco','2022-09-21','Windows 10 (64-bit)/Windows 11','Intel Core i5-3570','8 GB','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1050','40 GB'),(96,544,'Galahad 3093','A 12v12 team shooter featuring mechs based on Arthurian legend.','Mechs and Arthurian legend combine in Simultronics’ free-to-play team shooter Galahad 3093. The game features eight playable Knights and their mechs (known as Lances) each with its own unique