ward on the pass being cosmetic as well.','Card Game','Windows','WhisperGames','Clarity Games','2021-01-28','64-bit Windows 7 / Windows 10','Intel Core i5-2300, 2.8 GHz or equal equivalent','6 GB RAM','NVIDIA® GeForce™ GTX 660 or equal equivalent','8 GB available space'),(111,498,'Blankos Block Party','What happens when you take the vinyl collectible toy experience and combine it with an open-world multiplayer game? You get Blankos Block Party!\r\n','What happens when you take the vinyl collectible toy experience and combine it with an open-world multiplayer game? You get Blankos Block Party, a free-to-play game that allows players to build their own block parties – which are like Mario Party-style activities – to share with their friends. Players can even participate in regular competitions held by the developer Mythical Games, for a chance to see their builds featured.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the block party builds, the game’s other focus is on the Blankos, vinyl-style “dolls” brought to life. Just like with real world vinyl dolls, these are collectible and can be bought and sold. Just like with real-world collectables, Blankos Block Party features limited edition vinyls, including some players can win or those that are available as part of seasonal events. The Blankos in question are designed by popular vinyl toy artists like Jon-Paul Kaiser, Tara McPherson, Kronk, and Dan Lish.\r\n','MMO','Windows','Third Kind Games','Mythical Games Inc','2020-12-11','Windows 10 64-bit ','Intel Core i7-4770 or AMD FX 8310',' GB RAM','Nvidia GTX 660 or AMD Radeon HD 7870','?'),(112,499,'Slapshot: Rebound','Do you like hockey? How about physic-based multiplayer, arcade-style sports games with cute graphics? Well, this is the one for you.','Do you like hockey? How about physic-based multiplayer, arcade-style sports games with cute graphics? Well, this is the one for you. Oddshot Games’ Slapshot: Rebound offers players the ability to play matches of arcade-style hockey games, without 