al Return: Black Survival','Combining elements from battle royale, MOBA, and the survival genres, Eternal Return: Black Survival is a game designed with a broad audience in mind. ','Combining elements from battle royale, MOBA, and the survival genres, Eternal Return: Black Survival is a game designed with a broad audience in mind. The game takes place on a deserted island, where an organization known as AGLAIA is busy conducting shady experiments on humans in order to turn them into super humans. These test subjects are the game’s characters. \r\n\r\nPlayers compete in matches of up to 18 players, either in solo mode or with friends in the battle royale standard fight to be the last one standing. In addition to getting the combat basics down, players have other things to learn to make the best use of, such as being able to teleport across the map, or crafting important items. Crafting is very important in Eternal Return, allowing players to improve their gear and their chances of survival. \r\n\r\nThe game also offers players flexibility, allowing them to create custom games for as many or as few people as they like. This feature is designed with esports in mind.','MOBA','Windows','Nimble Neuron','Nimble Neuron','2020-10-14','WINDOWS® 7, 8, 8.1, 10 (64Bit)','Intel Core i3-3225, AMD FX-4350','4 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GT 640, ATI Radeon HD 7700','3 GB available space'),(115,473,'Spellbreak','Spellbreak is a multiplayer, multi-platform battle-royale where player take on the role of a “battlemage” mastering elemental magic and using spells to compete against other players.','Spellbreak is a multiplayer, multi-platform battle-royale where player take on the role of a “battlemage” mastering elemental magic and using spells to compete against other players. Players can choose between six different classes, Frostborn, Conduit, Pyromancer, Toxicologist, Stoneshaper, or Tempest. Each has a different playstyle that can be made even more unique with player customization – including creating different spell combinations.\r\n\r\nThe game features an ever-changing world known as Primdal with battles taking place in the Hollow Lands. Scattered throughout the map are hidden chests containing all kinds of useful equipment that will help during a fight. \r\n\r\nSpellbreak can be played on PC via the Epic Games Store, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch. The game features cross-play and cross-progression, so players can play anywhere and bring their progress with them.\r\n','Battle Royale','Windows','Proletariat','Proletariat','2020-09-04','64-bit Windows 10','Intel(R) Core(TM) i5-6400 CPU @ 2.70GHz (4 CPUs)','8 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GT 640/Radeon R7 GPU ','?'),(116,474,'Rocket League','Get your car-soccer gaming on for free with Psyonix’s Rocket League. The popular competitive multi-player game is a popular offering with over 57 million players.','Get your car-soccer gaming on for free with Psyonix’s Rocket League. The popular competitive multi-player game is a popular offering with over 57 million players. It includes both online casual and competitive modes as well as a fully-featured offline season mode. Players can also create custom matches using “Mutators” that allow them to change the rules, or play existing hockey and basketball-inspired modes.\r\n\r\nThe game offers a Rocket Pass option for serious players, which includes a 50%XP bonus and up to 70 special rewards like a new battle-car, keys, and more. There is also a challenge system that rewards players for participating in online matches and completing weekly challenges. Players can also purchase epsorts customization item in the Rocket League Esports Shop.\r\n','Sports','Windows','Psyonix LLC','Psyonix LLC','2020-09-24','Windows 7 (64 bit) or Newer (64 bit) Windows OS','2.5 GHz Dual core','4GB','NVIDIA GeForce 760, AMD Radeon R7 270X, or better','20GB'),(117,471,'Armor Valor','Build your empire with the help of mythical heroes and well thought out strategy in R2 Games’ s