ame puts an emphasis on player chouse with decisions affecting the course of the narrative.\r\n\r\nQuests range from helping solve quarrels between families to exploring dungeons and new realms — in addition to protecting the kingdom you’ve chosen to ally yourself with. So, there’s always something to do.','MMORPG','Windows','INFERNA LIMITED','INFERNA LIMITED','2019-12-21','Windows 7','Dualcore 2.6 Ghz','2 GB RAM','GTX 760','10 GB available space'),(128,443,'Ultimate Pirates','A browser-based strategy MMO published for both desktop and mobile browsers by Gameforge.  ','Ultimate Pirates is a browser-based strategy MMO published for both desktop and mobile browsers by Gameforge. Developed by Moonmana and Grafit — who are known for their contributions to Bethesda and CD Projekt Red games — Ultimate Pirates features both PvE and PvP that will appeal to the pirate lovers among us.\r\n\r\nSail the oceans, explore Caribbean islands and plunder all the treasure you can. Team up with other players or fight them and take all their loot — not just their treasure, but weapons. In addition to fighting other players for their booty, players will also find themselves up against NPCs and monsters of the deep. Of course, the end-goal is to end up as an “ultimate pirate”, which can only be achieved by building a pirate empire complete with ports, shipyards, buildings, and more.','Strategy','Web Browser','Gameforge','Moonmana','2019-12-02',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(129,437,'Stay Out','An MMORPG featuring urban exploration and shooter elements.','Stay Out is an MMORPG featuring urban exploration and shooter elements developed and published by Mobile Technologies LLC. Players ake on the role of a “Stalker” and explore places forgotten by humanity. These are places once ruled and ruined by man and reclaimed by nature.\r\n\r\nEplsore the alienation zone, avoid the dangers, and uncover an array of secrets. Rediscover long-forgotten secret labs. Search out strange artifacts, survive strange new life forms and mysterious anomalies. But don’t get so distracted you forget the important things like food and water.\r\n\r\nLike other Stalker inspired games, players will need to manage their inventory well and keep track of their biological stats. Surviving is more than just avoiding danger and killing monsters.','Shooter','Windows','Mobile Technologies LLC','Mobile Technologies LLC','2019-11-27','Windows 7/8 (64-bit)','Intel Core i5 / AMD Ryzen 5 (or better)','8000 MB RAM','GeForce 1050Ti / AMD RX570 with 3Gb memory','7000 MB available space'),(130,439,'PC Futbol Legends','An arcade soccer game inspired by cult arcade games from IDC games. ','PC Futbol Legends is an arcade soccer game from IDC games. Matches are played on medium-sized fields with no fouls or offsides. It’s designed to bring back the feel of classic arcade soccer games.\r\n\r\nThe game features a vintage, “not-too-serious” art style inspire by the cult games of the 90s. It avoids the complexities of football managers and hard-core simulators commonly seen today.\r\n\r\nInstad PC Futbol Legends uses simple controls based around basic soccer plays, such as passing, lobbing and shooting, and tackling. To make things more fun, the game offers temporary boosts.\r\n\r\nPC Futbol Legends includes an International Cup Mode and a league. It also features 52 national teams and 28 hand drawn managers.','Sports','Windows','IDG GAmes','IDG GAmes','2019-11-01',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(131,440,'Vampire Empire','A multiplayer strategy game that focuses on the war between vampires and werewolves. ','Set loosely in a medieval fantasy world, Game Hollywood’s Vampire Empire is a multiplayer strategy game that focuses on the war between vampires and werewolves. The game — published on R2Games platform — draws from a variety of history and lore, combining the world of the legendary vampire Count Dracula with that of other historical and fairytale figures. Join up with friends all over the world using real-time