ive CCG players, allowing the developers to adjust the AI and make it appropriately challenging. Eternal boasts dozens of enemy decks with “boss level” environments. It is billed by the developer as having unlimited choices in gameplay. Players can freely mix cards to create their perfect deck.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the promise of unlimited deck customization, Eternal also promises frequent updates that will add new cards and additional content. As an bonus, all content — cards and game modes — can be unlocked without the need of purchasing it.\r\n\r\nPlayers can sign up for Eternal via the game’s site.','Card Game','Windows','Dire Wolf Digital','Dire Wolf Digital','2018-11-15',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(146,503,'Artifact','Valve’s Artifact is two games in one. Whether you’re looking for the original Dota 2 trading card game created with the help of card game designer Richard Garfield or something a little more streamlined, Artifact has both in one download.','Valve’s Artifact is two games in one. Whether you’re looking for the original Dota 2 trading card game created with the help of card game designer Richard Garfield or something a little more streamlined, Artifact has both in one download. \r\n\r\nArtifact Classic is everything the game was originally envisioned to be, bringing the world of Dota 2 into a highly strategic and competitive card game. Artifact Foundry took Classic and reworked is based on player feedback, streamlining the gameplay and adding new content. In Foundry, players are able to see all three lanes of gameplay at once and utelize the mana pool across all of them at the same time. The developers also changed how randomness impacts gameplay in Foundry.\r\n\r\nThe Foundry version of the game offers 100 more cards than what’s available in Classic. It also boasts an extended tutorial, playable demos for each hero, and extra PvE and PvP content. \r\n\r\nSince both versions of the game are available as a single free-to-play download, players can access all content for free. In Foundry cards are unlocked via gameplay. In Classic, all cards are available to all players.\r\n','Card Game','Windows','Valve','Valve','2018-11-29','64-bit Windows 7 / 8 / 10','Intel i5, 2.4 Ghz or better','4 GB RAM','Integrated HD Graphics 520 w/128 MB or better','7 GB available space'),(147,538,'World War 3','A realistic multiplayer tactical FPS.','Team up with your friends and wage war in real-world locations in Wishlist Games and The 4 Winds Entertainment’s tactical FPS World War 3. Engage in combat in places like Warsaw and Moscow on maps designed to be as realistic as possible. Choose from a massive selection of weapons to build the ideal loadout before rolling out with a myriad of vehicles, drones, and more. You’ll need everything available to survive and defeat the other team.\r\n\r\nPlayers can take to battle as infantry soldiers, navigate the field in tanks or other vehicles, use drones to keep an eye on things, and more. Whatever way a player chooses to play, there’s something for them. The massive amounts of artillery and gadgets will allow them to build a loadout that’s ideal for them. Once a player has built their ideal loadout, they test them out on battlefields filled with up to 40 players.\r\n\r\nThere are currently two game modes. The first is a 20v20 point capture. The second is a 10v10 Team Deathmatch.','Shooter','Windows','Wishlist Games, The 4 Winds Entertainment','The Farm 51','2018-10-19','Windows 10','Intel Core i3-4340K / AMD FX-6300','8 GB','Geforce GTX 670 / GTX 1650 or AMD Radeon HD 7950','80 GB'),(148,299,'Combat Arms: Reloaded','A free to play modern first person shooter with lots of maps and weapons!','Combat Arms is a free to play tactical lobby based first person shooter (FPS) developed by the South Korean company Doobic Studios. It offers multiple types of game modes, a ranking system based on experience, and various ways to customize your weapons and player models.\r\n\r\nThere is no shortage of game modes to choose from in Combat Arms. You have One Man Army, Elimination, Capture the Flag, Fireteam, Quarantine Regen, Elimination Pro, Search and Destroy, Seize and Secure, Spy Hunt, Bombing Run, Hired Guns, and VIP Escort. These game modes all offer various ways to win from taking the enemies flag and running it back to your base to planting a bomb and defending it from the enemy team as you wait for it to explode. All of these game modes take place on various maps with very nice graphics.\r\n\r\nThe ranking system in Combat Arms is based on the experience you have earned in the game. You acquire experience by completing objectives, killing other players and using the Gear Points (GP) that you acquire from leveling up to purchase new gear. The ranks are all based on common military ranks that you can achieve in the army. Using the GP that you acquire you can purchase different weapons, weapon attachments, and accessories that your character can wear into battle all to make you look cooler and be more effective than your opponents.','Shooter','Windows','VALOFE, NEXON','Doobic Studios','2018-10-31','XP','Intel Pentium 3 1 GHz or AMD Equivalent','512 MB','GeForce 2 MX','6 GB'),(149,68,'Dreadnought','A free-to-play combat flight simulator developed by Yager Development and published by Grey Box. ','Dreadnought is a free-to-play combat flight simulator developed by Yager Development and published by Grey Box. In Dreadnought, players pilot a massive battleship, ranging from the titular Dreadnought to the Tactical Cruiser. All ships are heavily armed with projectile weapons, and each has it’s own variety of advantages and issues. And, all ships are highly customizable — down to the smallest detail. This includes weapons and modules as well as the paint job (hull coatings and decals).\r\n\r\nPlayers take on the enemy in 5v5 class-based arena battles. With each ship having advantages and disadvantages, players will want to work together to build the most efficient team possible.\r\n\r\nDue to the high customization options available in the game, Dreadnought only features 5 actual ships. However, players will be able to outfit them in a variety of ways, resulting in a much wider variety of ships overall.\r\n\r\nPlayer matches in Dreadnought are estimated to last between 5 and 15 minutes, making it a great game for people who may not have hours to spend logged in on any given day.\r\n\r\nOn the monetization end, Dreadnought features two kinds of currency: the currency earned in game — called “Fleet Points (FP), and the currency purchased via the game market using real cash — Grey Box Points (GP). Items bought with GP offer bonuses and customization options but will not impact gameplay.','Shooter','Windows','Grey Box','Yager Development','2018-10-14','Windows 7 64-bit','Intel Core i5-4690T - 2.5 GHz','4 GB of RAM','DirectX 11-compatible video card with dedicated 1 GB memory','11 GB space available'),(150,28,'Spacelords','A free-to-play 4v1 sci-fi shooter. ','MercurySteam’s sci-fi shooter Spacelords is the free-to-play re-take on Raiders of the Broken Planet. The game features 4v1 combat where players can experience both sides of the game’s story, either as the Raiders trying to free the Broken Planet or the Antagonist.\r\n\r\nPlayers head to the broken planet in search of a substance known as Aleph. This substance can be used to improve combat, heal, and is crucial to most missions. However, it’s also volatile and must be absorbed quickly, before it’s gone.\r\n\r\nSpacelords’ gameplay is centered around the concept of gathering Aleph, and includes brawling, which allows players to get in close and take it off of their enemies. Players will also want to make good use of cover to keep others from getting close enough to take their Aleph.\r\n\r\nThe game also contains a stress system based around Aleph. If players don’t watch their stress and keep it under control, they’ll become visible to their opponents, cover or not.\r\n\r\nLive the game’s story through a broad cinematic experience featuring over 80 scenes. Play as any one of 17 different characters that can be customized using more than 500 cards, and arm yourself with any of 70 unlockable, and moddable weapons.','Shooter','Windows',' MercurySteam Entertainment','MercurySteam','2018-09-22','Windows 7 or 8','Intel i5 4460/AMD FX6300','4 GB RAM','GTX560/AMD R7 260 (2GB graphics)','10 GB available space'),(151,450,'Battlerite Royale','A free to play battle royale set in the Battlerite universe.','Battle Royale meets MOBA in Stunlock Studio’s Battlerite Royale. Team up with friends, or go in on your own and fight to the last man standing on a map 30X the size of the maps in the original Battlerite game. Use spells, potions, traps, and more to keep yourself alive and eliminate your foes. And be smart about it.\r\n\r\nPlayers can choose from over 20 champions to play as, ranging from cute little magical creatures to big tanky monsters — and everything in between. As is standard with battle royales, you will have to deal with a shrinking land mass — this time because of the Death Vortex. But don’t worry, you can get away faster if you use use your loyal mount.','MOBA','Windows','Stunlock Studios','Stunlock Studios','2018-09-26','Windows XP or newer','Dual Core from Intel or AMD at 2.8 GHz','4 GB RAM','Intel HD 3000','3 GB available space'),(152,454,'Magic: The Gathering Arena','A free-to-play digital recreation of Wizards of the Coast\'s popular collectible card game.','Magic: The Gathering Arena is a free-to-play digital recreation of Wizards of the Coast’s popular collectible card game. Intended to be the best way to play the latest cards from the real-world Magic game, MTG Arena features the same rules, depth, and choices available from the original game.\r\n\r\nThe game features full card sets with around 1,000 cards being added every year. It also boasts a new Games Rules Engine (GRE), which is capable of reading any card created for Magic.\r\n\r\nMTG Arena has also been designed with spectator play and streaming in mind. It features easy to understand, esports specific visuals and a variety of play modes ranging from ranked matchmaking to draft events.','Card Game','Windows','Wizards of the Coast','Wizards of the Coast','2018-09-27','Windows 7, Windows 10','AMD Athlon 64 X2 Dual Core 5600+ or Equivalent','2 GB','GeForce GTX 8800 or Equivalent','?'),(153,341,'League of Angels 3','A free-to-play turn-based strategy browser game developed and published by GTArcade Entertainment, Inc.','League of Angels III is a free-to-play turn-based strategy browser game developed and published by GTArcade Entertainment, Inc. The game builds on the previous two installments, adding new features, but keeping to the same theme — build an army of lady-angels and fight other armies, big bosses, and even other players.\r\n\r\nOne of the main features of the game is the Hero League, an-all new PvP event that allows players to compete for special titles and rewards. This league is open to players level 40 and above with a Battle Rating of over 50,000. Another feature is the Conquest mode, which allows players to fight dragons and (potentially) walk away with their treasure.\r\n\r\nLoA III offers three modes: Realm, Arena, and Trial. Realm provides players with a way to work around obstacles in hero awakening, arma reinforcement and evolution, and mores. Arena is, obviously, for all your bloody PvP lust. Trial is for those who need to gain XP.\r\n\r\nWhen playing LoA III, players will build their army out of a selection of heroes — each with unique abilities divided into four classes: Defense, Attack, Healing, and Support. Of course, there are plenty of weapons and gear to collect and arm the heroes with as well.\r\n\r\nEffectively, if turn-based games with angel armies and shiny gear is your jam, then you’ll want to grab League of Angels III.','MMORPG','Web Browser','GTArcade Entertainment','GTArcade Entertainment','2018-08-14',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(154,282,'BlackShot: Revolution','Get thrown into the fast-paced action of a virtual war zone and compete against other players.','BlackShot: Revolution is a mondernization of the free-to-play first person shooter MMO developed by Vertigo Games. Get thrown into the fast-paced action of a virtual war zone and compete against other players for competing nations as a mercenary.\r\n\r\nChoose from four different mercenaries and customize them to fit your play style. You can choose to customize your kit from various Rifles, Snipers, Shotguns, SMGs, Pistols, Melee weapons, and Grenades. You can also customize how your character looks to an extent so people can tell you apart in game. As you use certain types of weapons you will earn rewards for the type of weapons you use, this is the game’s mastery system.\r\n\r\nWith over 10 different maps and 6 different game types you will never run out of different situations in Blackshot. Participate in Weapon Race, Team Deathmatch, Team Flag Match, Search & Destroy, Throwing, and Running Man. As you kill players and gain points you will earn ranks. You can climb all the way from the Beginner rank to Commander in Chief.','Shooter','Windows','Papaya Play','Vertigo Games','2018-07-27','Window XP / 2000 / Vista / 7','Pentium 4 2.0Ghz','1 GB','GeForce 6800 GT / RADEON X800 GT','5 GB'),(155,31,'Cosmos Invictus','A strategic collectible card game developed and published by Pegnio Ltd. ','Cosmos Invictus is a strategic collectible card game developed and published by Pegnio Ltd. Described by the developer as being filled with tactical elements not normally found in card games, Cosmos Invictus features customizable spaceships,pilots, and events that can have a great influence on the battle. The developer emphasizes that this game is “true, pure, hard sci-fi” with no magic involved.\r\n\r\nPlayers take on the role of Captain for one of two factions, Gaia Unity or High Frontier Alliance. Some cards will be determined by this choice. Decks are abuilt out of a selection of mechs (the main unit in space combat), mech pilots, and customizable spaceships capable of direct attack or counter attack. Pilots combined with mechs create extra abilities.\r\n\r\nPlayers can craft their own cards and can even melt duplicates down for use in the crafting process.','Card Game','Windows','Pegnio Ltd','Pegnio Ltd','2018-06-27','Windows XP, Windows Vista, Windows 7, Windows 8','Intel Pentium D or AMD Athlon 64 X2','2 MB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce 6800 (256 MB) or ATI Radeon X1600 (256 MB) or better','1 GB available space'),(156,460,'Empire: World War 3','A free-to-play browser-based action packed strategy game from the developer of Legends of Honor.','Empire: World War III is a free-to-play browser-based strategy game from the developer of Legends of Honor. Players guild bases, train units, and control them in battle. Acquire the resources needed to build your bases and armies by mining Millennium. You’ll need to make sure you obtain it before your enemies do.\r\n\r\nBuild and train multiple armies with different attributes and choose the right commander to lead them. As you level up, update troops and research different technologies to keep you at the top of your game. Don’t forget to be as sneaky as possible and sabotage your enemies and build alliances with others. Do anything you can to have the highest stash of Millennium.\r\n','Strategy','Web Browser','Goodgame Studios','Goodgame Studios','2018-06-28',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(157,506,'Totally Accurate Battlegrounds','Take 60 players, throw them on a map together with over 90 weapons, including balloon crossbows, pots and pans, and inflatable hammers, add physics-based parkour and you have Landfall’s Totally Accurate Battlegrounds (TABG).','Take 60 players, throw them on a map together with over 90 weapons, including balloon crossbows, pots and pans, and inflatable hammers, add physics-based parkour and a bit of The Floor is Lava, and you have Landfall’s Totally Accurate Battlegrounds (TABG).\r\n\r\nFeaturing everything players would expect from a battle royale game – the shrinking map, collecting equipment, and the fight to be the last player standing – TABG is different in that it features a physics engine that produces all kinds of wobbly effects. In fact, the devs seem to feel the wobblier the better.\r\n\r\nOriginally intended as an April Fool’s Day joke, the game was a spinoff of Landfall’s Totally Accurate Battle Simulator. Of course, it’s prank origins results in some rather silly gameplay scenarios, such as players slapping each other to death. The game also offers other unique features like dual-wielding.\r\n','Shooter','Windows','Landfall','Landfall','2018-06-06','Win 7 64 bit','Intel i5 @2.5 GHz or equivalent','8 GB RAM','GTX 770 or AMD R9 280','5 GB available space'),(158,434,'Will To Live','A free-to-play MMORPG-shooter developed and published by AlphaSoft LLC.','Will to Live is a free-to-play MMORPG-shooter developed and published by AlphaSoft LLC. Set in a post-apocalyptic wasteland, the game is an open-world shooter littered with radiation, mutants, and other survivors. To survive, players will not only need to contend with the above but also manage their health via hunger and thirst mechanics.\r\n\r\nWhile exploring the open world, players will not only fight players and other NPCs but discover the world’s history, gather resources, trade, and more.\r\n\r\nPlayers can create up to four characters in Will to Live — allowing them to have one of each class. Each class has its own equipment featuring realistic behavior that takes ballistics and specs into account. The weapons can be modified as well.','MMORPG','Windows','AlphaSoft LLC','AlphaSoft LLC','2018-04-05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(159,543,'Battle Arena Heroes Adventure','A MOBA with RPG elements.','Espirit Games’ Battle Arena Heroes Adventure is an RPG MOBA – that is to say, it’s a “purebred MOBA with the elements of an RPG”. This means that players will engage in the game in traditional 2D MOBA PvP style while at the same time experiencing a compelling story.\r\n\r\nThe game’s world is made up of a series of battle arenas, each a different region for players to explore. In the traditional RPG style, players can expect to face difficult bosses during their journey. This is in addition to taking on other teams in epic matches. Of course, other traditional components of the RPG experience are collecting rewards and leveling up your characters. Both of which players will be doing in Battle Arena Heroes Adventure. The leveling will be apparent as well, as characters evolve at levels 50 and 100.','Strategy','Web Browser','Espirit Games','Espirit Games','2018-03-19',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(160,42,'Spellsworn','A free-to-play arena battle game developed and published by Frogsong Studios AB. ','Spellsworn is a free-to-play arena battle game developed and published by Frogsong Studios AB. Inspired by popular PvP games such as League of Legends, Super Smash Bros., and Warlocks — a Warcraft 3 Mod, Spellsworn offers players the opportunity to compete in a battle of magic.\r\n\r\nCompete with up to seven other players in five round matches. As you play, earn currency that will allow you to buy better, even more powerful spells. Use these to build out your character in one of five disciplines — offensive, defensive, area, utility, and travel.\r\n\r\nCombat takes place in one of three arenas, each featuring their own unique challenges.','MOBA','Windows','Frogsong Studios AB','Frogsong Studios AB','2018-03-13','Windows 7 (64bit)','Dual core from Intel or AMD at 2.8 GHz','4 GB RAM','nVidia GeForce 8600/9600GT, ATI/AMD Radeon HD2600/3600','3 GB available space'),(161,43,'Z1 Battle Royale','A highly competitive free-to-play battle royale shooter.','Z1 Battle Royale (formerly H1Z1) is a highly competitive, free-to-play, single-elimination battle royale shooter. Each match starts with as many as 150 players parachuting into a 100 sq kilometer map. As with all battle royale’s players will need to collect the weapons and gear they’ll need to survive, once they’re on the map. They’ll also need to prepare for the map to shrink as a toxic gas creeps inward pushing all the players together.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the traditional battle royale, Z1 Battle Royale offers an Auto Royale mode, in which players in teams of four pile into cars and attempt to outdrive and outshoot the other teams in order to become the last team left. The teams will need to make a serious decision before starting though. Only one person can take the wheel, the other three have to man the guns.','Shooter','Windows','Daybreak Game Company','Daybreak Game Company','2018-02-28','Windows 7, 8, 8.1, 10 (64 bit only)','Intel i5 Quad-Core',' 6 GB RAM','nVidia GeForce GTX 280 series or higher','20 GB available space'),(162,44,'Tale Of Toast','A free-to-play open world MMO inspired by classic, core MMOs. ','Tale of Toast is a free-to-play open world MMO inspired by classic, core MMOs. Developed and published by Toasty Leaf AP, the game boasts an easy to learn playstyle, open world PvP, and more. Its content focuses on quality over quantity, offering players substantial quest chains rather than fluff quests.\r\n\r\nThe game offers players world dungeons as well as instanced group dungeons. All dungeons scale to the level of the players within and are procedurally generated.\r\n\r\nPlayers will be able to set their own play style, creating classes they’re happy with and learning the trade skills they want — rather than being forces into a specific focus.\r\n\r\nTransaction-wise the game offers players cosmetic items, pets, guild features, character renames and realm transfers. The devs promise no pay-to-win items will be available.','MMORPG','Windows','Toasty Leaf AB','Toasty Leaf AB','2018-02-23','Windows 7 (SP1+)/8.1/10 32bit','Intel Core i3',' 4 GB RAM','Intel HD Graphics 4000 or equivalent','4 GB available space'),(163,45,'SoulWorker','A free to play anime action MMO based on the popular anime of the same title. ','SoulWorker is a free to play anime action MMO based on the popular anime of the same title.\r\n\r\nThe game is a third-person action MMO designed in the same style as the anime. Players stake on the role of psychic teenagers with the ability to power special weapons called “Soul Workers,” which they will use to fight the monsters that have the vacant city of Cloudrealm. They won’t just be fighting, however, but also trying to discover what happened to the people who used to live in that city and possibly reverse it.\r\n\r\nPlayers get to choose between six different Soul Worker weapons — each aligning to a different class. These are: a chainsaw, a cannon, dual swords, dual pistols, a great sword, and a scythe. More powerful weapons can be obtained via crafting. There is also a limit-break style system — the Zenith attack — in which players who have accumulated enough Soul in combat are able to perform a powerful move related to their weapon. To make things even more interesting, two players can combine attacks into a more powerful one referred to as Coordination.\r\n\r\nVisually, the game is a 3D version of the anime it is inspired by. SoulWorker is slated for release later this year — although an exact date hasn’t been announced yet.','MMORPG','Windows','G・O・P','VALOFE','2018-02-27','Windows 7 32 bit','Pentium 4 dual core','2 GB RAM','Nvidia GeForce 7600 GS','4 GB available space'),(164,47,'Bombtag','A free-to-play multiplayer Bomberman-inspired game.','Bombtag is a free-to-play multiplayer Bomberman-inspired game. Game rounds support up to 8 players and last just a few minutes, allowing for quick matches when you only have a little time.\r\n\r\nSimilar to the game that inspired it, Bombtag is chaotic and fast-pasted. Players drop bombs, blow up crates — and their enemies, and collect powerups, all while trying to avoid being blown up themselves. Gameplay is a bit more in depth than just dropping bombs and waiting for them to blow. Players can slide into them to kick them away from themselves and into their enemies.\r\n\r\nThere are two game modes — free for all and teams and six maps to play them on. Players can customize their characters with over 800 pieces of cosmetic items. The game also offers the standard social features — friends list and chat, as well as a competitive rank system and leader board.','Strategy','Windows','David Schneider','David Schneider','2018-02-12','Windows XP, Vista, 7, 8, 10','Dual Core 3.0 GHz','2 GB','Intedl HD Graphics 4000 or equivalent','600 MB'),(165,48,'Ironsight','A free-to-play futuristic shooter published by Aeria Games. ','Ironsight is a free-to-play futuristic shooter published by Aeria Games. Set in the year 2025, the game places players in the roles of soldiers fighting over the last natural resources on Earth. All nuclear power plants on the Atlantic coast were wiped out following a Megatsunami in 2023, causing radioactive spills. The west has lost control over the Middle East and its resources, and as a result the US and Europe have teamed up to fight the Engergy Development Enterprise Network (EDEN) to regain control once again.\r\n\r\nIronsight offers players more than 100 original weapons to choose from, allowing for a high degree of character customization and specialization. The game features drones and mechs that can be used in strategic operations, as well as a variety of maps and game modes. The modes come in both PvP and PvE variety and include everything from Secure Point PvP to a selection of PvP and PvE Deathmatch options.','Shooter','Windows','WipleGames Inc.','WipleGames Inc.','2018-02-01','Windows 7','Intel Core 2 Duo E7500','2 GB','NVIDIA GeForce 6900 GT','8 GB'),(166,49,'Dead Maze','A free-to-play 2D isometric MMO full of zombies. ','Dead Maze is a free-to-play 2D isometric MMO full of zombies. In order to survive the undead apocalypse, players will need to work together, gather resources, and craft supplies needed to keep themselves alive.\r\n\r\nUnlike most zombie games, Dead maze requires players to restore civilization, starting with improving their own camps. Once a camp is established, players can build and furnish their own home, planting seeds, breeding animals, and more.\r\n\r\nOf course, they will need to fight the undead. Luckily, there are over 500 weapons to do that with. They’ll also need to be aware of their health and do their best to manage it.','MMORPG','Windows','801','801','2018-02-13','Windows 7','2 GHz','1 GB','?','250 MB available space'),(167,22,'Wild Terra Online','A medieval sandbox MMO designed with core players in mind. ','Wild Terra Online is a medieval sandbox MMO designed with hardcore players in mind. The game, developed and published by Juvty Worlds Developers Team, is a mix of survival featuring hunting and taming, building, crafting and trading, and combat.\r\n\r\nAs with most survival-type games, players will need to pay attention to not only external dangers, but manage both exhaustion and hunger. Luckily, there’s an extended culinary system.\r\n\r\nThere’s also an in depth creature system that allows for the hunting, catching, and taming of wild animals. Any large animal can be used as a mount.\r\n\r\nAS for building, the game gives players more than 150 buildings to work with, ranging from a campfire to full castles. There are also furnaces, smithies, mills, and more.\r\n\r\nWild Terra is available to download via Steam.\r\n\r\n','MMORPG','Windows','Juvty Worlds Ltd.','Juvty Worlds Ltd.','2017-12-18','Windows XP/Vista/7/8/10','2.2 GHz or higher','4 GB RAM','512 MB, WebGL support','600 MB available space'),(168,51,'Global Adventures','A free-to-play MMORPG developed by PixelSoft and Published by SubaGames. ','Global Adventures is a free-to-play MMORPG developed by PixelSoft and Published by SubaGames. A game with a contemporary — somewhat real-world — setting, Global Adventures casts players in teh role of a newly recruited agent for the Treasure Hunters Association. The agent’s first task will be to explore Mayan Ruins… a task that doesn’t go quite as planned as there are other groups who will get in your way. These groups include the Black Flag Gang, the Shinobi Cabal a ninja group who’d really like their own undead army, and a secret order known as the Priory. Along the way, you’ll fight Vampires, zombies, and more while traveling all around the world.\r\n\r\nThe game offers players 5 different classes to choose from as well as both solo and co-op content. Players can explore 5 of the world’s contienents and even build their own castles. The game features a TF2-ish art style and plenty of weapons and gear to customize playable characters with.','MMORPG','Windows','SubaGames','PixelSoft','2017-12-29','XP/Vista/7/8/10','Intel/AMD Dual Core 2.4g','3 GB','Nvidia GT 630 / ATI HD6570 / InterHD5200','10 GB'),(169,52,'Closers','A free-to-play episodic anime beat-em-up developed \r\nby Naddic Games and published by \r\nEn Masse Entertainment. ','Closers is a free-to-play episodic anime beat-’em-up developed by Naddic Games and published by En Masse Entertainment. It features five playable characters (4 classes), and a very anime storyline in which aliens are spilling through portals into New Seoul.\r\n\r\nPlayers can take on the role a combat genius, a leader, a martial artist, a young boy with support skills, or a grizzled veteran with a troubled past. These characters can be developed by upgrading skills and weapons as well as unlocking new powers.\r\n\r\nThe game revolves around the usage of skills, featuring basic fighter game movement such as dash, jump, and dash-jump combos. Players will travel around new Seoul fighting the invading aliens and completing missions assigned by NPC. All PvE gameplay is instance based.\r\n\r\nClosers also offers a PvP mode similar to MOBA gameplay. It allows players to play as either a Dimensional (alien) or a Closer in an attempt to destroy the other team’s tower while defending their own.','MMORPG','Windows','En Masse Entertainment','Naddic Games','2017-12-19','Windows XP','Intel Dual Core 2.0 GHz','2 GB','Nvidia GeForce 7600 GT','5 GB'),(170,322,'La Tale Evolved','A 2D side-scrolling fantasy MMORPG with anime-inspired graphics.','La Tale is a 2D side-scrolling fantasy MMORPG with anime-inspired graphics, published by OGPlant. Choose from multiple unique classes to adventure out in the 2D world, raise pets with unique skills, enter the Coliseum to battle tons of monsters, or participate in the PvP.\r\n\r\nChoose from six of the different classes that La Tale has to offer. Each of the classes has two different unique class advancements that you get to choose from later on in the game. Journey into the Coliseum where hordes of monsters will come at you non-stop and you have to continuously beat them and level up your character to progress in them game. Or you can participate in PvP inside the Coliseum and battle for the right to call yourself the best.\r\n\r\nCustomization is a big deal in La Tale, you can customize how your character looks by what they wear, what weapons they are carrying around, their skin tone, hair color, and even more as you play through La Tale. People that are already playing the game say that the in-game cash shop is even balanced so that you can’t pay to win and you can buy even more stuff to customize your character with.','MMORPG','Windows','Papaya Play','Actoz Soft','2017-11-17','Windows XP/ Vista / 7 / 8 ','Pentium 4 2.0 GHZ','1 GB','GeForce4 MX, ATI RADEON 9000 ','2 GB'),(171,120,'Luna Online: Reborn','A free-to-play, anime themed fantasy MMORPG and a remake of the previous Luna MMO! ','Luna Online: Reborn is a free-to-play fantasy MMORPG developed and published by SuBa Games. A remake of the previous Luna MMO, LO:R takes everything that players loved about the original game and adds more. Done in a 3D anime art style, it takes place on the world of BlueLand — a place where humans and elves work together to fight an evil race called the Majin.\r\n\r\nThis upgraded version of Luna Online was developed based on player feedback from the original game — designed to adjust or remove content that players felt negatively about. The developers didn’t just take away, however. They’ve added new Realm vs Realm and real time ranking systems to the game.\r\n\r\nLO:R features three playable races: Human, Elf, and Majin. It also boasts a new matchmaking system to help players find their in-game love, weekly guild sieges, an in depth housing system with a barn and livestock, and much more.','MMORPG','Windows','Suba Games','Suba Games','2017-10-17','Windows 7/8/10','Intel P4 1.4GHz','512MB ',' nVidia GeForce 2 series','2 GB'),(172,58,'The Ultimatest Battle','A free-to-play 2D platform game that pits two teams of players against each other in a variety of modes. ','The Ultimatest Battle is a free-to-play 2D plaform game that pits two teams of players against each other in a variety of modes. The game features real-time combat and an (almost) completely destructible environment.\r\n\r\nPlayers of Ultimatest Battle play as characters called “Nubs”. Nubs come in a variety of classes, each with their own attributes. They’re customizable — both visually and gameplay wise using items earned in game. Nubs are heavily armed and can use a variety of weapons based on their class. There are six classes to chose from including Soldier, Viking, and even Miner.\r\n\r\nGame modes include a variety of scenarios, including zero-gravity Moon battles, ControlPoint, SaveThePrincess, and Versus Boss.','Fighting','Windows','Ediogames','Ediogames','2017-09-12','Window 7','Intel core duo','1 GB','Intel HD 4000','300 MB'),(173,59,'Insidia','A free-to-play tactical, turn-based dueling game developed and published by Bad Seed. ','Insidia is a free-to-play tactical, turn-based dueling game developed and published by Bad Seed. Players build a team of four champions and compete against one another in (sort-of) turn-based combat. Unlike other turn-based games, Insidia features simultaneous turns, meaning both players take their turns at the same time and watch them play out. Because of this, players can knock out a match in less than 15 minutes.\r\n\r\nThe team-building feature allows players to blend their champions’ abilities in order to create combos. And while there are four champion types on a team, there is a larger variety to choose from, making each team unique.\r\n\r\nAs for the maps themselves, the game does not offer simple deathmatches, but requires players to capture and control critical areas of the map while they destroy the opponent base.','Strategy','Windows','Bad Seed','Bad Seed','2017-09-07','Windows 7 64 Bit','Dual-Core 2.0','4 GB','DirectX 10','2 GB'),(174,30,'Quake Champions','Quake Champions is a callback to the early days of the Quake IP, featuring the fast-paced action that made the IP popular over two decades ago. ','Quake Champions is a callback to the early days of the Quake IP, featuring the fast-paced action that made the IP popular over two decades ago. The game combines the lore of the original Quake with multiplayer elements found in Quake III Arena.\r\n\r\nPlayers play as warriors, each bearing different attributes and abilities. There are more than ten champions to choose from, giving players a wide variety of play styles to choose from. In addition, players can modify their gameplay by swapping out weapons. Fan favorites such as the Rocket Launcher and Railgun return. New weapons have been created as well.\r\n\r\nQuake Champions also includes several popular game modes: Deathmatch, 1v1 Duel, and Team Deathmatch, as well as a new team-based mode: Sacrifice.\r\n\r\n','Shooter','Windows','Bethesda Softworks','id Software','2017-08-22','Windows 7 and later','AMD Phenom II X4-945 / Intel Core 2 Quad 6600','8 GB RAM','AMD R7 240 GB / Nvidia GT 730 2GB / Intel HD 530','20 GB available space'),(175,354,'Gods Origin Online','A free-to-play browser-based RPG from VivaGames in which players take on the role of human summoners that call deities from the Astral Realm back in time. ','Gods Origin Online is a free-to-play browser-based RPG from VivaGames in which players take on the role of human summoners that call deities from the Astral Realm back in time to before Ragnarok in order to save them from their fates. The game only offers players two classes to chose from: Swordsman and Mage. Each has their own specialties. That said, the developer does appear to plan the addition of more classes as time goes on.\r\n\r\nPlayers can acquire familiars in Gods Origin. These are an important part of the game and each familiar has their own ultimate and can be leveled up in order to increase talents and skills.\r\n\r\nAs with most online MMOs, players will have access to a variety of social features, including a friends list, guild creation, and more.','MMORPG','Web Browser','VivaGame','VivaGame','2017-08-29',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(176,61,'Black Squad','A free-to-play military FPS developed by NS STUDIO and published by NEOWIZ.','Black Squad is a free-to-play military FPS developed by NS STUDIO and published by NEOWIZ. It is built using Unreal Engine 3 and boasts realistic graphics.\r\n\r\nThe game offers players 10 different modes to choose from. These range from classic to massive multi-play modes. Team vs team modes include 5v5, 8v8, 10v10 and 16v16. The 16v16 mode allows players to call for airstrike and artillery support.\r\n\r\nPlayers will also be able to choose from a variety of modern firearms and over 20 maps.','Shooter','Windows','NEOWIZ','NS Studio','2017-07-28','Windows 7 64bit','Core2 Duo 2.4 / AMD Phenom X4 820','4 GB RAM','NVIDIA GEFORCE 8600 OR GT630 / RADEON HD 6750','7 GB available space'),(177,64,'Secret World Legends','A free-to-play reboot of The Secret World. ','Secret World Legends is a free-to-play reboot of The Secret World. Developed by Funcom, Secret World Legends takes the story aspect of TSW and completely reworked combat, leveling, skills and more. While the focus of the game is still the narrative, thew new action combat and other features are designed to appeal to a broader audience than the original game.\r\n\r\nThe game takes players into a dark and mysterious world filled with conspiricies, magic, and creatures of legend. In the beginning it’s a little Stephen King meets H.P. Lovecraft. There are zombies, Cthuhlu-esque sea creatures, cults, mummies, zombies, and more.\r\n\r\nThe player takes on the role of super powered foot soldier working for one of three groups; the Illuminati, the Templar, or the Dragons. They’ll travel to real-world locations like New York, London, Seoul, and somewhat real places in coastal Maine, Egypt, Transylvania, and more.','MMORPG','Windows','Funcom','Funcom','2017-07-31','Windows XP/Vista/7','2.6 GHZ Intel Core 2 DUO or equivalent AMD CPU','2 GB for Windows XP/3GB for Vista and 7','nVidia 8800 series 512 VRAM / Radeon HD3850 512MB','?'),(178,63,'Argo','A tactical first-person shooter from the Arma 3 developer.','Argo is a free-to-play “hardcore tactical first-person shooter” from Arma 3 developer and publisher Bohemia Interactive. Billed as a total conversion of Arma 3, the game allows players to take on the role of mercenaries contracted by one of two rival factions in an updated version of the Arma Malden island map\r\n\r\nPlayers can choose one of three game modes to compete in — all of which utilize 5-man teams. The first is “Clash”, which has two teams fighting over territory. “Link” requires players to capture a chain of points before the other side can, and ‘Raid’ sends one team in search of a data terminal while the opposite team defends the terminal’s three potential locations.\r\n\r\nPlayers can also participate in a 10-man combat patrol co-op wherein they fight against the AI.\r\n\r\nA bonus feature of the game is that it allows players to make use of a 3D scenario editor to create their own playable missions. The editor features an intuitive interface that allows players to place AI, set triggers, and assign waypoints easily.','Shooter','Windows','Bohemia Interactive','Bohemia Interactive','2017-06-22','Windows 7 SP1 And Up',' Intel Dual-Core 2.4 GHZ or AMD Dual-Core Athlon 2.5 GHz','4 GB','NVIDIA GeFeorce 9800GT / AMD Radeon HD 5670','20 GB'),(179,65,'Pixel Worlds','A free-to-play, side-scroller MMO sandbox game developed and published by Kukouri Mobile Entertainment. ','Pixel Worlds is a free-to-play, side-scroller MMO sandbox game developed and published by Kukouri Mobile Entertainment. The game is cross-platform and available not only on PC, but also OSX, iOS and Android.\r\n\r\nIn Pixel Worlds, player can build and create any number of worlds, mine, craft, farm, and participate in a player run economy. They can build their own worlds or play in those created by their friends.. There are also a variety of Live Events that take place every few weeks.','MMORPG','Windows','Kukouri Mobile Entertainment ','Kukouri Mobile Entertainment ','2017-06-09','Windows 7 or later','Intel Core 2 Duo 1.8 GHz or AMD X2 64 2.0 Ghz','2 GB RAM','256 MB HD 2600 or better \\ 256 MB Nvidia 7900 or better','300 MB available space'),(180,55,'Deceit','A free-to-play multiplayer first-person shooter set \r\nin an asylum! ','Deceit is a free-to-play multiplayer first-person shooter set in an asylum. Players are part of a group, a third of which has been infected with a virus. The ultimate goal is to get the hell out, but in order to do that players will need to find allies and complete objectives while managing avoid the infected who transform into a nightmare form.\r\n\r\nAs players progress and make decisions that will allow them to achieve their objectives, they will gain information that informs them as to what team they’re on. At the same time, players will need to contend with blackout periods that allow the infected to transform, becoming faster, stronger, and equipped with night vision.\r\n\r\nThe game features fast paced gameplay, and insane combat in which players will need to behave strategically in order to survive.','Shooter','Windows','Automaton','Automaton','2017-05-03','Window 7 (64 Bit)','Intel Core i3 / AMD Ryzen 3','4 GB','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 650 Ti / AMD Radeon HD 7850','10 GB'),(181,66,'Gwent: The Witcher Card Game','A free-to-play card game based on CD Projekt Red\'s popular Witcher franchise. ','Gwent is a free-to-play card game for PC and XBox One, based on CD Projekt Red’s popular Witcher franchise. The game features both a multi-player and single-player mode with adventures, skirmishes and a player vs. AI mode. All of this is developed by the same team behind The Witcher III: Wild Hunt.\r\n\r\nIn fact, the core game is based on the card game featured in Wild Hunt, but with several new additions. The stand alone card game features new card art, voice overs and skills. There is even a competitive PvP mode built completely from scratch for Gwent.\r\n\r\nAs with any card game, players will be able to choose a deck type (or faction), build it out, and go into battle against other players. Gwent features a gameboard with a battlefield built of three rows, melee, ranged, and siege. Each row can be populated with cards of varying stats. A game is won when a player takes two out of three rounds.','Card Game','Windows','CD Projekt Red','CD Projekt Red','2017-05-24',' Windows 7/8/8.1/10 (64 bit)','Intel Celeron G1820 | AMD A4-7300','2 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GT 710 or GeForce GT 7900 | AMD Radeon R5 330 or Radeon HD 4650','4.5 GB available space'),(182,67,'Awesomenauts','A 3v3 2D battle arena Developed by Ronimo games.','Awesomenauts is a 3v3 2D battle arena Developed by Ronimo games. Originally launched as a pay-to-play game, the PC version of AwesomeNauts eventually converted to free-to-play. Players take on the role of intergalactic mercenaries (known as Awesomenauts).\r\n\r\nThe game boasts more than 20 Awesomnauts, each with unique skill sets. It incorporates elements from both 2D and Fighting games. There are multiple modes of play. However, its primary mode is the 3v3 match, in which each team attempts to destroy the other’s Solar Collector. Players fight their way through other players, drones, and turrets in order to do this.\r\n\r\nAwesomenauts’ deafult mode is ranked play, featuring 9 different ranks which players can be matched in. Those who finish a season in top ranking will earn rewards. During ranked play, no two players on a team can use the same character. The game’s other available modes allow for more varied play but do count toward ranking and the eventual reward. These modes include skirmishes and round-robin.\r\n\r\nThere is also a meta-game linked to player profiles. Each player will earn experience for playing matches and can purchase character improvements based on those levels. When a player reaches max level they can opt to use the prestige system and return to the lowest level in exchange for a badge.','MOBA','Windows','Ronimo Games','Ronimo Games','2017-05-24','Windows 7, 8, or 10','Any processor with 2 cores','2 GB','AMD or NVIDIA with at least 512 MB','3.5 GB'),(183,70,'Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop','A free-to-play top-down tactical co-op expansion on the Alien swarm game and Source SDK.','Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop is a free-to-play top-down tactical co-op expansion on the Alien swarm game and Source SDK developed by a group of designers at Valve who were hired from the MOD community. Reactive drop no longer grants players access to the Source SDK, however it does offer expanded co-op, with up to 8 players, Steam Workshop support, four PvP modes, a single player mode, and new aliens, weapons, achievements and more.\r\n\r\nThe game sends players on a bug hunt and is a blend of co-op and squad level gameplay. Players team up with friends to form a squad made of IAF Marine classes and use a selection of unlockable weapons featuring a wide variety of loadout configurations to battle aliens in an offworld colony.\r\n\r\nReactive Drop is spectator friendly and features leaderboards as well as the ability for spectators to see hacking minigames and mouse movements in real time. It is available via Steam.','Shooter','Windows','Reactive Drop','Reactive Drop','2017-04-20','Windows XP or above','Pentium 4 3.0GHz','2 GB','DirectX 9 compatible card with 128 MB, Shader model 2.0, ATI X800, NVidia 6600 or better','10 GB'),(184,71,'Catan Universe','A free-to-play strategy game based on the classic board and card games. ','Catan Universe is a free-to-play strategy game based on the classic board and card games. Players race to settle Catan, building road and towns, as well as a thriving trade.\r\n\r\nThe game allows players to compete in duels against players around the world, offering 1v1v1 matches. Players can play the basic board in multiplayers as well as the introductory game, Catan — The Duel for free. Other modes are available as in-app purchases.\r\n\r\nBasic online features are available. Players can create their own avatar, engage in community functions such as chat, guilds, and more. The game can be played via client or in a browser, whichever works for the player.','Card Game','Windows','United Soft Media','Exozet','2017-04-25',' Windows 7 32-big','1.5 Ghz Dual-Core Intel Core i5','2 GB','Open GL 3.1+ Compliant ','1 GB'),(185,72,'Krosmaga','A free-to-play CCG/tower defense hybrid developed \r\nby Ankama Studio and published by \r\nAnkama Games. ','Kosmaga is a free-to-play CCG/tower defense hybrid developed by Ankama Studio and published by Ankama Games.  The game offers players fun in short, strategy-filled bursts… and features characters from both Dofus and Wakfu as controllable heroes.\r\n\r\nPlayers will take on the roll of a god, and control heroes on a battlefield using decks of cards. These decks can either be pre-made or created by the player. There are hundreds of cards available to build these decks with.\r\n\r\nThe game features PvP battles in which players can challenge others, as well as adventures that can be taken on in a single player mode. Cards are tied to players’ Ankama accounts, making it possible for players to access them on any device.','Card Game','Windows','Ankama Games','Ankama Studio','2017-04-12','Windows 7 or higher','Intel Pentium D or AMD Athalon 64X2','2 GB Ram','NVIDIA GeForce 6800 or ATI Radeon X1600 Pro','3GB'),(186,355,'Chronicles of Eidola','A free-to-play 3D Browser RPG from AMZGame.','Chronicles of Eidola is a free-to-play turn-based RPG from AMZGame. The game places players in the role of an avenger who works with a wide variety of characters to get things done. The game offers several options in how to play, including PvE, PvP and PvF (or Player vs Function). It boasts 3D graphics enabled by the new Flash stage 3D engine and promises a unique gaming experience.\r\n\r\nPvE-wise, Chronicles of Eidola offers Guild Battles as well as the “Gauntlet” which allows players to challenge a never-ending stream of enemies to see how far they can go. On the PvP end of things, players can participate in Arena battles with the winners receiving rewards. Finally, PvF offers players who are looking for something a bit more relaxing a variety of mini-game-type activities to partake in.\r\n\r\nChronicle of Eidola can be played in-browser via the game’s official site.','MMORPG','Web Browser','AMZ Games','AMZ Games','2017-04-10',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(187,77,'Revelation Online','A free-to-play fantasy MMO developed by NetEase and published by My.com. ','Revelation Online is a free-to-play fantasy MMO developed by NetEase and published by My.com.\r\n\r\nA game featuring flight, Revelation Online offers players a vast world to explore. There are ten provinces and three Great Cities in the game’s world. Each city boasts a castle of its own and the rest of the world is littered with castles — including some in the sky and others buried in the ocean.\r\n\r\nThe game boasts a variety of content available for both single and group play. There are 5 – 10 player dungeons, 20 player raids, and a variety of world bosses. PvPers also have several different kinds of content to take part in including castle sieges, arena, aerial combat, open world PvP, and 10 different PvP maps to battle it out in.\r\n\r\nPlayers have 6 different classes to choose from; Gunslinger, Blademaster, Spiritshaper, Vanguard, Swordmage, and Occultist. To further customize gameplay, players can also choose between three different control styles, Tab-Target, Click-to-Move and Free Aiming.','MMORPG','Windows','My.com','NetEase','2017-03-06','Windows XP','Intel Pentium dual-core 2.4 GHZ','2GB','Geforce 9500GT / GT610 or Intel HD4000 ','?'),(188,87,'MU Legend','A free-to-play MMORPG developed by Webzen and the followup to MU Online. ','MU Legend is a free-to-play MMORPG developed by Webzen and the followup to MU Online. A fantasy hack ‘n’ slash game, MU Legend is based on Unreal Engine 3 and shares features from its predecessor, such as the UI and controls.\r\n\r\nThere are four playable character types available for play: Dark Lord, Whisperer, Blader, and War Mage. Dark Lords are former knights who gave up their humanity in exchange for power, making them capable of only cold reasoning. Whisperers harness the energy of nature and excel at stealth. Bladers were created as protectors and are brutal warriors fighting as representatives of the lower class. War Mages are exiles, removed from society after their abilities became too powerful.\r\n\r\nThe game offers a variety of content for players from several dungeons to a guild system and even an arena.','MMORPG','Windows','VALOFE','VALOFE','2017-03-23','WinXP SP3','Intel Quad Core/AMD Phenom II X4 and above','3 GB','GeForce 8800GT / Radeon HD4850 and above','25 GB'),(189,421,'Therian Saga','A browser-based sandbox MMORPG with a complex crafting system.','Therian Saga is a free to play browser-based sandbox MMORPG with strategy elements where players create a unique character to explore, hunt, train, and craft.\r\n\r\nTherian Saga is not your typical role-playing game, this browser MMORPG, published by Gameforge AG, offers turn-based combat, a complex crafting system, a task-based queue system and Dungeons and Dragons-inspired dungeon crawling. Though the game has a low player based and can sometimes be slow-paced, one of the game’s redeeming qualities is its detailed customization. Players can choose from a myriad of skills and various aesthetic choices to contrive their own unique character to progress through the game with.\r\n\r\nAdditionally, players can queue up certain tasks for their avatar, which they will complete over time to meet the requirements of various game objectives.','MMORPG','Windows, Web Browser','Gameforge','Virtys','2017-03-27',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(190,69,'Cabals: Card Blitz','A free-to-play game developed by Kyy Games and published by BISBOG SA. ','Cabals: Card Blitz is a free-to-play game developed by Kyy Games and published by BISBOG SA. The strategy card game offers players unique features in addition to the familiar CCG gameplay style. These include:\r\n\r\n    Cards are drawn automatically and randomly during battle\r\n    Players can battle against offline opponents\r\n    Players can choose their own path through a non-linear PvE map\r\n    Two different cards can be fused to produce an entirely new card\r\n\r\nIn addition to the above features, the game also offers a speed slider during battle, to allow the players to determine how fast or slow the game can be. With the slider set at Max, a game can take as little as 30 seconds to play.\r\n\r\nLike other CCGs, Cabals offers single and multi-player modes, with the single player mode giving players the opportunity to earn daily rewards in the form of gold, new cards and gems. The PvP mode is designed to guarantee players opponents without waiting in queue by letting them play against those offline.\r\n\r\nThe game is available now on Steam — as well as mobile devices.','Card Game','Windows','BISBOG SA','Kyy Games','2017-02-08','Windows XP SP2+','2.33 GHz or faster x86-compatible processor, Intel Atom 1.6GHz or faster for netbooks','512 MB','128 MB DirectX 9.0c compatible video card','200 MB'),(191,82,'Line of Sight','Free FPS game described as \"Bioshock meets Call of Duty\"! ','Line of Sight is a free-to-play online FPS published by BlackSpot Entertainment. Described as “Bioshock meets Call of Duty,” the game has a modern military setting in a twisted universe.\r\n\r\nLike Bioshock, the game features super human abilities. It also offers players a pure military FPS experience and a “Classic Mode” in which players can play the game like any traditional online FPS.\r\n\r\nFor more serious — or Pro players — the game features class ranking, clan and league systems, and features needed for eSports play.','Shooter','Windows','BlackSpot Entertainment','BlackSpot Entertainment','2017-01-31','Windows 7','Dual Core 2.0GHz from Intel or AMD 2.0GHz','2 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce 8600/9600GT, ATI/AMD Radeon HD2600/3600','3 GB available space'),(192,343,'Dragon Awaken','A free-to-play, browser-based fantasy RPG developed \r\nby Game Hollywood and published by \r\nProficient City.','Dragon Awaken is a free-to-play, browser-based fantasy RPG developed by Game Hollywood and published by Proficient City. Players take on the roll of a warrior, who through an attack on a dragon’s lair ends up possessing the power of the dragon and becoming a dragon knight.\r\n\r\nThe story-centric game offers a diverse selection of place for players to explore, filled with characters from mythology and real-world history. To aid in creating an immersive world, the developers created a unique dungeon series that allows players to explore freely by unlocking each of them.\r\n\r\nDragon Awaken offers a variety of new features, including a semi-turn based battle system, the “Astro System” — which allows players to adjust their stats, and mounts with modifiable stats. Players can switch skills as needed and are able to recruit heroes in battle.\r\n\r\nThe game does offer a sub-mode — VIP. This allows players go acquire items more quickly and earn XP bonuses. They also get a free vault, access to unique fashions and mounts, and more.','MMORPG','Web Browser','Proficient city','Game Hollywood','2017-01-03',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(193,85,'Infestation: The New Z','A re-work of the open world zombie shooter game Infestation: Survivor Stories (or as it was formerly known \"The War Z\").','Infestation: The New Z is a re-work of the open world zombie shooter game Infestation: Survivor Stories (or as it was formerly known “The War Z”).Developed by Fredaikis AB and published by OP Productions LLC, the game drops players into a world where they must survive by scavenging for the things they need and either teaming up with or fighting against other players while avoiding the dangers all around them.\r\n\r\nThe New Z features different game modes, a lounge where players can trade loot, warm-up servers to get used to the game before hopping into PvP. For the more competitive players, there is a Battle Royale mode. The objective is to be the last man standing.\r\n\r\nAdding to the open world aspect of the game is the ability to drive around in cars, to create clans, and more.','Shooter','Windows','OP Productions LLC','Fredaikis AB','2016-11-22','Windows 7','AMD A8 3870 3, 6 Ghz or Intel Core i3 2100 3.1Ghz ','2 GB','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 465 / ATI Radeon TM HD 6870','10 GB'),(194,92,'One Tower','A unique 1v1 MOBA known as a \"micro-moba\" developed and published by SkyReacher following a successful Kickstarter. ','One Tower is a unique 1v1 MOBA — known as a “micro-moba” — developed and published by SkyReacher following a successful Kickstarter. The game pits two players against each other in a small-scale version of MOBA arenas with a single lane and offshoot areas where monsters wait to be downed by either player.\r\n\r\nThe monsters are an important aspect of the game as they can help a player accelerate gold acquisition, which is needed to generate minions. Players have full control over their minions waves, being able to purchase specific minions with gold and chose their position in the wave. Not all gold is accumulated from monster kills, player will automatically receive gold over a certain period of time. Gold is also earned via killing the enemy and their minions.\r\n\r\nPlayers will also find elements of RTS and RPG games have been added to One Tower, to make for a more interesting 1v1 experience. The ultimate goal, like any MOBA, is for each player to protect the structure at their end of the lane while destroying the enemy’s.\r\n\r\nOne Tower is available to play via Steam.','MOBA','Windows','SkyReacher Entertainment','SkyReacher Entertainment','2016-11-11',' Windows 7 or higher (64-bit)','Intel Core i3-4170 or AMD FX-8120','2 GB','DX11 Compatible GeForce GTX 460 1GB or AMD HD 6850 1GB','5 GB'),(195,88,'Shadowverse','A free-to-play strategic CCG developed and published by Cygamesm the creators of Rage of Bahamut and Granblu Fantasy. ','Shadowverse is a free-to-play strategic CCG developed and published by Cygamesm the creators of Rage of Bahamut and Granblu Fantasy. Available on Steam, iOS and Android, Shadowverse features over 400 cards from which to build customized decks.\r\n\r\nThe game offers single and multiplayer content with tactical gameplay. There are three kinds of cards, followers, spells, and amulets. Followers are the most active in battle, while spells offer an effect that activates once, and amulet cards support you in battle.','Card Game','Windows','Cygames, Inc.','Cygames, Inc.','2016-10-28','Windows 7','Intel Core 2 Duo 2.4 GHz or AMD A4-7300','2 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce 7600GT or AMD Radeon HD 84700','2 GB'),(196,89,'AdventureQuest 3D','A free to play cross-platform MMORPG from the creators of the original 2D RPG game.','AdventureQuest 3D (AQ3D) is a free to play cross-platform fantasy MMORPG with colorful cartoony graphics from the creators of the original 2D RPG Flash game! AdventureQuest was created by the game’s original designers and is scheduled to come out in 4th Quarter 2016.\r\n\r\nJourney through a colorful persistent world filled with magic, monsters, vampires, werewolves, pirates, ninjas, dragons and more with graphics that will appeal to kids and adults. Unlike traditional MMORPGs, which limit players to a single class, AdventureQuest 3D allows players to switch between any of the game’s classes upon unlocking them. So don’t forget to visit the Hall of Trainers where you can unlock new classes.\r\n\r\nPlay with people around the world in co-op, solo mode or PVP. You can even play with friends who are not at your level, the “side-kicking” feature will boost your friend’s level so they can play with you in dangerous places. AdventureQuest 3D was developed by Artix Entertainment, the creators of AdventureQuest, DragonFable, MechQuest, and AQWorlds. You can access the world of AQ3D from your phone, tablet, and PC.','MMORPG','Windows','Artix Entertainment','Artix Entertainment','2016-10-19','Windows 7','Dual Core 1.8GHZ or Single Core 3.0GHZ','1 GB RAM','512 MB','500 MB available space'),(197,93,'Riding Club Championships','An online competitive horse riding game inspired by traditional equestrian disciplines. ','Riding Club Championships is an online competitive horse riding game inspired by traditional equestrian disciplines. As with real world riding championships, players will participate in activities like show jumping, barrel racing, pole bending, and more.\r\n\r\nThe game allows players to play alone or with others, even competing in a weekly ranked tournament. There is also an option to create custom courses and share them with others\r\n\r\nThe game also boasts a horse RPG system, grooming, a selection of horses and gear, and a paddock mode. Of course, there are also standard MMO features such as a quest system, and multiple chat rooms.\r\n\r\nRiding Club Championships can be downloaded via Steam.','Racing','Windows','Artplant','Artplant','2016-09-27','Windows Vista, 7, 8, and 10','Dual Core CPU 2.0 GHz ','1 GB','NVidia GeForce 8800 GT or better','1 GB'),(198,94,'Battlerite','A free-to-play team arena brawler developed by Stunlock Studios. Players play as one of several available champions on teams in 2v2 or 3v3 matches. ','Battlerite is a free-to-play team arena brawler developed by Stunlock Studios. Players play as one of several available champions — with more in development — on teams in 2v2 or 3v3 matches.\r\n\r\nThe game features three arenas, Mount Araz — built on a dragon graveyard at the edge of cape Kaal, Orman Temple — built in the garden of an abandoned temple, and Sky Ring — built on a floating island in the desert kingdom of Trolobe.\r\n\r\nPlayers can compete via the game’s ranking system and earn their chance to compete in community tournaments. There is also a variety of rewards to be earned via quests. Rewards come in the form of chests containing cosmetics that can be used to customize outfits, weapons, victory stances and more.\r\n\r\nFeatures unique to the game include battlerites that players can choose from as part of strategically developing their play style to match the gameplay, as well as top-down bullet-time, giving players a second look at their gameplay choices.\r\n\r\nBattlerite is available to play via Steam.','MOBA','Windows','Stunlock Studios','Stunlock Studios','2016-09-21','Window 7 or later','Dual core from Intel or AMD at 2.8 GHz','2 GB','Intel HD 3000','1500 MB'),(199,99,'Star Crusade','A free-to-play sci-fi themed collectable card game developed and published by ZiMAD inc. ','Star Crusade: War for the Expanse is a free-to-play sci-fi themed collectable card game developed and published by ZiMAD inc. Players command one of six factions fighting for control of a highly contested sector of space. These factions range in type from cybernetically enhanced to zealots to battle hardened. Some feature large mercenary armies while others prefer massive weapons.\r\n\r\nUnlike a lot of CCG’s, Star Crusade allows players to customize their deck size — with over 400 cards to build from. The game features 3 modes: Casual, Raid, and Ranked. It also offers a variety of missions for players and can be played anywhere — both on PC and mobile devices.\r\n\r\nRaids are a special type of gameplay that does not take player rank into account. During gameplay in this mode, players can not use a prepared deck and maps will be random.\r\n\r\nThe game features 4 different card types: Units — entity cards that will remain in play until they are destroyed, Tactics — one off cards capable of changing the flow of the battle in one move, Ciphers — cards that effect an enemy without them getting to see them beforehand, and Equipment — cards used directly by the commander (player) to directly engage in the battle. The equipment cards can consist of weapons or enhancements.\r\n\r\nWhile the base game is free to play, there are a variety of content packs available to supplement it. These range in price from $20 to $50 and can be purchased for all available platforms.','Card Game','Windows','ZiMAD, Inc.','ZiMAD, Inc.','2016-09-08',' Windows XP, Vista, 7, 9','Intel Pentium D or AMD Athlon 64 X2','2 GB','NVIDIA GeForce 6800 or ATI Radeon X1600','3 GB'),(200,344,'Omega Zodiac','A Greek and Norse mythology based free-to-play action MMO developed and published by Proficient City and Game Hollywood.','Omega Zodiac is a Greek and Norse mythology based free-to-play action MMO developed and published by Proficient City and Game Hollywood. This browser-based game features guild battles and world bosses while giving players one of three classes to play as. Players can take the role of the knight — and up-close and personal melee class, the archer, and the arcane mage.\r\n\r\nEach boast their own abilities — nine combo skills each, as well as 5 constellations per character with their own set of skills. Players can also unlock Sacred Sets of armor by collecting Star Maps. Activating the sets via Star Maps will boost certain character stats.\r\n\r\nAs with most MMORPGs, there is a full story to take part in as well as PvE and PvP. PvP includes guild battles while PvE players can battle world bosses that spawn every couple of hours.\r\n\r\nThe game is free-to-play via the Omega Zodiac site.','MMORPG','Web Browser','Proficient City','Game Hollywood','2016-08-25',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(201,102,'The Elder Scrolls: Legends','A free-to-play CCG based on The Elder Scrolls franchise. ','The Elder Scrolls: Legends is a free-to-play strategy card game based on the popular Bethesda Softworks Elder Scrolls franchise. It’s playable on both PC and iPad. Bethesda plans to launch the game in North America and Europe with localizations for English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, and Polish-speaking countries.\r\n\r\nTaking characters, creatures and lore from the vast world of the Elder Scrolls games, Bethesda has created a collectable card game with a variety of gameplay modes designed to give players freedom to choose how they want to play.\r\n\r\nIn Elder Scrolls Legends, players are able to acquire card packs and arena tickets by either purchasing them or earning them in game. Prices for both of these items have not been revealed as of yet.\r\n\r\nThose interested in The Elder Scrolls: Legends can apply for Closed Beta testing on the official game site.','Card Game','Windows','Bethesda Softworks','Bethesda Softworks','2016-08-04','Windows Vista/7/8/10','Intel Pentium D or AMD Athalon 64 X2','2 GB','Nvidia GeForce 6800 (256 MB) or aTI Radeon X1600 Pro (256 MB)','3 GB'),(202,106,'Riders of Icarus','A free-to-play action MMORPG featuring mounted, in-air combat. ','Riders of Icarus is a free-to-play action MMORPG featuring mounted, in-air combat. Developed by WeMade and published by Nexon America, the game offers players a wide variety of winged creatures for players to collect — as well as a selection of land creatures. These are trainable and can be used as more than just a simple ride when in combat. Each of them has unique abilities and can be collected more than once.\r\n\r\nCreatures are “tamed” in various ways and can be turned into mounts or companions — although not both at the same time. This means that players who want to collect all of them will need to tame the same creature twice. It’s part of the collectors aspect of the game.\r\n\r\nPlayers can work together to coordinate large aerial battles against other players or head to the ground to take on bosses. Both types of combat use an action-oriented melee combo system, with a newly updated action mode that can be toggled on and off.\r\n\r\nAt present, Riders of Icarus is still in Beta, although those interested can purchase Founders Packs via the official site.','MMORPG','Windows','VALOFE','WeMade','2016-07-06',' Windows 7, 8, 10','Intel Core i5-2500k @3.3GHz / AMD FX-6200 @3.3GH','4GB','GeForce GTX 460 (1GB) / Radeon HD 6870 (1GB)','30 GB'),(203,365,'Naruto Online','A free-to-play MMO based on the popular anime series and manga, developed \r\nby Bandai Namco Entertainment. ','Naruto Online is a free-to-play MMO based on the popular anime series and manga, developed by Bandai Namco Entertainment. The game follows the story line of the anime series with five new characters that represent the elements of earth, water, fire, wind, and lightning. Players choose one of these characters to play as.\r\n\r\nPlayers have the opportunity to relive key moments from the series while building their own ninja team consisting of characters from the show. The game features a combo fighting system that takes advantage of the team option as well as a variety of modes from single player to multi-player dungeons. There are also giant world bosses to fight and several ways for players to earn XP without getting bored.\r\n\r\nNaruto is a broswer-based game and can be played without the need of any downloads.','MMORPG','Web Browser','OAS Games','Bandai Namco','2016-07-20',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(204,108,'Zula','A free-to-play online FPS developed and published by IDC/Games. ','Zula is a free-to-play online FPS developed and published by IDC/Games. The game takes place in real-world locations such as Istanbul and offers players the chance to play as either a group of vigilantes called the Zula and an international paramilitary force — the Gladyo.\r\n\r\nIt features at least ten maps and a selection of modes for players to choose from. These include Team Deathmatch, Capture the Flag, Free for All, and Wanted. There are 16 playable characters — all inspired by television heroes — for players to pick from and all character outfits are based on paramilitary specs.\r\n\r\nTo make their characters unique, players will have more than 150 customizable weapons to use in game.','Shooter','Windows','IDC/Games','IDC/Games','2016-06-23','Windows XP/7/8/10','Pentium 4 2.4 GHz / Athalon XP 2500+','2 GB','Graphics Intel HD','1 GB'),(205,109,'LuckCatchers','A free-to-play sandbox sim based on the novels of fantasy and steam-punk author A. Pehov.','LuckCatchers is a free-to-play sandbox sim based on the novels of fantasy and steam-punk author A. Pehov. Technically, the game would be a prequel to those novels, being set 300 years prior to them. It’s a world without rules, open to any choices players make from the start.\r\n\r\nIn LuckCatchers, players will concentrate on social and economic features — including trade, and of course, war. There are over 30 NPC-ruled cities where players can do a variety of things, as well as a player-based world trade system and a real labor market. Regular game events include lotteries, dragon migrations, and plane races.\r\n\r\nLuckCatchers is not a casual game, and does feature PvP. However, new players are protected from it for the first month of playtime. Players can gather resources, craft, build a government, and more. This includes building ships and planes based on your own designs, producing weapons and ammunition, and constructing settlements.\r\n\r\nThe game is available to play on Steam.','MMORPG','Windows','DiP Online','DiP Online','2016-06-15',' Win 7 and up','Intel Core 2 Duo 2.5 GHz or AMD AthalonTM 64 X2 5600+ 2.8GHz','4 GB','GeForce x60 or best; ATI HD4870 or best; 1Gb videoRAM','3 GB'),(206,110,'UFO Online: Invasion','A free-to-play post-apocalyptic, turn-based tactical combat \r\nMMO developed by Bad Pixel. ','UFO Online: Invasion is a free-to-play post-apocalyptic, turn-based tactical combat MMORPG developed by Bad Pixel. Set some time after Earth is attacked by a massive alien vessel in 2024, the game tasks players with handling the aftermath of a global war. The aliens may have been defeated and left, but they also left a mark — in the form of alien life-forms and infrastructure that were abandoned during their retreat.\r\n\r\nInvasion features “simultaneous turns tactical combat,” which helps speed up the process of the game. Players spend 60 seconds during the Planning Phase to decide their actions and watch everything happen during the Simulation phase. This results in the game being able to handle massive PvP battles with dozens of players involved.\r\n\r\nOther features the game boats are a large open world filled with hidden treasures, quests, missions and more, a player-driven industry and economy, a skill system featuring more than 100 skills and 11 masteries, conquerable bases, and the ability to create and improve clans.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the free base game, Bad Pixel also offers three pieces of purchasable DLC: a Starter Kit, Mod Kit, and Adrenaline Kit. Prices for all vary with the total of all three being a little under $23.','MMORPG','Windows','Bad Pixel','Bad Pixel','2016-06-08','Windows XP, Vista, 7, 8, 10','1GHz or higher','1 GB RAM','any DirectX 9.0c compatible with 128 MB VRAM ','DirectX 9 compatible'),(207,112,'Weapons Of Mythology','A 3D free-to-play fantasy MMORPG published by IDC/Games. ','Weapons of Mythology: New Age is a free-to-play fantasy MMORPG published by IDC/Games. Built on the Unity 3D engine, the game casts players in the role of the hero, tasking them stopping the “dark side”.\r\n\r\nThe game is set during the Chu Han Contention and focuses on the Zhan and Jie sects. These two sects each serve their own king in the fight for the ultimate ancient Relic.\r\n\r\nPlay-wise, Weapons of Mythology features everything players expect from a modern MMO, PvP, boss hunts, territory wars, and more. Players can play as one of five classes, create and join guilds, use Relics to build out their character, and acquire pets able to take on human form.\r\n\r\nTo play, players will need to download the client via the official game site.','MMORPG','Windows','IDC/Games','Gamemag','2016-06-07','Window 7/8/10 (64 bit)','Intel Core Duo E7500','2 GB','GeForce 470 w/ DirectX 11','6 GB'),(208,116,'Tree of Savior','A fantasy 3D MMORPG with a massive freedom of choice, cute looking characters and a distinct art style. ','Many anxiously await the arrival of Tree of Savior (TOS), a fantasy 3D MMORPG with a massive freedom of choice, cute looking characters and a distinct art style. The game is being touted as a spiritual successor to the still popular Ragnarok Online, and that is more than enough to whet the appetite of MMORPG fans the world over.\r\n\r\nTree of Savior mimics many of the elements of Ragnarok Online, such as the attractive art style and the gameplay mechanics. More impressive is the fact that players will be treated to a musical score crafted by the same composers who gave Ragnarok Online its strong soundtrack.\r\n\r\nOver 80 classes will be available to players in Tree of Savior, making combat and gameplay, fun, engaging, and varied all across the board. Monster cards, like those of Ragnarok Online, will also be making an appearance. Tree of Savior also features PVP Content with the Team Battle League and Guild Wars (GvG).\r\n\r\nFans of Ragnarok Online are waiting on baited breath for Tree of Savior to arrive and bring them into a whole new MMORPG experience.','MMORPG','Windows','IMC Games','IMC Games','2016-05-10','Windows XP ','Intel Pentium Core 2 ','4 GB RAM ','NVIDIA Geforce 8600 ','4 GB'),(209,118,'Starbreak','A Roguelike MMORPG with MetroidVania-style platformer \r\ngameplay! Castlevania and Metroid fans will \r\nlove this game! ','Explore new and strange sci-fi worlds in Starbreak, a free-to-play roguelike action platformer MMO with MetroidVania-esque gameplay from Crunchy Games. Starbreak focuses on fast-paced gameplay that forces players to think on their feet when facing the game’s challenges. StarBreak is inspired by popular platformers, such as Castlevania and Metroid, but re-imagined with randomly generated content.\r\n\r\nPlayers will start by choosing one of four shells in Starbreak: Wildfire, Duskwing, Ironclad, and Fabricator. Each one has its own unique abilities that affect the game in different ways. Players can also join together in multiplayer co-op in order to tackles the challenges together and share in the loot.\r\n\r\nGameplay is challenging in Starbreak, requiring players to time their attacks, jumps, and fights carefully. If players are careless, their character can die permanently, forcing them to start all over again. And with such unique environments to explore, adventure and risk are never far away.\r\n\r\nStarbreak also has over 200 unique items to collect, giving players a wide range of items to either equip or sell in order to empower their character. Players looking for an exciting platforming challenge will want to give Starbreak a try.','MMORPG','Windows, Web Browser','Crunchy Games','Crunchy Games','2016-05-10','Windows Vista','800 MHz',' 512 MB','Intel HD Graphics 4000, OpenGL support','512 MB'),(210,119,'Fantasy Tales Online','A free-to-play, retro MMO featuring puzzles, a rich crafting system and Randomly generated dungeons! ','Fantasy tales online is a free-to-play, retro MMORPG featuring puzzles, a rich crafting system and randomly generated dungeons. Developed by Cold Tea Studio, the game is current available to play for free in Early Access — although, those looking for a little more can invest in the game’s Frontier Pack for twenty bucks.\r\n\r\nEven in Early Access, the game already boasts over 50 hour of content. All the core mechanics of the game are in place, including classes with unique builds, an item system, quests, guilds, and a party system. So Join your local player town, collect blocks to place in your home, band with friends and upgrade your home to a guild house as the base of your operations.\r\n\r\nDuring the Early Access state, the developers plan to work with the players to implement all the following changes and additions.\r\n\r\n    New boss fights requiring players to strategize to tackle large obstacles.\r\n\r\n    Continue to raise our level cap by adding new zones, quests and unique items.\r\n\r\n    New puzzle elements and dungeon mechanics.\r\n\r\n    Randomly generated dungeons featuring unique monsters, bosses, traps and more…\r\n\r\n    Elaborate expedition quest chains such as sieging instanced towns.\r\n\r\n    Extended the crafting system recipes to allow crafting top tier items.\r\n\r\n    Build Your Character, Home, and Unleash Your Powers.','MMORPG','Windows','Cold Tea Studio ','Cold Tea Studio ','2016-05-06','Windows 7 ','Intel Pentium D or equivalent ','2 GB RAM ','Intel HD Graphics or equivalent with OpenGL 1.5+ Drivers ','500 MB available space'),(211,117,'Astral Heroes','A free-to-play collectable card game from the creators of Astral Masters. ','Astral Heroes is a free-to-play collectible card game from Apus Software. The spiritual sequel to Astral Masters, Heroes features what the developers are calling a “truly fair free-to-play model,” stating the good stuff will never stuck behind a pay wall. As part of the decision to keep pay to win out of the game, the development team eliminated card rarity and made all cards equal in quality.\r\n\r\nAs with most CCG’s Astral Heroes features a variety of game modes — ranging from solo to competitive play — as well as 3 deck building modes:\r\n\r\n    Custom Decks: Construct and play a deck of your own personal design\r\n    Random Decks: Improvise a strategy on the fly with a deck of random cards\r\n    Draft Tournament: Draft the cards you need before your opponents snatch them!\r\n\r\nThe game will also launch with a global “Online League” that matches people from around the world, guilds, and a series of daily quests, missions and more.','Card Game','Windows','Apus Software','Apus Software','2016-03-15',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(212,124,'Holodrive','A free-to-play 2D multiplayer shooter developed by BitCake Studio and published by Versus Evil in which players play as customizable robots or \"Dummys\". ','Holodrive is a free-to-play 2D multiplayer shooter developed by BitCake Studio and published by Versus Evil in which players play as customizable robots or “Dummys”. The robots can be armed with a large arsenal of projectile weapons acquirable from weapon packs or via crafting. Each Dummy can carry 7 weapons at one time.\r\n\r\nThe game’s designed to have fast pased action requiring the use of strategy. It also heavily features explosions. To add to the fun, players can customize their Dummys to look like almost anything from ninjas, to cyborgs, to pirates.\r\n\r\nHolodrive even features a unique mode called Cocoball which combines the gameplay of basketball and pinball. There are also three other modes including deathmatch.','Shooter','Windows','Versus Evil','BitCake Studio','2016-03-24','Windows Vista, 7, 8, 10','Dual Core 2.66GHz','4 GB','DirectX 9.0c compatible card with 512MG','2 GB'),(213,304,'Cabal Online','A free to play fast-paced skill-based MMORPG in a stunning world!','Cabal Online is a free to play 3D MMORPG developed by the South Korean company ESTsoft. CABAL Online introduces fast-paced skill-based combat in a stunning world that blurs the line between fantasy and science fiction. The game takes place in the fictional world of Nevareth nearly a thousand years after its destruction by a group called the Cabal. The game contains PvP and PvE elements each of which will reward the player in various ways.\r\n\r\nPvE is very well represented in Cabal Online. There is the constant grinding that will allow you to keep doing the same process over and over again slowly improving your character over time, questing which will offer multiple types of rewards and experience points, and instances that will reward you with rarer items as well as the in-game currency Alz that you can use in the in-game item shop.\r\n\r\nIf you would prefer to go the route of PvP then have no worries as there is plenty of that in Cabal Online as well. Travel around the world crushing other players while they attempt to quest and grind, arrange a duel between yourself and another player, join a nation and participate in the Mission War system that puts in you massive combat situations with other players, and don’t forget about joining and guild and battling other guilds for your place on the top of the leaderboards.','MMORPG','Windows','ESTsoft','ESTsoft','2016-02-17',' Windows XP SP 3 or newer','Intel Pentium 4 2.0 GHz','1 GB','Nvidia GeForce 6 series / ATI Radeon 9800 PRO','3.5 GB available space'),(214,125,'Atom Universe','A free-to-play multiplayer online social Virtual World set in a theme park.','Atom Universe is a free-to-play multiplayer online social Virtual World set in a 3D theme park where players can meet and interact in a fun and thrilling carnival atmosphere.\r\n\r\nAtom Republic has brought social Virtual World games to a whole new level, In Atom Universe, players can join together amidst the fun and whimsy of a virtual theme park with no shortage of amusements available. Classic rides abound in Atom Universe, from roller coasters and go-karts to massive multi-colored Ferris wheels. What better way to meet someone new than in an amusement park?\r\n\r\nBut amusement parks are more than rides, and Atom Universe features dozens of different mini-games to play, from classic theme park arcade standards like Whack-a-Mole to mini-golfing and bowling. And much like a certain theme park in the real world, Atom Universe is always changing and adding something new.\r\n\r\nPlayers looking for fun social interaction in a theme park setting will love Atom Universe.','Social','Windows','Atom Republic','Atom Republic','2016-02-27','Windows 7/8 64-bit ','Quad-core Intel or AMD, 2.5 GHz or faster',' 8 GB RAM',' DirectX 11 compatible graphics card ','5 GB available space'),(215,374,'Clash of Avatars','A free to play 3D browser MMORPG with powerful Avatars, 50 mounts, \r\nand several loyal pets.','Clash of Avatars is a free-to-play browser based 3D fantasy MMORPG from AMZGame where players create characters based on anime and cosplay. The browser MMORPG is rendered in beautiful 3D graphics, making it standout from similar Chinese browser MMORPGs.\r\n\r\nEven though the in-game classes are limited to the Mage, Priest, and Warrior classes, Clash of Avatars features over 60 unique avatars, 10 helpful pets, and 50 reliable mounts to choose from.\r\n\r\nClash of Avatars will also host familiar PvE events, like challenging World Bosses or strategic Corridor Defense. In addition to that, players in Clash of Avatars will also be able to take part in PvP events, including Coliseum battles and even flag events, just to name a few. It may be early to call it, but Clash of Avatars is shaping up to be an entertaining browser MMORPG title.','MMORPG','Web Browser','AMZgame','AMZgame','2016-01-19',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(216,134,'War Trigger 3','A MMO shooter with infantry, vehicle, and air combat across massive maps! ','Blasting out of Rocketeer Games is War Trigger 3 (formerly Red Crucible: Firestorm) a free-to-play MMO shooter that pulls players into intense online matches featuring infantry, vehicle and air combat across massive maps.\r\n\r\nEquipped with gear taken straight from modern military forces, Red Crucible: Firestorm will give players to choose their preferred fighting style from the Assault, Sniper, Support, and Demolitions classes. These weapons can be significantly upgraded as players gain experience, giving them a stronger edge over their opponents on the battlefield, especially when maps can support up to 24 players at a time.\r\n\r\nWar Trigger 3 also prominently features modern war machines in the form of tanks, helicopters, artillery platforms, anti-air vehicles, and more. These vehicles are essential for either getting quickly across the map or bringing heavy firepower down on the enemy.\r\n\r\nPlayers can either play by themselves or they can join online clans to build a stronger, more effective fighting force in War Trigger 3. Teams like this can make all the difference in the wide variety of modes available in War Trigger 3, such as Survivor, Team Deathmatch, Conquer, Team Deathmatch Armored, and more.\r\n\r\nWar Trigger 3 offers much for the MMO shooter genre and will bring the pulse-pounding combat right to the player.','Shooter','Windows','Rocketeer Games','Rocketeer Games','2015-12-23','Windows 7 / OSX Lion','Intel Core i3','4 GB','Intel Integrated Graphics','4 GB'),(217,136,'VEGA Conflict','A Cross-Platform free to play 2D sci-fi strategy MMO.','VEGA Conflict is a Cross-Platform free to play 2D browser based sci-fi strategy MMO. VEGA Conflict requires players to take on the role of space minters and seek absolute control over the scarce resources found in the sectors’ asteroids. Available on PC, Mac, iOS and Android, VEGA Conflict allows players to obtain and manage a fleet of large, unique ships and command centers. Use your fleet to conquer the VEGA Federation, a villainous organization that seeks to acquire and utilize the sectors’ resources for themselves.\r\n\r\nPublished by KIXYE, VEGA Conflict boasts a large player base and real-time PvP combat with PVE resource gathering. Your territory may come under attack without warning, so always be prepared to defend yourself against enemy forces. You must ascertain your enemies strengths and weaknesses, and strategically contrive your fleet around them. Interact with other players by joining alliances and discuss your approach. The game also features a ship customization systems that allows players to perpetually enhance their fleets’ abilities.','Strategy','Windows','KIXEYE','KIXEYE','2015-12-15','Windows XP+ ','Dual Core 1.8GHz','4 GB','DX9 (shader model 2.0) capabilities','2 GB'),(218,137,'Metal War Online: Retribution','A high-speed multiplayer online concept car shooter game with racing elements!','Metal War Online: Retribution is a high-speed futuristic multiplayer online car shooter game with racing elements. In the future corporations around the world are involved in huge wars for resources. You will see how powerful transnational corporations are embroiled in a fierce battle for resources and the entire world will become a huge battlefield. You will choose any of the powerful war machines and will win your battles and lead your side to victory!\r\n\r\nDeveloped and published by GDT Limited, and released as an Early Access title on December 11, 2015, the game centers on what the developers are referring to as “corporate wars”. Two major corporations – the Global Resource Network and Morgan Industries utilized mercenary groups, security agencies, and private armies in a war that became so large that they could no longer keep it a secret from the public.\r\n\r\nPlayers take on the role of the mercenaries, using high-tech machinery in battle on behalf of the corporations. You will also be joining millions of players from around the world, so you are sure to find someone you’ll want to play with again and again. Currently there are four combat classes in the game. Your objective is simple. Just defeat your enemy, at any cost, and make it home alive! Think you can manage that? If you have a love for shooter games and fast cars, then check out Metal War Online: Retribution!','Shooter','Windows','GDT Limited','GDT Limited','2015-12-11',' Windows 7 / Vista / XP SP3','Intel Core 2 Duo or AMD Athlon X2 64 3.0 GHz','2 GB','512 MB NVIDIA GeForce 9500GT / ATI Radeon HD 3450','3 GB of free space'),(219,139,'Immortal Empire','A free to play multiplayer strategy RPG developed by Tactic Studios.','Immortal Empire is a free to play role playing game with strategy elements, developed by Tactic Studios. Adventure as an immortal in the realm of Alvedor while discovering the secrets of the Empire. Enjoy a great multiplayer experience with your friends, and enemies, in Immortal Empire.\r\n\r\nControl up to five different immortals in your party as you adventure through Alvedor defeating your enemies with cunning tactics. Progress your immortals by leveling them up and unlocking more powerful and unique spells. As you defeat your enemies you will find rare and powerful pieces of gear that will help to improve your immortals. If the gear you find isn’t enough, you can always create and customize your own gear with materials you find during your adventures.\r\n\r\nEnjoy a great multiplayer experience in Immortal Empire whether you are participating in the co-op with your friends or the PvP with your enemies. The teamplay allows you to start huge wars for control in custom, objective-based game modes. Climb different ladders in ranked play in Immortal Empire, participate in quests in the co-op more or fight against other players in versus mode.\r\n\r\nImmortal Empire is a multiplayer strategy RPG with a great amount of party customization and a good social aspect to it. It allows you to make friends and crush your enemies with its great custom teamplay mechanics.','MMORPG','Windows','Tactic Studios Inc.','Tactic Studios Inc.','2015-12-03','XP','Intel Core 2 Duo or equivalent ',' 2 GB','NVidia GTX 650 (1GB memory) ','768 MB'),(220,149,'America’s Army: Proving Grounds','Take a first person shooter, have the game developed by the U.S. Army and you’ve got America’s Army.','America’s Army: Proving Grounds is a free to play military online FPS game. Take a first person shooter, add in Rules of Engagement and other Army codes, have the game developed by the U.S. Army and you’ve got America’s Army: Proving Grounds. While America’s Army is designed to be a fun game, it also serves as a bit of a recruiting tool for the U.S. Army and adds elements of Army training, core values, and a focus on teamwork to the mix.\r\n\r\nDetailed environments and diverse maps make America’s Army a very popular free-to-play shooter. Supporting multiple games modes that include 6v6, 12v12, and other game types adds a bit of diversity between each match that keeps players engaged. Securing downed enemies adds to the feel of realism and since points are awarded for actions such a providing cover or suppression fire, America’s Army forces players to rely on the unit as a whole rather than a single player. One lone gunman is not likely to last very long against a team.\r\n\r\nIf you enjoyed the offline games or just want to take a dive into a shooter game with a bit more focus on teamwork and strategy, America’s Army: Proving Grounds has a large enough player base to keep you earning experience and upgrading your tactics and weapons for quite some time.','Shooter','Windows','U.S. Army','U.S. Army','2015-10-01','Windows Vista ',' 2.4+ GHz Quad Core CPU ','4096 MB RAM ','Direct X 9.0c compliant, Shader 3.0 enabled video card with 512MB RAM','10000 MB available space '),(221,383,'Legends of Honor','A free to play browser based medieval fantasy 2D MMORTS.','Legends of Honor is a free to play browser based medieval fantasy MMORTS. Strengthen your defenses, improve your castle, and send your heroes to do battle in Legends of Honor, a 2D strategy MMO game from Goodgame Empire.\r\n\r\nManage your resources and build your city walls to defend against attackers in Legends of Honor in any way you want. Your city’s survival depends on you and your strategy so make it count.\r\n\r\nOf course, Legends of Honor also allows you to recruit heroes to your cause and to send them as part of your troops out into the wilderness to vanquish marauders and defend against encroaching threats, not the least of which is other players looking to expand their own territories.\r\n\r\nPlayers can also ally themselves with one another in Legends of Honor, with the option to join one of three factions with names meant in homage to Game of Thrones writer George R.R. Martin.\r\n\r\nExploration and innovation are well rewarded in Legends of Honor, but only if you take that step and begin building your empire strongly from the ground up.','Strategy','Web Browser','Goodgame Empire','Goodgame Studios','2015-08-20',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(222,384,'Felspire','A free-to-play 2D browser-based fantasy MMORPG with plenty of dungeons and world bosses to slay.','Felspire is a free-to-play 2D browser-based fantasy MMORPG published by 37Games. Choose between Archer, Mage, and Warrior as you enter the realm of Eremos\r\n\r\nPlayers will arrive in a world where a portal known as the Felspire connects the world and the underworld, leaving mankind open to the vicious machinations of monsters. Your quest hinges on fighting these beasts and saving mankind from their horrors.\r\n\r\nThough Felspire only has three classes, players can specialize their roles in each one multiple times in order to create their own unique character and abilities. Countless collectibles ranging from specialized mounts to impressive titles ensure that no two player characters are ever truly alike.\r\n\r\nFelspire boasts the feature of keeping the automated gameplay system on at all times after the player’s second class advancement. This means that the player’s character is always grinding and gaining experience.\r\n\r\nPlayers in Felspire can also join forces in guilds to tackle special obstacles in Multiplayer PvE challenges and quests. And when they tire of their companions, they can duel them in the PvP Battleground that will help players climb the ranks of the game’s top spots.\r\n\r\nEven with its heavy emphasis on automated gameplay, Felspire is still a enjoyable browser MMORPG.','MMORPG','Web Browser','37Games','37Games Entertainment','2015-08-07',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(223,154,'Sphere 3: Enchanted World','A fantasy action MMORPG with a non-target combat system.','Sphere III: Enchanted World is a 3D fantasy action MMORPG that was published by Nikita Online. Use the game’s unique non-target combat system and participate in the PvP that is a strong focus in Sphere III.\r\n\r\nAs you play Sphere III you will quickly learn that the combat does not auto-aim for you. You will have to manually aim your attacks using the color-coded crosshairs on your screen to determine the best skills to use against your enemies. This is particularly difficult when you are participating in the PvP servers where player’s will move much more erratically than an AI opponent. Careful killing to many players though, the game’s Karma System will make you lose gold and even items if you get killed and have a low Karma.\r\n\r\nOnce you get bored with the thousands of quests that Sphere III offers you may decide to start participating in Castle Sieges. Castle Sieges offer you the chance to take over castle and make them your own. If you end up controlling at castle this is the best way to earn some of the greatest items in Sphere III.\r\n\r\nSphere III: Enchanted World features a great non-target combat system that provides freedom of aiming, dynamically calculates the damage and allows a player to quickly pick an optimum attacking ability, offering players something to develop their skills with. You can also participate in Castle Sieges to earn the best items in the game and make your Karma go up or down while participating in the PvP.','MMORPG','Windows','NIKITA ONLINE','NIKITA ONLINE','2015-08-18','Windows XP, Vista or Windows 7,8,8.1 (32 or 64-bit)','Dual core more than 2 GHz ','2 GB','Shader 3.0 support Geforce 6600, Radeon X1600, 256 Mb RAM and DirectX 9.0c support','6 GB'),(224,157,'Fishing Planet','A Free to play realistic online first-person multiplayer fishing simulator! ','The core focus of Fishing Planet is providing players with a peaceful environment that they can relax in while waiting for that big catch. With seven locations and an array of weather conditions to take advantage of, Fishing Planet offers a unique experience in player interaction.\r\n\r\nFishing Planet also gives players a massive selection of equipment to choose from. Players can customize their gear to suit their fishing style and watch as their catch count rises.\r\n\r\nAnd don’t worry about Fishing Planet featuring just one generic type of fish. There are 32 species of fish available to catch in all of the various locations, each one requiring different baits and tactics.\r\n\r\nSport fishing wouldn’t be competitive without a leaderboard, and Fishing Planet pits players across the internet against one another to see who can catch “the big one” and take first place.\r\n\r\nFishing Planet promises a relaxing atmosphere and a competitive challenge to players looking to ease into a game.','Sports','Windows','Fishing Planet LLC','Fishing Planet LLC','2015-08-11','Windows XP, Windows Vista, or Windows 7','Dual-Core 2.4 Ghz','4GB','Graphics Card Intel HD4000 or higher','12 GB'),(225,386,'Aberoth','A free to play 8-bit MMORPG with retro graphics and MUD-like interface.','Adventure, magic, and fantasy await you in Aberoth, a free-to-play MMORPG crafted in the retro graphics of days gone by! Don’t let the graphics fool you, though, for Aberoth offers much to players who dare to embark on the path it offers.\r\n\r\nAberoth brings a unique take to the MMORPG market, and not just because of its retro graphic style. Players have almost total freedom within the game right from the beginning (starting out in an Orc prison cell aside). If you’re not interested in battling fierce monsters or questing through the varied lands within the game, you are more than welcome to fight other players within the game world with all of the skills and items you possess.\r\n\r\nBut be warned! Your enemies are crafty as well, and they will not hesitate to pick up items and scrolls cast aside in order to defeat you. From the thieves of Rogue’s Den to skeletons of the Desert Tomb, enemies lie in wait all throughout Aberoth, waiting to challenge your skills.\r\n\r\nPerhaps the greatest asset of Aberoth is that it plays well even on the lowest system. No software upgrades or downloads required to engage in this unrestricted MMORP world of magic and fantasy. There is always a quest to be completed and special events are announced regularly.\r\n\r\nEscape the Orc Prison and begin your path to greatness within the realms of Aberoth!',' MMORPG','Web Browser','Jarbit','Jarbit','2015-07-17',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(226,159,'Codename CURE','A free to play 3D MMOFPS featuring cooperative play, and objective-based missions.','The undead prowl the maps in search of flesh in Codename CURE, a free to play MMOFPS with objective based missions set against the backdrop of a zombie apocalypse.\r\n\r\nTaking a leaf from Team Fortress 2’s book, Codename CURE gives players access to five different classes to play as, each with their own strengths and weakness against the zombie hordes. Players will mow down legions of the undead with weapons unique to each class in heart-pounding FPS combat.\r\n\r\nPlayers will also be introduced to massive in-game maps in Codename CURE, forcing them to think tactically about how they will defend against the lurking zombies. Each map has its own objectives which must be completed if the team is going to survive to see the end of this nightmare.\r\n\r\nOnly the strong will survive and end the zombie outbreak in Codename CURE, and everyone has their own role to play.','Shooter','Windows','Hoobalugalar_X','Hoobalugalar_X','2015-07-18','Windows® 7 (32/64-bit)/Vista/XP ','Pentium 4 3.0GHz or equivalent ','1 GB RAM ','nVidia GeForce 6 series, ATI Radeon 9600 ','4 GB available space '),(227,161,'Skyforge','A impressive Free to play MMORPG where you can become a god! ','Skyforge is a impressive Free to play MMORPG created by Obsidian Entertainment and Mail.ru group’s Allods Team. Skyforge puts you in the shoes of an Immortal wielding amazing powers, with the mission of protecting your world against hordes of creatures hell-bent on seeing the destruction of your planet. Will you be able to defeat the armies of other Gods, and finally reach of title of a God for yourself?\r\n\r\nSkyforge’s class system is completely versatile, allowing you to switch between classes seamlessly, as long as you are not currently in combat. You don’t start out with all 13 classes, but you are able to unlock the other 10 classes simply by progressing through the game. Some of the classes available are Cryomancer and Lightbinder.\r\n\r\nYou can complete quests through the Divine Observatory, visit the Research Center in order to alter your character and train/test new classes and you can visit the Park which allows you to Host and partake is events. All of this is available from the hub world, which is also the capital of Aelion. Every part of Aelion is explore-able, resulting in loads of content.\r\n\r\nSkyforge rocks stunning visuals and top tier graphics, provides a huge selection of weapons, including guns and swords, and has a fantastically built progression system called the “Ascension Atlas”. This replaces the normal leveling platform and switches it for a Prestige system found in a lot of FPS titles like COD. This allows for the fluid class changes.','MMORPG','Windows','Innova Co SARL','Allods Team & Obsidian Entertainment Collaboration','2015-07-16','Windows XP / 7 / 8 / 10','Dual Core E2160 1.8 GHz','2 GB','GeForce 8600 GTS, Intel HD 3000, Radeon HD 4650 or better','20 GB'),(228,163,'Card Hunter','A free online collectible card game which blends together role-playing, card play and tactical combat. ','Tabletop gaming shall never be forgotten so long as Card Hunter is there to defend it! From developer Blue Manchu, this free-to-play online RPG and strategy game combines the familiar dice, cards, and miniatures of traditional tabletop gaming with the fast pace and vast community of the internet.\r\n\r\nAssemble your team and build your deck before you venture out onto the grid-based battlefields of Card Hunter, preparing to face strange beasts and hazardous enemies, all under the watchful of the powerful and wise Game Master, Gary.\r\n\r\nCard Hunter teaches you to adapt your strategies for turn-based combat and ready your card deck to achieve victory against your foes and claim vast treasures and new cards carrying powerful abilities and items.\r\n\r\nInvite your friends to join your endless quests in Card Hunter, building your team to support one another in order to overcome the foes that lie before you on the path to glory.\r\n\r\nAnd if you’re looking for further challenges, Card Hunter gives you the chance to engage other players in everything from friendly challenges to intense league matches where rivalries thrive. Climb the month’s season and let all who dare to challenge you know that you are a master of Card Hunter.\r\n\r\nThough Card Hunter requires 300 MB of available storage, it is well worth the adventures and quests this game will bring you. Begin your hunt for fun and glory with Card Hunter today!','Card Game','Windows, Web Browser','Blue Manchu','Blue Manchu','2015-07-14','Windows 7 or later ','2.33 Ghz or faster x86-compatible processor or Intel Atom™ 1.6GHz ','1 GB RAM ','300 MB available space ','300 MB available space '),(229,104,'Fallout Shelter','A free-to-play simulation game based on Bethesda Game Studios\' popular Fallout franchise. ','Fallout Shelter is a free-to-play simulation game based on Bethesda Game Studios’ popular Fallout franchise. Originally released as a mobile game, the game became popular enough that Bethesda decided to release a version for PC.\r\n\r\nAs with most sim games, Fallout Shelter requires the player to take care and manage a small society of people known as “Dwellers.” This is done by meeting their needs, food, water, power, etc. Dwellers can be made useful to the vault society by managing their stats and training them for specific things. Characters with high stats in specific things will be able to generate higher amounts of resources for the community. In addition, the community is grown by either waiting for new people to arrive or by pairing a male and female dweller to create children.\r\n\r\nPlayers can build a wide variety of rooms for the vault dwellers to use; everything from rooms to generate resources, to training rooms, and recreational areas.\r\n\r\nAnother feature of Fallout Shelter is exploration. Players can send dwellers into the wasteland on missions and to seek out new locations. Of course, these dwellers should be properly trained and geared, or they won’t last long.','Strategy','Windows','Bethesda Game Studios','Bethesda Game Studios','2015-06-14','Windows 7 64 bit','Intel Core 2 Quad CPU Q9550 @2.83GHZ','2 GB RAM','NVIDIA GeForce GTS 250 1Ghz, Radeon HD 6970 1GHz','2 GB available space'),(230,388,'Lord’s Road','A free-to-play 2D browser-based fantasy MMORPG that features two playable classes.','Lord’s Road is a free-to-play 2D browser-based fantasy MMORPG that features two playable classes. While some players may call its simple two-class system (Warrior and Mage) limiting, many players enjoy the fresh challenge that Lord’s Road has placed before them.\r\n\r\nThis chinese browser MMORPG sets itself apart from most conventions of the genre by making its AFK mode only available to premium members. This decision forces players who do not wish to pay to accomplish character grinding and dungeon crawling the old-fashioned way: by actually playing the game. That may sound like a turn-off for some people, but gamers who love MMORPG combat will surely love this feature.\r\n\r\nPlayers can also enlist the help of one of the nine goddesses in Lord’s Road, bringing her into combat where she will prove to be an invaluable asset with helpful hints.\r\n\r\nLord’s Road also allows players to engage one another in PvP combat, both 1v1 and guild battles where players will fight for the highest rankings among one another.\r\n\r\nLet the goddesses guide you as you fight your way through Lord’s Road. They may even help you find many of the collectibles that can improve and enhance your in-game abilities.','MMORPG','Web Browser','AMZGame','AMZGame','2015-06-03',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(231,168,'Heroes of the Storm','A free to play MOBA developed by Blizzard Entertainment.','Heroes of the Storm is a free to play Multiplayer Online Battle Arena (MOBA) developed by Blizzard Entertainment. Heroes of the Storm is an extremely well-polished MOBA that utilizes many assets from past Blizzard games.\r\n\r\nChoose from many different Heroes that are present throughout the Blizzard universes. Heroes from StarCraft like Artanis and Tychus, Heroes from Warcraft such as Lunara and Cho’Gall, Heroes from Diablo like Kharazim or The Butcher, and you can even choose from retro Heroes from past Blizzard games like the Lost Vikings.\r\n\r\nBattle on five versus five battlegrounds each with different objectives, but the ultimate objective always being destroying your enemies core. Everyone chooses different Heroes that they will level up together as the game progresses choosing new talents at levels 1, 4, 7, 10, 13, 16, and 20. The great thing about being able to choose different talents at so many levels and competing in 5 v 5 situations is that virtually no game will ever turn out the same.\r\n\r\nGet randomly placed in one of 10 different battlegrounds with objectives that vary from delivering coins to a pirate to blast your opponent’s core to battling angels and demons that will push down lanes and destroy your opponent’s structures.\r\n\r\nHeroes of the storm is a MOBA that is extremely well-polished and competes very well against all others MOBAs on the market. Choose from a great selection of Heroes from a fantastic set of universes and battle on many iconic battlegrounds.','MOBA','Windows',' Blizzard Entertainment',' Blizzard Entertainment','2015-06-02','Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8','Intel Dual Core / AMD X2 5600+','2 GB','Nvidia GeForce 7600 GT / ATI Radeon 2600 XT','10 GB'),(232,357,'Vikings: War Of Clans','A free-to-play MMO strategy game developed and published by Plarium.','Vikings: War of Clans is a 3D free-to-play browser based strategy game developed and published by Plarium. Originally developed for mobile devices, the game is now available on PC. It is a multiplayer game in which player form their own clans, train troops and build their society.\r\n\r\nIn Vikings, players can team up into clans of 100 people in order to achieve goals and help each other. They can also work together to obtain the resources necessary to maintain buildings and upgrade troops. Players are separated geographically into different locations known as kingdoms with each kingdom housing around 45,000 players.\r\n\r\nAs one might expect from the name Vikings is based on Scandinavian history, with the developers taking their lead from TV shows and movies as well as other sources containing information on Scandinavian culture.','Strategy','Web Browser','Plarium','Plarium','2015-04-15',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(233,391,'Star Trek: Alien Domain','A free to play browser based 2D strategy MMO set in the Stark Trek universe.','Star Trek: Alien Domination is a free to play browser based 2D strategy MMO set in the Stark Trek universe. Players must choose between siding with the Klingon Empire or the United Federation of Planets. Each faction offers unique artwork, officers and ships to take you on alien-killing adventures. The United Federation of Planets has access to Constitution-class and Defiant-class starships, while the Klingon faction offers D7 Battle Cruisers and Birds of Prey.\r\n\r\nPlayers can also create ships new to the Stark Trek universe by researching emerging technologies. The browser-based strategy game boasts a new Star Trek story and requires players to construct bases to obtain resources and research emerging technologies to amass a diverse fleet of ships to make you a formidable alien killer and universe dominator.\r\n\r\nSet in the realm of fluidic space, Star Trek: Alien Domination offers a medium player base and some customization, in that you can build various upgradeable structures to gain access to different skill trees. Players must strategically exercise resource-management skills to maintain and expand their colonies. The game also offers both PvP and PvE options. PvP ranges from one-on-one fights to massive guild-against-guild fights. Colonize available planets and defend your colonies against attacks from other players in turn-based online strategy duels.','Strategy','Web Browser','GameSamba','GameSamba','2015-04-07',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(234,177,'Dungeon Fighter Online','A free to play arcade-style side-scrolling action game mixed with RPG elements.','Dungeon Fighter Online is a 2D free to play multiplayer arcade-style beat’em up game developed by Neople. It features 2D side-scrolling action fighting with some roleplaying elements including, along with multiple unique classes and some PvP.\r\n\r\nIn Dungeon Fighter Online you will traverse the game fighting hordes of monsters trying to keep you HP and MP meter high as you battle your way to the more difficult stages of the game. You HP meter will decrease as you get hit and your MP meter will decrease as you use your skills.\r\n\r\nWhen you begin your beat’em up experience you can choose from several different classes. You can choose from the Male Slayer, Blade Master, Soul Bender, Berserker, Asura, Female Slayer, Sword Master, Dark Templar, Demon Slayer, Vagabond, Male Gunner, Ranger, Mechanic, Spitfire, Launcher, Female Mage, Elementalist, Summoner, Battle Mage, and Witch. Each of these classes has very unique abilities and gear that you can customize as you adventure through the world.\r\n\r\nThe combat in Dungeon Fighter Online can be either passive or active. All of the classes have abilities that you can choose to either let active on their own, which will make them cost a lot of MP, or you can choose to activate them yourself, which will make the MP cost of the ability go down.','Fighting','Windows','Neople','Neople (Subsidiary of Nexon)','2015-03-24','Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8','Intel Dual Core / AMD X2 5600+','2 GB','Nvidia GeForce 8800 GT','5 GB'),(235,56,'Grimoire: Manastorm','A free-to-play multiplayer FPS... with wizards. ','Grimoire: Manastorm is a free-to-play multiplayer FPS… with wizards. Rather than arming players with guns and ammo, they’re given unique spells.\r\n\r\nThe game offers players six classes to chose from and boasts thousands of potential spell loadouts. Players will need to have a sound understanding of their character’s abilities in order to compete. Even more, they’ll need to know how to counter their opponents abilities.\r\n\r\nThe classes offered are Fire, Lightning, Earth, Ice, Nature, and Neather. Each has their own book of spells and can be adjusted to suit each individual player’s style. There are two multiplayer modes that can be played across 12 settings.\r\n\r\nThe game is free-to-play, and offers two rotating classes that can be used at any time. Classes and spells can be unlocked by purchasing them or spending points earned in game.','Shooter','Windows','Omniconnection','Omniconnection','2015-02-04','Windows XP SP3 (32-bit only), Windows Vista, Windows 7','2.0+ GHz','2 GB',' SM3-Compatible','2 GB'),(236,394,'One Piece Online','One Piece Online is a 2D Tower Defense Action MMO! ','Set in the ever popular world of Shonen Jump’s One Piece, One Piece Online is a 2D Tower Defense Action MMORPG that will let players take part in the universe of the beloved anime & manga series. Combining elements of tower defense games with traditional RPGs has created a unique game that many players can enjoy.\r\n\r\nKeeping with the theme of its namesake, One Piece Online splits players into one of three classes: Sniper, Swordsman, or Devil Fruit User. Each class has its own unique abilities and style of combat. Players will also be able to recruit familiar characters from the world of One Piece in order to aid them in battle.\r\n\r\nOne Piece Online also makes use of an auto-play mechanic, meaning that players can let their characters grind even while their away from the game. This can be a useful tool for players with limited time on their hands. Players can also engage in a wide variety of single-player and PvP modes that offer hours of entertainment.\r\n\r\nWith the only downside being pay to win elements, One Piece Online is a fun game that fans of the series will undoubtedly enjoy.','MMORPG','Web Browser','JoyGames','JoyGames','2015-01-22',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(237,180,'Gear Up','Control your unique tank or robot in multiplayer arcade action!','Gear Up is a free to play multiplayer arcade action game with tanks and robots. Vehicular combat is fun, and Gear Up is no exception to that. From Doctor Entertainment AB, Gear Up puts players in massive arena-style matches that can support up to 16 players in a single match. With gameplay built around an arcade-style mechanic, players will find Gear Up easy to learn and riotously fun to play.\r\n\r\nThe key to Gear Up is customization. Players can customize their bots however they want and jump into the action right away. The in-game currency allows players to purchase a variety of deadly weapons and movement types in order to best their enemies in frantic bot on bot combat.\r\n\r\nGear Up features four game modes that ensure the fun never ends. Deathmatch, Team Deathmatch, Tag, and Conquest all promise furious bot combat between players armed with their own heavily customized machines.\r\n\r\nThe combat in Gear Up is fierce, so players need to find out how they can make their personal bots even fiercer than the competition.','Shooter','Windows','Doctor Entertainment','Doctor Entertainment','2015-01-29','Windows Vista SP2 / Windows 7 / Windows 8','Pentium 4 3.46GHz or Athlon 64 3800+','2GB','GeForce GT 120 or Radeon HD 4550','1 GB'),(238,399,'Siegelord','A free to play 2D medieval fantasy browser-based MMORTS.','Siegelord is a free to play 2D medieval fantasy browser-based MMORTS, players compete with other players by expanding the cities they initially start the game with into vast empires. Published by 37 Games Entertainment, the RTS game is a mix of strategy and civilization building. To generate resources, you must construct certain buildings on the land you currently have available to prepare for real-time battles with other players. The battles are simple and somewhat automated. However, you will need to ensure your settlement is prepared well enough to offer the support you’ll need during combat in the form of resources, equipment and troop-enhancing technologies.\r\n\r\nSiegelord is set in a medieval fantasy world where three opposing empires, the Albion, Nords Alliance and the Empire of Gorm, fight for territorial domination. Players must choose a faction to fight for, and recruit and equip generals to offer support to your troops in battle. Generals are unlocked throughout the game and offer skills and equipment. You can play through the single-player campaign, or fight other players for territorial control. While battling other players, you must choose the proper formation for your troops (assault, attack or defense) to seize victory. Stay frosty, as the borders of the land of Theiden shift perpetually as players conquer new territory.','Strategy','Web Browser','37Games Entertainment','37Games Entertainment','2014-12-19',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(239,184,'Blockade 3D','A free to play FPS in an editable procedural world.','Blockade 3D is a free to play multiplayer First Person Shooter (FPS) in an editable procedural world similar to Minecraft. In this cubic sandbox you can build and destroy things with 4 teams at the same time and up to 32 players on one map.\r\n\r\nIn Blockade 3D you can build your own map, be the last-man-standing against zombies, be in a tank battle and more. You can also upgrade your weapon and equipment, there is lots of in-game possibilities.','Shooter','Windows','Shumkov Dmitriy','Shumkov Dmitriy','2014-11-05','Windows XP / 7 / 8 / 8.1 / 10','Pentium 4 2 GHz','1 GB RAM','GeForce 5700','300 MB available space'),(240,185,'Eldevin','A indie story-driven Free to Play MMORPG.','Eldevin is a indie free to play, browser-based (and client-based) fantasy MMORPG developed by Hunted Cow Studios. The game takes place in the Eldevin Kingdom with the story based on the discovery of Elemental Spheres.\r\n\r\nTake on Eldevin’s massive world where any action that you take can affect future quests that you may run into. Speaking of quests never fear of running out of something to do, Eldevin offers hundreds of quests that can change from character to character depending upon how you resolve certain situations.\r\n\r\nInstead of choosing a close in Eldevin you will be choosing from 100s of abilities in six different talent trees. This offers a much wider range of customization than a simple class system could ever offer and with the game’s real-time combat system it will be very different from other MMORPG experiences.\r\n\r\nAfter you get done diving into the multiple dungeons and instances that Eldevin has to offer you will have most likely acquired some crafting materials that you can use to craft your own weapons, armor, and items with the 14 different professions that Eldevin offers.\r\n\r\nEldevin is a free to play MMO that has a great story line, tons of quests with a dynamic universe, a class-less real-time combat system, and tons of crafting that you are able to do.','MMORPG','Windows, Web Browser','Hunted Cow Studios','Hunted Cow Studios','2014-11-05','Windows XP, Vista, 7, 8','Intel® Core™ 2 Duo E6600 or AMD Phenom™ X3 8750 processor or better ',' 2 GB','Graphics Card Recommended. (OpenGL 3.0 support and above) ','1 GB'),(241,186,'Double Action','A free to play FPS with bullet time and stylish kills!','Double Action is a free to play multiplayer online FPS that incorporates bullet time (Matrix style!) in free for all matches across tons of different environments. Get higher scores for kills with flair and claim to the top of the scoreboards.\r\n\r\nUse the crazy bullet time where you slow down the time for both you and your opponents so that you can decide on your next plan of action. As you are participating in the free for all that is Double Action try to get some stylish kills while diving, rolling and flipping to earn extra points to win the match.\r\n\r\nWhile you don’t choose from different characters to play as you do get to choose what their special ability will be. There is a wide selection of different special abilities that every character can have. Some give you extra grenades while others might give you faster movement speed. You are also able to customize your weapon loadout and change it during the match to counter whatever your opponents are doing and develop the perfect combination of items for yourself.\r\n\r\nDouble Action is an FPS that incorporates bullet time into the fast paced moments of free for all action. Get stylish kills, customize your special abilities, and choose the perfect combination of items for yourself in Double Action.','Shooter','Windows','Double Action Factory ','Double Action Factory ','2014-10-23','Windows XP ','1.7 GHz ','512 MB RAM','?','5 GB available space'),(242,187,'Pox Nora','A multiplayer online game that combines a collectible card game with a turn-based strategy game.','If you’re looking for a turn-­based strategy game that encompasses the elements of tabletop miniatures, fantasy RPG and collectible card game, look no further than Pox Nora. Developed and published by Desert Owl Games LLC, Pox Nora combines great 2D graphics with endless adventure. Players take their deck of cards, known as Runes, and go on an adventure in countless single player campaigns, and skirmish against the game’s AI; and if you’re looking for a multiplayer experience, Pox Nora has that too, with PvP match ups. Public decks are available to unlock with gold, or by playing the faction walk through campaigns and if you like Pox Nora, you can expand your deck options by purchasing additional rune packs that will give you access to more Champions, Spells, Relics and Equipment. But don’t worry ­ if you’re not looking to spend money, that’s okay. Pox Nora is completely free to play.\r\n\r\nPox Nora allows you to build decks from eight unique factions through full or split faction play and when you build your collection of runes over time you will be able to customize your decks with the Rune Manager. You can even trade in runes with other community members or build them with the Rune Forge. For the more competitive among us, you are able to join in draft tournaments to win prizes, and are able to save up and send virtual gold that you earn by playing the game, to get additional characters and more in the game’s Marketplace.','Card Game','Windows','Desert Owl Games LLC ','Desert Owl Games LLC ','2014-10-15',' Windows XP/Vista/7/8','500 MHZ CPU or Greater','512 MB of RAM','NVIDIA or ATI Video Card with 64MB of VRam, with current video drivers','200MB of hard drive space'),(243,404,'Tribal Wars 2','The sequel to the classic city-building strategy game Tribal Wars! ','Published by InnoGames, Tribal Wars 2 is a browser based strategy MMO game that allows players to rule over a castle in a medieval kingdom plagued by perpetual war. The land is brimming with nights and barbarians in this sequel to the online city-building strategy game Tribal Wars. The goal is to expand your kingdom and defend it from enemy players in this real-time PvP-driven world. Players can progress through the game in various different fashions depending on what units they decide to recruit. To conquer the world, players can exercise diplomacy and forge alliances to defend themselves against opponents, or break alliances and defeat other players in battle.\r\n\r\nYour kingdom exists under the constant threat of enemy players that can occur regardless of whether you’re logged in. The MMORTS game allows players to engage in strategic battles, requiring them to choose the proper units for the situation, defend from attacks and launch counter-attacks. You can also recruit spies to analyze your enemy’s defenses. Other players can do the same, however, so be sure to strategically launch countermeasures to ensure you are prepared for anything.','Strategy','Web Browser','InnoGames','InnoGames','2014-09-02',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(244,192,'WAKFU','A 2D tactical turn-based fantasy MMORPG developed by Ankama Games, in conjunction with Square Enix.','Wakfu is a free to play 2D tactical turn-based fantasy MMORPG developed by Ankama Games, in conjunction with Square Enix. WAKFU features a robust and diverse class system and strategic, turn based gameplay. To end the description there would do the game an injustice though as WAFKU also boasts a more “persistent” type world in that killed enemies or gathered resources might never appear again.\r\n\r\nThe game’s two dimensional, anime art style has spawned a series of anime shows and comic books. In game, players can take part in crafting, PvP (also turn based), and even mold the world they play in. Farm and replenish the land, or take what you want and leave nothing for others, the choice is yours. WAKFU’s in game systems extend even deeper though as players compete to win over others in a bid to become Governor in player led elections.\r\n\r\nUpon creating a character, players are quickly given all of their class’s abilities very early in game and progression is left to the player’s own desires. Skill up certain abilities the way you want to play and at your own pace.\r\n\r\nWhile WAKFU is technically free-to-play, this title certainly benefits from a subscription as much of the game can feel limited if you are not paying the subscription fee. The subscription costs are low when compared to most subscription based MMORPGs, but players will want to check out the free portion of the game a bit before deciding if the game’s unique style and systems are worth your hard earned cash.','MMORPG','Windows','Ankama Games','Ankama Studio','2014-09-19','Windows XP SP3 or higher ','Pentium IV 2.8 GHz or equivalent ','1 GB RAM ','GeForce 4Ti or equivalent ','1500 MB available space '),(245,193,'Infinity Wars','A MMO trading card game, Build up your decks and customize them with tons of factional cards! ','Infinity Wars: Animated Trading Card Game is an MMO trading card game published by Lightmare Studios. Build up your decks and customize them with tons of factional cards to forge an empire. Go through the storyline or compete against other players in PvP matches.\r\n\r\nLearn everything there is to know about the game’s five factions by completing the very extensive campaign. As you complete the campaign you will earn new cards and decks to use later on. Whichever faction you choose to play as will determine your play style. Some factions focus on attacking other player’s morale while others set up impenetrable defenses.\r\n\r\nThe matches take place in a simultaneous turn-based system where you have to predict what your opponent will do. You divide the playing field into four zones and each of them require special attention to defeat the other player. Once you have mastered Infinity Wars take your game to the next level and challenge other players in the competitive PvP scene that is available. You can earn rewards and glory by competing in the competitive PvP matches.\r\n\r\nInfinity Wars: Animated Trading Card Game is an MMO that focuses on building up a deck of cards and predicting enemy’s movements to defeat them in battles.','Card Game','Windows','Lightmare Studios','Lightmare Studios','2014-09-05','Windows XP or later ','?','1 GB','Graphics card with DirectX 9 capabilities.','5 GB'),(246,195,'Divine Souls','A action-based MMORPG in a fantasy world with magic and technology. ','Divine Souls is an action-based MMORPG with real-time combat combos developed by GamePrix. You are placed into a fantasy world where advanced technologies and magic coexist. Choose from different classes and battle in PvE and PvP arenas using your technology, or your magic, to conquer all.\r\n\r\nWhen you start the game you are able to choose from four different classes. The Fighter, a melee class that can soak a bit of damage, The Slasher, a melee class that focuses on dishing out the damage, the Mage, a ranged class that will deal tons of damage at a distance, or the Priest, a support class that will make sure everyone stays alive.\r\n\r\nYour goal in Divine Souls is to wade through instance after instance clearing areas that are littered with monsters and always have an epic boss battle waiting at the end. Or if PvP is more your speed take to the PvP arenas and show off your player killing skills there, get rewards for the higher you progress in the ranks.','MMORPG','Windows','Suba Games ','GamePrix ','2014-08-15','Windows XP or later ','Single-Core 2.4 GHz or faster ','1 GB RAM ','GeForce 7 Series or equivalent or later','4 GB available space'),(247,196,'Cubic Castles','A free to play 3D Platforming and a open world building game.','Cubic Castles is a free to play online 3D platforming and a open world voxel building game. In this massively multiplayer persistent world you can build anything you want using cubes and other items!\r\n\r\nExplore worlds made by other players or find a plot of land and start creating! Crafting is intuitive, just drag your raw resources and tools into a workbench to see what you can build. Build anything you can dream up and explore with other players or create parkour challenges with crazy obstacles like mechanical spikes, lava, quicksand and more.\r\n\r\nIn Cubic Castles you can create your own unique look with shirts, hats, glasses and more!','MMO','Windows','Cosmic Cow LLC','Cosmic Cow LLC','2014-08-13','Windows 7','Core 2 Duo or higher. Athlon 64 or higher','4 GB RAM','1024x768, DirectX 10','50 MB'),(248,198,'Creativerse','Playful Corporation enters the sandbox, voxel world with their free-to-play title Creativers.','Playful Corporation enters the sandbox, voxel world with their free-to-play title Creativerse. Upon first glance it may be easy to dismiss this game as simply another Minecraft clone but players looking for something a bit different will want to give this title a shot.\r\n\r\nYes, You’ll be gathering materials and building things. Yes, you’ll be upgrading your armor. However, with a wide variety of unique systems (such as taming animals and caring for them to earn extra loot or even farming) there’s something a bit different in Creativerse.\r\n\r\nThe voxel based world is colorful and vibrant and the game’s multiplayer options make it very easy to pair up with some friends on PvE, PvP, or even RP servers. Each world has a wide variety of biomes to explore, ancient technology to find, and recipes to construct so simply getting the best gear is only the beginning of the game.\r\n\r\nIf you were turned off by the game’s initial stumbles with Early Access and their cash shop, you should know that the cash shop has been converted to a cosmetic only shop and the initial complaints of required purchasing are no longer the case.','MMO','Windows','Playful Corporation','Playful Corporation','2014-08-12','Windows Vista SP2, Windows 7, Windows 8 ','Intel Core 2 Quad Q6600, 2.4 GHz / AMD Phenom II X4 920 Quad-Core 2.8 GHz or better ','4 GB RAM','GeForce GTX 8800/ ATI Radeon HD 2900XT ','2 GB available space '),(249,199,'Royal Quest','A free to play fantasy MMORPG game with unique PvPvE locations, PvP Arenas, Battlegrounds and Castle Sieges. ','Royal Quest is a free to play fantasy MMORPG game with several unique PvPvE locations, PvP Arenas, Battlegrounds and Castle Sieges. You will get a fresh MMO experience in Royal Quest ­ developed by Katauri and published by 1C Online Games, the creators of Space Rangers and King’s Bounty series.\r\n\r\nRoyal Quest gives you an innovative elemental battle system which allows players to exploit enemy weaknesses by properly choosing which weapons and skills to use against the target, while using game mechanics that are easy to learn (including an automatic character upgrade system), and offer a deep and challenging experience later in the game.\r\n\r\nWhen you play Royal Quest, you will discover over 100 outdoor locations and multi­floor dungeons while you complete nearly 1000 quests designed for both group and single players. You will be able to fight more than 200 extraordinary monsters, each with its own rare card with special attributes and dive into extensive skills and talents system and combine them in a unique way for each of the 8 classes!\r\n\r\nWhen you get lonely, Royal Quest allows you to summon pets that follow you around and collect loot for you, compete with other players in PvP Arenas, Battlegrounds and Castle Sieges, as well as earn the right to control a Castle and its surrounding areas with your Guild! You will compete in PvP Arenas, Battlegrounds and Castle Sieges and gather powerful Shadow Gear by winning over other players in special PvPvE zones!','MMORPG','Windows','1C Online Games ','Katauri ','2014-08-06','Windows 7/ Vista / XP SP3 ','Intel Core 2 Duo / AMD Athlon X2 64 3.0 Ghz ','2 GB RAM ','512Mb NVIDIA GeForce 9500GT / ATI Radeon HD 3450',' 5 GB available space'),(250,348,'Bleach Online','A free to play 2D browser based MMORPG based on Bleach, the popular manga and anime series.','Based on the popular Japanese manga and anime series, Bleach Online is a free-to-play 2D browser-based MMORPG that immerses you in the world of Ichigo Kurosaki and all of the Soul Reapers.\r\n\r\nComing from GoGames, Bleach Online offers a storyline based on what fans of the series know from the manga and anime. They’ll be able to pick from three unique classes that all offer their own advantages and abilities.\r\n\r\nFor players who like to stay busy while playing their MMORPGs, Bleach Online can be played in AFK Mode so that their characters can level up even when they’re not actively playing thanks to the automated combat system.\r\n\r\nBut don’t feel like you’re going to have to go it alone. Bleach Online players can recruit iconic characters from the manga and anime series to join their party out in the field to really take the fight to the Hollows with up five partners.\r\n\r\nAnd for an extra fun addition, Bleach Online allows players to put some of the more notable characters in bikinis in the self-styled Bikini Game.\r\n\r\nIf you love Bleach then Bleach Online is definitely worth a look.','MMORPG','Web Browser','GoGames','GoGames','2014-07-14',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(251,209,'Freestyle2: Street Basketball','A free to play MMO street basketball game. Team up with the best street ballers! ','Freestyle2: Street Basketball is a free to play MMO street basketball game. Take to the streets for some 3v3 basketball in Joycity’s Freestyle2: Street Basketball. Improving on the original in almost every way, Freestyle2 sports a unique art style, clever music integration of a unique Hip Hop soundtrack, and the bragging rights of being the top basketball MMO on the market…because there’s just so many of them.\r\n\r\nChoose from 1 of 5 positions (Center, Power Forward, Small Forward, Shooting Guard, and Point Guard) and quest your way through the streets using your jump shot, fly set up, dunk, or absurd arcade shot to gain experience and develop your character through choosing from over 30 different skills to impact your gameplay. Your character has a myriad of options available to customize their look using outfits, hairstyles, shoes, and more.\r\n\r\nWhile the game itself may sound simple, (the tutorial will take you through just about every skill in the game) the gameplay becomes addictive when you team up with other players, play in tournaments, and discover just how much teamwork will be needed to topple the best teams on the street.','Sports','Windows','Joycity','Joycity','2014-06-20','Window XP ','P4 2.8 GHZ ','1 GB RAM ','GEFORCE 7600 GT 512MB','1500 MB available space'),(252,211,'GunZ 2: The Second Duel','A free-to-play multiplayer Third Person Shooter and follow up to the successful GunZ: The Duel. ','GunZ 2: The Second Duel is the free-to-play fast-paced Third Person Shooter (TPS) follow up to the successful GunZ: The Duel. Released in 2013/2014 by MAIET Entertainment, the property is now owned by MattietSoft and is run mostly through player hosted servers.\r\n\r\nGunZ 2 features 6 classes for players to choose from. Each class offers its own unique skills and abilities so players are free to take on the role of more defense based characters or run and gun type heroes based on personal preference.\r\n\r\nMovement in game is augmented through the addition of dashing, wall running, and various gymnastic tumbling moves. These moves add a layer of mobility not found in most other third person shooters and allows melee combat to play a larger role in the game.\r\n\r\nThere are currently 5 game modes available and 6 maps available for play. Modes range from typical death matches to objective based gameplay. GunZ 2 also offers a PvE mode where players can band together in small groups and play through story missions in an attempt to take down the Adam Corporation.','Shooter','Windows','MAIET Entertainme','MAIET Entertainme','2014-05-01','XP / Vista / 7 / 8','Intel Dual Core or 2.4 GHz AMD CPU','4 GB','GeForce 8600 / 9600 GT / ATI Radeon HD 2600/3600','4 GB'),(253,213,'Archeblade','A free-to-play PvP-based multiplayer action game based on a Korean Fantasy Novel.','ArcheBlade is a team-based fighting game powered by Unreal 3 and developd by CodeBrush Games. Choose from a large selection of characters and take control of a great combination fighting system to come out on top in ArcheBlade.\r\n\r\nChoose from a ton of unique and exciting characters to fight with in ArcheBlade, each of these characters have their own unique fighting styles with combo attacks that can be utilized by pressing the left and right mouse buttons to string together flurries of attacks. You can also execute moves by jumping and dashing.\r\n\r\nWhile you are fighting your character will have a rage meter that is slowing filling up when you receive and deliver damage. Once that rage meter fills up your character is able to unleash its special ability that can range from heals to powerful area of effect attacks that deal massive amounts of damage. Choose different gameplay styles, like forward bruiser or ranged assassin, to deal with all sorts of situations.\r\n\r\nArcheBlade is a team-based fighting game that is powered by Unreal 3 and offers a ton of unique characters to fight with. Execute amazing combos by executing button combinations similar to those from classic fighting games like Street Fighter.','Fighting','Windows','CodeBrush Games','CodeBrush Games','2014-04-25',' Windows XP 32bit','Intel Core 2 Duo 1.86 GHz, AMD Athlon 64 X2 2GHz','2 GB RAM','ATI HD3850, GTX250','1500 MB HD space'),(254,214,'Villagers and Heroes','A free-to-play fantasy sandbox 3D MMORPG that has plenty to offer gamers.','Villagers and Heroes (previously known as A Mystical Land) is a free-to-play fantasy sandbox 3D MMORPG that has plenty to offer gamers. Based more on crafting than combat, Villagers and Heroes gives players who are looking to build their own worlds without the threat of combat create to their heart’s content.\r\n\r\nThe focus of Villagers and Heroes is player built communities, where players can build a village that matches their wants and desires. Players can customize their characters to an in-depth degree that other MMORPGs lack (such as backstory).\r\n\r\nCrafting is essential in Villagers and Heroes, and players can focus their talents on one area of skill or even master them all. And if players want to challenge themselves again after having built world they’re proud of, they can reset their character back to Level 1 and begin fresh.\r\n\r\nThough lighthearted in tone and atmosphere, players who want to build their world in a relaxing and supportive environment will find much to love about Villagers and Heroes.','MMORPG','Windows','Mad Otter Games','Mad Otter Games','2014-04-17','Windows XP / 7 / 8 / 10','Pentium D / Athlon 64 X2','2 GB','On board graphics',' 3 GB'),(255,215,'Hex','HEX combines roleplaying aspects of a MMO with the collectible and strategic gameplay of a Trading Card Game.','Hex: Shards of Fate is a free to play MMO trading card game (TCG) that allows customization and skill to determine the victor. Players can build and upgrade their decks and battle one another! Hex offers an engaging online card battling game that many players will swiftly become engrossed in.\r\n\r\nHex starts off with an intuitive tutorial that helps new players get accustomed to the game. Players will learn basic rules and strategies as well as what rewards they can expect from winning.\r\n\r\nOnce the tutorial is out of the way, Hex players can engage in card battle with NPCs and other players, strengthening their card deck with each victory. Every player is a champion hero who has access to a special talent that can be called upon in the heat of pitched card battles.\r\n\r\nPlayers can also compete in special PvE tournaments in the Frost Ring Arena of Hex. Rewards vary between stronger and rare cards to in-game gold that players can spend at the shop.','Card Game','Windows','Hex Entertainment, Gameforge','Cryptozoic Entertainment','2014-04-11','Windows XP 32 bit','Pentium D 805 2.67GHz or Athlon 64 X2 Dual Core 3600+','2 GB GB RAM','GeForce 6800 GT or Radeon X1600 Pro 512MB','3 GB Free Space'),(256,405,'Pocket Starships','A free-to-play cross-platform space combat MMO from SPYR games.','Pocket Starships is a free-to-play cross-platform space combat MMO from SPYR games. The game is playable on a variety of mobile devices as well as on PC via browsers, allowing it to be played anywhere using true cross-platform play.\r\n\r\nIt features PvP as well as co-op and a robust quest system that allows players to advance their rank. The PvP offers players a league system with 1v1, 3v3, and 5v5 matches.\r\n\r\nIn addition, there is a full crafting system that allows players to build and upgrade most items in the game. This includes ships, weapons, and more.','Strategy','Web Browser','Spyr','Spyr','2014-02-28',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(257,409,'Sparta: War of Empires','A 2D browser-based MMORTS in which players must exercise their city-management skills to construct and upgrade different structures and troops.','Sparta: War of Empires is a free to play 2D browser-based MMORTS in which players must exercise their city-management skills to construct and upgrade different structures and troops to conquer new territory in fifth century Greece. Recruit various different upgradeable military units to incorporate into your soon-to-be vast army to defend your city-state and conquer Xerxes’ forces.\r\n\r\nIn this real-time strategy game, voice-acted King Leonidas serves as your guide to Ancient Greece. The game boasts great quality graphics, a medium player base and voiced tutorials. Players can form allegiances with their friends to vanquish rival groups. Sparta: War of Empires offers diplomatic elements that players can utilize to obtain resources, which you will require to further expand your Spartan city-state. These diplomatic endeavors include trading and borrowing war materials from your allies, or stealing them from your enemies.','Strategy','Web Browser','Plarium','Plarium','2014-03-13',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(258,221,'Lucent Heart','A free to play MMORPG with a match making system that helps players find their soulmates.','Lucent Heart is a 3D fantasy MMORPG with a unique Zodiac system that plays an important role in your character are you progress through the game. It features cute anime style graphics and the game encourages social interaction between other players and relationship building through its soulmate system.\r\n\r\nThere is a built in match making system in Lucent Heart that helps players find their soulmates somewhere in the game. Let Cupid find love for you as you are allowed to have three different soul mates in game, but only one of them you can marry. Soulmates will earn shared experience, special emotes, and a few more things to make their experience better than those without Soulmates.\r\n\r\nChoose to either be a Mage or a Fighter that can advance at level 10 to another class and then can advance two more times at level 36. With that being a total of eight different classes to choose from Lucent Heart has a great class selection with a good amount of customization.\r\n\r\nLucent Heart has a strong focus on the social interactive side of gaming. Fall in love in Lucent Heart by finding your Soulmate and then getting married for special treatment within the game.','MMORPG','Windows','Suba Games','Playcoco (Subsidiary of Gamania)','2014-01-10','XP / Vista / 7 / 8 / 10','Pentium 4 1.3 GHz or better','512 MB','GeForce 3 Series / Radeon 8500 or better','2 GB'),(259,376,'League of Angels','A free to play 2D browser-based fantasy MMORPG with turn-based combat.','Fight to save the world from eternal darkness in League of Angels (LOA), a 2D browser-based fantasy MMORPG with strategy elements and familiar gameplay mechanics.\r\n\r\nLeague of Angels features turn-based combat, lots of content and mini-games built around the game’s theme. Players can choose between three classes as well as which gender they want their character to be.\r\n\r\nYour mount is one of your best ways to achieve a stat boost in League of Angels, but remember that a lot of the content within this game is pay-to-win.\r\n\r\nPlayers can also make use of the AFK system in League of Angels while multitasking, making character grinding easy and perfectly contained in the background.\r\n\r\nFor players looking for an interesting take on angelic myth, League of Angels is an interesting pick to give consideration to. Join other players in an effort to rescue the Angels that have been imprisoned by the evil Suurde!','MMORPG','Web Browser','GTArcade','Youzu Interactive','2013-12-10',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(260,424,'Crystal Saga','A free to play 2D browser-based MMORPG that allows players to explore the land of Vidalia.','Crystal Saga is a free to play 2.5D browser-based MMORPG that allows players to explore the land of Vidalia and defeat enemies like dangerous beasts and barbarians using five distinct classes: knight, mage, rogue, priest and ranger. In traditional MMORPG-style, the game requires a strategic combination of tank, healer and DPS to defeat enemies. The game offers standard fetch, gather and kill quests for players to complete to earn new items, weapons and mounts.\r\n\r\nAs you through the persistent game, you will earn souls that can be utilized to customize your character’s skills. Players can also earn mounts and fly around Starglade atop a dragon or a phoenix, and train monsters to become dangerous battle partners. Each class in this browser MMO can equip a pair of “battle wings” that, with each additional level, take on a new look and upgrade the player’s stats.\r\n\r\nThe vast world of Vidalia includes dozens of PvP and PvE zones, more than 50 outdoor maps and several dungeons and battlegrounds. Players can also battle against each other in five different PvP modes, earning new legendary items as their reward. The game is visually appealing, and the saturated colors help make Vidalia an immersive fantasy world with a large player base.','MMORPG','Web Browser','Aeria, R2Games','R2Games','2013-11-20',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(261,411,'Soldiers Inc.','A free to play 2D top-down browser based MMORTS game.','Soldiers Inc. is a free to play 2D top-down browser based MMORTS game set in an apocalyptic scenario. Players must complete various objectives in order to expand their meager bases into sprawling, formidable forces.\r\n\r\nBoasting retro graphics, Soldier’s Inc. allows you to expand your borders and improve your forces with various upgradeable units boasting skill trees. The strategy game offers three distinct types of units: defensive, offensive and recon. Send in your recon troops to analyze your foes before engaging them in battle. Additionally players are also encouraged to PvP against their neighbors, players can form alliances with other player to obliterate your opponents and raid them for their resources.\r\n\r\nZandia is a war-torn world in which players become Commander and take instructions from a mysterious character codenamed Mr. Black. Hired by a black ops organization known as the Syndicate, you must fight other players for territorial control in order to secure resources. Build your army, construct a base, upgrade your units and prepare to do battle.','Strategy','Web Browser','Plarium Games','Plarium Games','2013-08-01',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(262,234,'Champions of Regnum','A free to play, realm versus realm fantasy MMORPG.','Champions of Regnum is a free to play, realm versus realm fantasy MMORPG published by NGD Studios. Fight over forts, castles, and create your own realm with the strong PvP experience that the game provides. Make use of NPC guards and even dragons as you fight to take control of the six gems and be granted a wish by the golden dragon.\r\n\r\nPvP has a strong focus in Champions of Regnum. You can choose to take part in round-the-clock territorial wars, open PvP, or arena battles each with their own rewards and prestige associated with them. Every gem that you claim for your own realm will grant you a wish that can be used to negatively affect other realms or grant yours a bonus.\r\n\r\nChoose between multiple disciplines and after you have leveled up choose to specialize into one of the unique builds that discipline offers. You can level up in many different ways: gaining experience through quests, grinding, capturing territory, or delivering letters for your realm.\r\n\r\nAnother great thing many people will overlook is that Champions of Regnum is not hard on computers so most people using a modern computer should be able to run the game, even Linux users shouldn’t have a problem.\r\n\r\nMake your realm stronger by gathering gems to ask the golden dragon to grant you a wish, or use that wish to negatively affect your enemy’s realms.','MMORPG','Windows','NGD Studios','NGD Studios','2013-02-27','Windows XP ','Core2Duo','1024 MB','Shader Model 2.0 and 256 MB RAM: NVIDIA GeForce 6600 or ATI 2600 ','4 GB'),(263,414,'Rail Nation','A free to play 2D browser-based train simulation strategy MMO game.','Rail Nation is a free to play 2D browser-based train simulation strategy MMO game, published by Travian Games and developed by Bright Future. Rail Nation offers players the ability to choose between the opposing factions Eastern Atlantic Railway or the Western Pacific Railroad, each seeking to control the rail system and expand their network of trains as they progress through the game.\r\n\r\nPlayers initially pick a hub city and start with a basic train route. Then they must gather resources by planning their routes, delivering goods and building additional tracks to connect their network to more and more American cities. After starting with steam engines, players can research more advance technologies and upgrade to diesel and electric trains to enhance their networks’ capabilities.\r\n\r\nThis train simulation game spans across six eras as server time passes. Eras last two weeks, and will progress as server time passes, regardless of whether people are actively playing. The game’s cities are composed of groups of players, and the final era is a competition between the 10 top-ranked cities. Each era offers more trains to choose from and subsequently more ways to deliver goods for profit. Players can build and upgrade structures in their train station houses including a laboratories, lottery buildings and engine sheds. The game boasts historical accuracy, a decent player base and loads of content to keep players engaged.','Strategy','Web Browser','Bright Future','Travian Games','2013-01-13',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(264,240,'Epic Cards Battle','A free to play online strategic trading card game with dozens of cards and five factions. ','Epic Cards Battle is a free to play online strategic trading card game (TCG) from momoStorm Entertainment. Only the players who collect the strongest cars and assemble the most powerful decks will emerge victorious.\r\n\r\nUsing cunning strategy, players will assemble their decks through cards bought or collected in the Campaign in Epic Cards Battle. There is five factions and 3 kinds of card types: Unit, Spell, Trigger. Players must choose their tactics wisely, as they will have no input into how battles between NPCs and other players play out.\r\n\r\nPlayers can purchase cards in Epic Cards Battle with Rubies, the in-game currency, or they can pay money for Diamonds and get access to some of the most powerful cards in the game.\r\n\r\nBuilding a strong deck is the key to success in Epic Cards Battle, so choose carefully before the battles commence. Epic Cards Battle is available on PC as well as iOS and Android.','Card Game','Windows','momoStorm Entertainment','momoStorm','2013-01-29','Windows XP / 7 / 8 / 10','Any 2 GHz CPU','512 MB','Any GPU','300 MB'),(265,349,'Big Farm','A friendly browser-based farming simulation MMO game!','GoodGame Big Farm is a free to play browser-based 2D multiplayer farming simulation game. The fun is always fresh and the lessons homegrown in Goodgame Studios’ Big Farm! This casual strategy game is a perfect MMO game for all ages to enjoy!\r\n\r\nBig Farm starts out by telling you that dear old Uncle George has left you his beloved farm. Unfortunately, as much as Uncle George loved the farm, he couldn’t take care of it like he wanted to. It’s up to you to take control of this decrepit farmyard and turn it into something Uncle George would have been proud of!\r\n\r\nIf you’ve played games like FarmVille or Empire then the mechanics of Big Farm will feel like greeting an old friend again. You’ll use your smarts to repair the farm and make it shine. Along with help from your family and nearby neighbors, you’ll turn economics to your advantage and learn what it takes to make a farm a prosperous piece of land.\r\n\r\nThrowing in the adorable graphics of the farm buildings, the crops, and the animals, it’s easy to see why Goodgame Big Farm is an amusing and addictive strategy game. Don’t waste any more time in the city! Head out to the fields and turn Uncle George’s dream into reality in Big Farm!','Strategy','Web Browser','GoodGame Studios','GoodGame Studios','2012-10-29',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(266,416,'Wartune','A 2D browser-based Strategy MMORPG with classic turn based RPG features.','Published by R2 Games, Wartune is a 2D browser-based strategy MMO with classic RPG elements to deliver an interesting experience. Your gameplay experience is shaped by your choice of class. Classes include knights, mages and archers. The game features strategic city-building and turn-based combat, both PvE and PvP.\r\n\r\nThe game boasts a high player base, special events, daily quests and massive, thousand-player boss battles. Featuring single and multiplayer dungeons, Wartune requires players to expand their cities by obtaining resources and creating structures.','MMORPG','Web Browser','R2 Games','7Th Road','2012-10-25',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(267,417,'Dino Storm','A free-to-play 3D MMO with cowboys, dinosaurs, and laser guns.','Dino Storm is a unique free-to-play 3D MMO with RPG elements that gives players cowboys, dinosaurs, and lasers… oh my! Players looking for all-out, nonsensical and entertaining gameplay will want to try Dino Storm.\r\n\r\nDino Storm is like the Old West, only cowboys ride dinosaurs instead of horses and fire lasers instead of bullets. And just like any cowboy worth their spurs, Dino Storm features a unique fame system that helps players build a name for themselves.\r\n\r\nThe dinosaur is the player’s trusted mount in Dino Storm, and it’s their best friend out in the wilderness. Players will take on hundreds of quests with their Jurassic steed right by their side. There’s also the option to join bands of other laser-shooting player cowboys and take on the challenges together.\r\n\r\nPlayers will protect the towns from vicious outlaws in Dino Storm, and danger is never far from any player who is looking to do what’s right with a laser in one hand while riding atop a dinosaur.\r\n\r\nDino Storm was born from a unique combination and it looks like the creativity of this game is anything but extinct.','MMORPG','Web Browser','Splitscreen S.','Splits. S','2012-09-12',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(268,418,'The Settlers Online','A free to play city building MMORTS based on the popular Settlers series.','The Settlers Online: Castle Empire is a free to play 2D browser based city building MMORTS, developed and published by Ubisoft, players can construct their own cities from and manage its population. This strategy game features an in-depth resource-management system that requires players to think carefully about how they use their materials. To expand your initially pitiful, barren island into a thriving city, you must recruit specialists from your tavern to fend of bandits and explore new territory. Resources are far from infinite; players will constantly have to explore in order to expand their settlement.\r\n\r\nUnlike other resource-management games, The Settlers Online: Castle Empire features an interesting economic system that requires players to foster an effective city infrastructure and pay close attention to the economic aspects of their settlements. The strategy game features a decent player base, high-quality graphics and a myriad of quests to complete in order to progress through the game. You can also trade resources with other players, or take control of other player’s cities.','Strategy','Web Browser','Ubisoft','Blue Byte','2012-09-11',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(269,24,'Counter-Strike: Global Offensive','The popular multiplayer shooter from Valve. ','Counter-Strike: Global Offensive is the popular multi-player shooter from Valve. One of the most popular games in esports, CSGO is primarily an objective-based shooter wherein two teams compete in a variety of game modes to complete an objectives ranging from defusing a bomb to rescuing hostages.\r\n\r\nThere are nine game modes, including: competitive, casual, deathmatch, arms race, demolition, wingman, flying scountsman, weapons course, and (most recently) a battle royale mode titled Danger Zone. As with most competitive online shooters, CSGO supports matchmaking.\r\n\r\nDue to the long life of the game, players have a wide selection of weapons to choose from when playing. The game also offers a solid spectator mode.\r\n\r\n','Shooter','Windows','Valve','Valve, Hidden Path Entertainment','2012-08-21','Windows® 7/Vista/XP','Intel® Core™ 2 Duo E6600 or AMD Phenom™ X3 8750 processor or better','2 GB RAM','Video card must be 256 MB or more and should be a DirectX 9-compatible with support for Pixel Shader 3.0','15 GB available space'),(270,453,'Gotham City Impostors','A free to play multiplayer FPS that pits vigilantes dressed up like Batman against criminals dressed up like the Joker','Gotham City Impostors is a free to play multiplayer First Person Shooter (FPS) that pits vigilantes dressed up like Batman against criminals dressed up like the Joker in open warfare on the streets of Gotham City\r\n\r\nGotham City Impostors does not have rigid character classes and lets you play the way you want. You’ll be able to choose the guns, gadgets and even the hairdos that fit your personality and play style. It doesn’t matter if you want to be a mighty muscleman on roller skates or a lithe lassie packing a rocket launcher.\r\n\r\nGotham City Impostors features a robust leveling up system that lets you unlock all the items required to make your impostor as crazy as you desire. Whether you prefer to develop your impostor by proving your prowess in solo challenges designed to test your skills and reflexes or by battling your way to the top of the scoreboard in several over­-the-­top multiplayer modes.\r\n\r\nGotham City has gone insane! Batman is up to his pointy ears in unwanted “helpers” who are determined to dish out their own blood thirsty brand of vigilante justice in his name (and image). Meanwhile, a small army of self appointed junior Jokerz have turned the streets of Gotham into a barmy battlefield of bullets, bodies, and bear traps. As you can probably tell, this might not end well.','Shooter','Windows','Warner Bros. Interactive Entertainment','Monolith Productions, Inc.','2012-08-31',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(271,249,'RPG MO','A nostalgic free MMORPG reminiscent of old-school RPG\'s like Ultima and Runescape.','RPG MO is a free-to-play retro-style sandbox MMORPG featuring pixilated graphics and wide, colorful world in which players can level up various combat abilities, or take a break from the hack-and-slash and focus on crafting skills. This 2D open-world MMORPG is available on PC via browser, client and Steam. RPG MO is also available on smartphones and tablets.\r\n\r\nRPG MO is a nostalgic sandbox experience reminiscent of old-school RPG’s like Ultima and Runescape. In combat, players can switch between various stances to level different skills. Collect powerful weapons and armor and train melee skills to become a formidable warrior, or put down the sword and level magic skills to discover new, dangerous spells.\r\n\r\nAdditionally, players can take on the role of a merchant collecting materials through mining and chopping wood to level crafting abilities and create valuable items to sell to other players. The game boasts a wide range of over a dozen skills players can train in with no level caps. Players can choose to specialize, focusing on specific skills, or level them all up. Players can also build their own homes, which are visible to other players.\r\n\r\nThe game offers various PvE quests, and allows players to collaborate with each other for group dungeon quests. Players can also fight each other in PvP zones. Boasting a large, loyal player base and consistent updates, RPG MO serves as a fun, addicting does of pixilated nostalgia.','MMORPG','Windows, Web Browser','Marxnet','Marxnet','2012-07-18',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(272,262,'Digimon Masters Online','A free to play 3D MMORPG based on the popular Digimon franchise.','Digimon Masters Online (DMO) is a free to play MMORPG set in the Digimon universe that allows you to collect different Digimon and battle with them throughout the vast Digimon anime universe. Players will control one of the four main Tamers from the Digimon Data Squad and you will adventure out into the Digimon world.\r\n\r\nYou are able to choose from one of the four main Tamers of the Digimon Data Squad: Marcus Damon, Thomas H. Norstein, Yoshino Fujieda, and Keenan Crier. Although the avatar is one of the four main Tamers from the anime series you are able to customize your name and modify the appearance of the Avatar. Once you select your Tamer you are allowed to choose a Partner Digimon, your main Digimon throughout the game.\r\n\r\nYou are able to acquire more Digimon besides your Partner Digimon by hatching Mercenary Digimon from Digi-Eggs using an incubator. These Mercenary Digimon will help you in battles and quests along your path through the Digi-World.\r\n\r\nBattling is done in real-time in Digimon Masters, your Digimon will battle other Digimon using special attacks that use up their Digi-soul meter, the energy, in battle. If your Digi-soul meter runs low, then you will only be able to use standard attacks during the rest of the battle. If another player happens to come by your battle since they are happening in real time they are able to join in and assist you, or they can just sit back and watch you suffer.','MMORPG','Windows','MOVE ON USA CO.','Move Games Co., Ltd.','2011-10-20','Windows XP or better','Intel Pentium 4 or AMD equivalent','256 MB','GeForce FX5200 or better',' 2GB'),(273,423,'Steel Legions','A free to play 3d browser based tank game with fast-paced tactical battles! ','Steel Legions is a free to play 3d browser based tank game with fast-paced tactical battles. You take control over a heavy steel Steampunk war machine in an alternative history, where four empires acrimoniously rival for power, land and resources.\r\n\r\nPlayer choose their side and start to either take on missions against players of the other factions to gain their own level. Or they hunt Marauders, which they steal resources from needed to improve and maintain their war machines. Switching between dynamic, fast-paced PvP action, a variety of game modes and long term development makes this browser game a fun installment in PvP online games.','Shooter','Web Browser','Splitscreen Studios','Splitscreen Studios','2011-06-15',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(274,60,'Brink','A free-to-play first-person-shoot developed by Splash \r\nDamage and published by Bethesda Softworks. ','Brink is a free-to-play first-person-shoot developed by Splash Damage and published by Bethesda Softworks. The game blends, single-player, co-op, and multiplayer modes into a single experience. In Brink, players occupy the Ark, a floating city built by men. The city is on the brink of war, despite being built as a self-sufficient, 100% green habitat.\r\n\r\nBrink allows players to customize their characters to create a unique appearance as well as build. Players can fight their way through the single-player campaign or choose to go online and participate in co-op activities or engage in full-blown multiplayer action. Long time FPS players should feel right at home with Brink, as it features a control scheme common to the genre.\r\n\r\nBrink is available to play via Steam.','Shooter','Windows','Bethesda Softworks','Splash Damage','2011-05-09','Windows XP(SP3) or later','Intel Core 2 Duo 2.4GHz','2GB','NVIDIA 8800GS / ATI Radeon HD 2900 Pro or equivalent','8GB of free space'),(275,274,'GetAmped 2','A free to play fighting MMO, experience frantic battles up to 20 players.','GetAmped 2 is a free to play fighting MMO developed by CyberStep, Inc. You will choose from multiple different fighter classes and explore Wingdom city fighting other players. The main focus of GetAmped 2 is PvP but there are PvE aspects as well.\r\n\r\nChoose from multiple different playable classes that are all used to smash your opponents face in. Venture through Wingdom city challenges players to PvP battles and using the skills you have learned to battle your way to the top of the leaderboards. Customize your character as you level up with various weapons and accessories that make you even harder to defeat as you advance in experience.\r\n\r\nWhile the real focus of GetAmped 2 is PvP there is a PvE/Cooperative side of gameplay to it as well. You and other players can group up to take on the Guardian mode. Guardian mode is where you group up with four other players and battle against NPCs to try and reach the boss. Once you reach the end of the level and defeat the boss you are rewarded with various prizes that will either help your character advance in skill, or just make them look good.\r\n\r\nGetAmped 2 is a free to play fighter MMO that has a strong focus on PvP. Choose from tons of classes that are all focused around fighting and battle other players to be crowned the best PvPer in the city of Wingdom.','Fighting','Windows','CyberStep','CyberStep','2010-12-16','Windows XP / 7 / 8 / 10','Pentium 3 1.2 GHz or better','256 MB','Any GPU with 32MB VRAM','1 GB'),(276,277,'Aika Online','A free-to-play MMORPG with large scale PvP battles.','Aika Online is a free-to-play MMORPG developed by JoyImpact that is focused on PvP. It’s set in a large fantasy world that is home to many nations and it is up to you to make yours victorious.\r\n\r\nThere are five different nations in Aika Online. Players choose from six different classes: Warrior, Paladin, Rifleman, Dual Gunner, Warlock and Cleric. Each class has their very own unique set of skills. The combat is focused on leveling up, gaining new skills, and pressing the corresponding buttons to those skills to attack in the environment. There are thousands of quests that you can go on and you never have to go on these quests alone. You will be traveling with your companion that is known as a Pran. You are raising your Pran from its childhood and its attitudes and abilities will change depending upon how you treat it.\r\n\r\nThe main focus of Aiki Online is its PvP, there are massive battleground fights between 1000s of people in which you fight to obtain magical artifacts, control of territory, and the rights to call your nation the best. Aika Online has some good things going for it: Large scale PvP battles, enjoyable graphics and a good combat system.','MMORPG','Windows','HanbitSoft','JoyImpact','2010-08-27','Windows 2000 / XP / Vista','Pentium3 1GHz','512 MB','3D Accelerator with 128 MB','1GB'),(277,281,'Grand Fantasia','A free to play anime inspired 3D MMORPG with customizable characters and \r\ncompanions.','Grand Fantasia is a free to play 3D fantasy MMORPG with anime inspired graphics developed by Easyfun. Journey throughout the beautiful world with customizable characters and companions as you craft and quest your way through the game.\r\n\r\nBegin the game by customizing your character and choosing one of the five different starting classes. After you have chosen a class you get to customize your companion, a Sprite, that will be adventuring throughout the world with you. As you level up you are able to obtain job advancements in your class at level 15,30,65 and 85. At level 30 you also get the ability to choose another path and choose another class for your character to level up in.\r\n\r\nYour Sprite does more for you than just following you around and helping out in combat. Use your Sprite to forage and craft for you to make sure you have some extra gear to either equip for yourself or sell to some other players for a bit of extra cash. Your Sprites can even participate in PvP events against other Sprites to earn gold and fame.\r\n\r\nGrand Fantasia is a cute anime inspired game that has a great selection of customization from the character classes to the companions (Sprites) that you can collect along your adventure.','MMORPG','Windows','X-Legend Entertainment','X-Legend Entertainment','2009-12-01','XP / 2000 / Vista / 7 / 8','Intel Pentium 4 2.4 GHz or AMD Equivalent','512 MB','GeForce FX 5200 / ATI Radeon 9600','2 GB'),(278,425,'Grepolis','A free to play browser-based strategy MMORTS set in Ancient Greece.','The lands of Ancient Greece await the guiding hands of players who take on Grepolis, a browser-based MMORTS from InnoGames. Grepolis is built upon the traditional city-building gameplay mechanic, but if offers so much more than that.\r\n\r\nOne of the key pieces of Ancient Greek history was the worship of the gods of Olympus. Grepolis takes that a step further by giving players access to Divine Powers based on which Greek god they choose to worship.\r\n\r\nGrepolis also doesn’t limit players to Greek monuments. As players expand the borders of their ancient empires, they can construct the wonders of the Ancient world and place them wherever they want regardless of historic accuracy.\r\n\r\nBut what would be the fun of an MMORTS if it didn’t allow you to challenge other players? Grepolis features an innovating conquest and colonization mechanic that allows players to take over the cities and empires of others.\r\n\r\nAnd if your city should fall, Grepolis gives you the chance to begin anew in order to forge a stronger empire, perhaps in the hopes of one day reclaiming what was lost.\r\n\r\nPlayers can access Grepolis across browser and mobile devices at their leisure, meaning they can take their story of Ancient Greek conquest wherever they want.','Strategy','Web Browser','InnoGames','InnoGames','2009-12-08',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(279,287,'Twelve Sky 2','There’s a lot of world to explore in this fantasy MMORPG!','There’s a lot of world to explore in Twelve Sky 2, a fantasy MMORPG from MaynGames. Players will be set in an immersive in-game world that allows them to search the widest plains to the darkest corners.\r\n\r\nBased on Chinese culture, Twelve Sky 2 makes use of an underutilized theme in order to craft a unique gameplay experience. Players will choose one of three factions to be a part of, each faction determining the player’s appearance and which clan they’re from.\r\n\r\nPlayers in Twelve Sky 2 will also be able to utilize up to seven different skills for varied combat. When engaging in intense PvP combat against friends and foes, variety is one of the strongest keys to victory.\r\n\r\nTwelve Sky 2 will cause players to find their own path through the in-game world, but it is along such paths that adventure and glory is often found.','MMORPG','Windows','RedFox Games','SG Data','2009-09-09','Windows XP / 2000','Pentium III 800mhz','512 MB','GeForce 5200 or Radeon 7600 64 MB','3 GB'),(280,280,'WolfTeam','A free to play MMOFPS with a twist.','Wolf Team is a free to play tactical lobby-based multiplayer online FPS with a twist, the ability to switch between humans (guns) and werewolves (melee attacks) based on your situation. Players can freely switch between their human and wolf counterparts to give them situational advantages such as higher health or a vast arsenal of weaponry.\r\n\r\nIn Wolf Team, you enter into fast-paced FPS action with up to 15 other players. There are 15 different maps and seven game modes (including Conquest, Deathmatch or Destruction mode) with a wide variety of weapon options. The backstory of the game shows the player as a soldier sent to destroy some rogue experiments, other soldiers who had undergone mutation, and becomes infected.\r\n\r\nPlayers can rank-up from Recruit to General, though only 1 player can hold the top title. The game tracks your stats, such as players killed, deaths, and ratios, among others. Like most free-to-play models, the game offers an Item Mall with monthly deals and permanent services that players can pay for.\r\n\r\nWith a ranking system, Prides, numerous game modes, and an extensive armory, Wolf Team is a game worth looking into if MMOFPS games are up your alley and you occasionally have the urge to howl at the moon.','Shooter','Windows','Aeria Games','Softnyx','2009-07-09','XP / Vista / 7 / 8','Intel Pentium 4 1.4 GHz','1 GB','GeForce 5700 / Radeon 7600','3 GB'),(281,291,'theHunter','An MMO shooter where players can hunt 22 different animals in various locations.','Hunting simulation is brought to new depths with theHunter, a free to play realistic hunting game where players can hunt 22 different animals in various locations inspired by real world reserves.\r\n\r\ntheHunter pushes the boundaries of in-game depth, immersing players in the thrill of the hunt without actually killing live animals. There’s more to hunting than just finding and shooting an animal, and players in theHunter will be called upon to track, stalk, and even identify animals based on different calls and other evidence.\r\n\r\nSet in nine different preserves across the globe, this online shooter actually features 127 animals across 22 species, making variations and encounters nigh uncountable. The environments of theHunter make players feel as though their actually prowling through the dense underbrush, stalking a wild animal.\r\n\r\nPlayers don’t have to go it alone, either, as theHunter can support up to eight players in a hunting party.For gamers interested in hunting but don’t want to leave their homes, theHunter offers a unique FPS experience that cannot be matched.','Shooter','Windows','Expansive Worlds , Avalanche Studios','Expansive Worlds , Avalanche Studios','2009-03-05','Windows ® 10/8/7 ','Intel 2 GHz or AMD Dual Core','2 GB RAM','NVidia GeForce 8800, ATI/AMD Radeon HD 2400 (NVidia GeForce 8800, ATI/AMD Radeon HD 2400) ','3 GB available space '),(282,293,'Atlantica Online','A free-to-play 3D tactical massively multiplayer online role-playing game.','Atlantica Online is a free to play 3D MMORPG that has a good mix of tactical combat, player cooperation, and challenges outside of combat to appeal to anyone that likes tactic based games. Developed by NDOORS Corporation, The MMORPG is set in a fantasy-themed alternate history Earth. It has locations modeled off of real world locations from six of the seven continents as well as the forgotten continent of Atlantis.\r\n\r\nThe combat system is very tactical being a turn-based system with many different groups of mercenaries you can hire to fight alongside you during your PvE and PvP experience. As you level up your main character you are able to take on more areas in the game such as Raids, which are tactical dungeons that are an entirely different environment to the everyday quests you go on.\r\n\r\nAtlantica Online offers many different ways to group up with other players as well as many different incentives to doing so. Join or create a guild and take control of a town to get more money and gear for making your main character stronger. Once you have a guild group up with your nation and take on huge dungeons that require 30+ members to complete and offer crazy amounts of rewards.\r\n\r\nIf you are the type of player that doesn’t enjoy combat you are still able to progress your character by crafting and by taking advantage of the mentor system, a system where a new player becomes your apprentice and you teach them about the game and once they hit level 30 you get 200,000 gold.','MMORPG','Windows','VALOFE','NDOORS Corporation','2008-10-30','Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8','Pentium 4 1 GHz','1 GB','Any Graphics card with 128MB video ram and Shader 3.0 support','15 GB'),(283,295,'Florensia','A free to play fantasy MMORPG with legendary worlds ashore and at \r\nsea.','Florensia is a free to play fantasy MMORPG developed by NETTS. Journey out into the high seas and experience the beautiful environment while defeating monsters in the water and on land. Take on tons of quests and customize your ship and character as you gain experience in the game.\r\n\r\nStart off the game by choosing one of the multiple different classes the game offers, 12 playable classes: 4 Basic classes (Mercenary, Explorer, Noble and Saint). After you have chosen a class you get to build your ship that you will be sailing the open sea with. Choose from five different pre-built ships that you can choose to customize later on as you level up.\r\n\r\nAs you are exploring the ocean you will uncover secret locations and strange creatures that you can defeat to earn valuable treasures and experience. Keep an eye out for other players on the sea as you go, some may be friendly and help you find some of the secret areas, while others may be enemies and attempt to sink your ship and make off with your booty.\r\n\r\nFlorensia is a free to play fantasy MMORPG that you explore the ocean and islands in. Journey alone or find friends to complete quests with and find massive amounts of treasure and secrets to continuously level up your character and your ship.','MMORPG','Windows','Netts Corporation','Netts Corporation','2008-10-15','Windows 2000/XP','Pentium3 1.3GHz','512 MB','DirectX 9+','4GB'),(284,426,'AdventureQuest Worlds','A free-to-play 2D fantasy browser MMORPG. There are no downloads or software to install! ','The journey you’ll embark upon within AdventureQuest Worlds will never be dull. A free-to-play 2D browser MMORPG courtesy of Artix Entertainment, AdventureQuest Worlds will delight your eye with beautifully animated cut-scenes, combat that occurs in real-time, and new content that is released every Friday!\r\n\r\nCustomize your character to your heart’s desire and set off inside of the massive in-game world. It’s dangerous to go alone, so build your team with other players who can bring the skills that you may lack. But do not fear that you are limited to specific skills, for AdventureQuest Worlds allows its players to multi-class and learn all there is to know.\r\n\r\nThe story of AdventureQuest Worlds is ever-changing thanks to the constant release of new content. But your decisions within the game also affect the world around you, so choose wisely.\r\n\r\nAdventureQuest Worlds is easy to get involved with (requiring no downloads and no upgrading), exciting to play, but difficult to put down. The world within the game is constantly shifting, and you never know just what dreaded beast or heinous foe the next Friday will bring before your path.','MMORPG','Web Browser','Artix Entertainment','Artix Entertainment','2008-10-10',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(285,296,'S4 league','A free to play MMO Shooter with fluid gameplay and acrobatic moves!','S4 league is a free to play MMO third person Shooter created by Aeria Games and released on April 4th, 2011. If you ever played the popular GunZ: The Duel Game, S4 League based their gameplay off that title. Just like in GunZ, you can do amazing acrobatic moves like Jumping off walls and dashing large distances. The feel of S4 League and the fluid gameplay is what makes this game genre so addicting.\r\n\r\nIn S4 league, you partake in fast-paced Adrenaline filled gameplay, battling in a PVP setting against other players. You will defeat your foes using your choice of gun and sword combination, and also bringing a skill and passive stats with you, depending on what style of gameplay you want to utilize.\r\n\r\nS4 League offers over 40 weapons and has a unique renting system. You can rent an item for a select amount of time, which does not count the time in which you spend logged off the game. Your character can also equip three different items at any given time: A primary, and secondary gun-type weapon along with a sword. There are many different game modes to choose from including Touchdown, Chaser, and classics like Deathmatch and Battle Royal.\r\n\r\nS4 League has an anime style feel to it due to its animation and overall style. There is also an epic techno music soundtrack that adds to the fast style of gameplay. S4 League may be fun to play at its basic form, but it shines from how much tactical planning and skill that goes into this game genre.','Shooter','Windows','VALOFE Global','GameOn Studio','2008-09-22','XP / Vista / 7 / 8','Intel Celeron 1 GHz','512 MB for XP or 1 GB for Vista / 7 / 8','GeForce 4 MX series','3 GB'),(286,319,'Ace Online','A free to play fast action 3D sci-fi MMO where players control space fighters jets.','Ace Online (Air Rivals) is a 3D sci-fi MMO shooter developed by MasangSoft. It has great controls for a flight action game, tons of customizable options and a great PvP oriented system.\r\n\r\nYou are in control of your very own space ship, labeled as Gears in-game, that you pilot around on the planet Phillon attempted to become a masterful pilot for one of the two playable factions, Bygeniou City United or Arlington National Influence, in game. You are in entire control of the ship from customizing how it looks to upgrading the different parts that make it function.\r\n\r\nWhile you can fly around completing various missions and earning rewards and upgrades for your Gear the main focus is definitely on PvP. Fly around the various areas and come across huge space battles that feature up to 100 vs 100 Gears battling it out for control of the galaxy. The PvP is extremely thrilling as you have full control over everything about your Gear, the speed you are flying, the next maneuver you make, and what weapon you are firing next at that enemy you have been tailing.\r\n\r\nAce Online is a great fighter pilot game that puts you in complete control of your aircraft. It has tons of customizable options and a great PvP system that enables only the quickest maneuvering and best shooting players able to rise to the top.','Shooter','Windows','Suba Games','MasangSoft','2008-08-29','Windows 98 / ME / XP / Vista / 7 / 8','Pentium 3 1 GHz or better','512 MB','Any 32 MB DirectX compatible GPU','2 GB'),(287,300,'Rohan: Blood Feud','A free-to-play medieval MMORPG highly-focused on PVP.','Rohan: Blood Feud is a free to play medieval fantasy-themed 3D MMORPG developed by PlayWith Interactive. Rohan: Blood Feud allows the player to choose between the five races, and is then sent to do the normal MMORPG elements: Explore, fight, and perform quests. One of the major features in Rohan: Blood Feud is the “Vengeance” system. By utilizing this system, you can acquire “vengeance” upon characters that have killed you in the past. You can also kill other players and get rewards for doing so.\r\n\r\nBy joining a Guild in Rohan: Blood Feud, you can fight with your guild members for control over in-game areas. By gaining control of these areas, you can battle other guilds to maintain control and also create rules like taxes over that area.\r\n\r\nRohan: Blood Feud has other features like Crafting, which you can use materials from minerals, plants and other various natural items in Rohan in order to create new items. You can also forge two existing items for the chance to obtain rare items within the game. You can also obtain pets and mounts in Rohan: Blood Feud. If you do not take care of your pets in Rohan: Blood Feud, they can die, which is a unique feature normally not found in most MMORPG’s.','MMORPG','Windows','Playwith Interactive','Playwith Interactive','2008-05-28','Windows XP SP 3 Windows 7 ','Quad Core 2.5Ghz ','2GB ','GeForce GTS 250 Radeon HD 4850 ','12 GB'),(288,428,'Ikariam','A free to play browser-based city-building strategy game by GameForge.','Ikariam is a free-to-play browser based MMORTS with familiar gameplay, PvP multiplayer and civilian micromanagement\r\n\r\nIkariam features real-time progression, the game’s time flows whether you are online or offline, that offers a harrowing experience for many players as it can mean the difference between the success or loss of their city.\r\n\r\nSet within a chain of Greek-inspired islands, Ikariam challenges players to manage their resources while forging their own city-state. Luckily, Ikariam also offers in-depth tutorials for many facets of the game, making learning each feature easy and intuitive.\r\n\r\nContent is great, but Ikariam also shines through its colorful graphics and wonderful animations, making it stand out from other strategy MMOs in the current market.\r\n\r\nBut it isn’t just your own town you have to worry about in Ikariam. The island is populated with city-states belonging to other players, and it’s up to you whether or not you send the ambassadors to broker an alliance with them, or the army in order to plunder their own riches. However, the other players can do the same to you if you’re not careful.\r\n\r\nIkariam offers plenty of PvP scenarios that make the real time format engaging on a level rarely seen by other strategy MMOs.','Strategy','Web Browser','GameForge','GameForge','2008-03-31',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(289,303,'Saga','A free-to-play MMORTS that also features city-building and trading card games.','Courtesy of Silverlode Interactive, Saga is a free-to-play MMORTS that also features city-building and trading card games on top of the real-time strategy elements.\r\n\r\nSet in a world of medieval fantasy, players in Saga will lay the foundations of their civilization and watch as it grows from timid village to mighty kingdom. Players will also decide which side they will choose in an ongoing war between the forces of Light and Dark.\r\n\r\nBut there’s more to Saga than simple city-building. Players must not only gather resources, but they must also complete quests in order to gain new and specialized units and resources. With these at their disposal, players will not only build a mighty kingdom in Saga, but also a fierce army to protect it as well.\r\n\r\nThe combat system of Saga allows players to counter their enemy’s moves in real-time, setting up defensive formations in order to repel enemy attacks. Furthermore, the equipment of fallen foes can be taken in order to further customize one’s own army.\r\n\r\nAnd if players feel like they’re being overwhelmed in Saga, they can always call on a friend to come and aid them in battle.\r\n\r\nIf nothing else, Saga offers a unique mix of genres that will give players much to contemplate as they make their way through the game.','Strategy','Windows','Silverlode Interactive','Silverlode Interactive , Wasatch Games','2008-02-26','Windows XP ','1.6 GHz ','512 MB RAM ','128 MB, Shader model 2.0, OpenGL 1.4 ','1 GB available space'),(290,311,'Rumble Fighter','A free to play Fighting MMO, test your skills!','Rumble Fighter is a free to play Fighting MMO. Rumble Fighter was originally called Gem Fighter and was released solely in Korea, but was renamed when it was ported. If you are someone that can’t get enough of games like Smash Brothers, then Rumble Fighter is a title you should check out. Basing the gameplay off of that style of fighting games, Rumble Fighter has plenty of fighting styles called “Sacred Scolls”. During battles, you can utilize the “ExoCore” system, providing you with the option to transform during a battle, which will alter your battle style, along with your appearance.\r\n\r\nAlong with the PVP gameplay, there are also PVE modes to choose from, along with a variety of PVP modes like Arena, and King of the Hill. There are around 25 game maps in Rumble Fighter, and each present a new challenge due to its layout or other interactive features. Another key feature of Rumble Fighter is the ability to switch between Skill sets and equipment builds between battles. This allows you to test builds easily and also makes it so you can use the right build for every task. Rumble Fighter is simple in nature, but offers a lot of complexed, skill-based gameplay that will keep you engaged for countless hours if that is what you’re looking for. Test your skills in Rumble Fighter today!','Fighting','Windows','RedFox Games','Nimonix','2007-08-02','Windows XP','Pentium 4 2GHz (AMD and Celeron Series Included)','1 GB','125MB RAM with DirectX 3D support (Geforce3 Ti, ATI Radeon 9500)','1 GB available space'),(291,312,'Granado Espada Online','Adventure back to colonial times where you can find prestige, wealth, adventure, and a lot of work.','Granado Espada is a 3D fantasy MMORPG published by T3Fun. Adventure back to colonial times where you can find prestige, wealth, adventure, and a lot of work. Gain prestige by collecting unique family members and questing to make your family the most wealthy and well known family of them all. There are tons of unique and exciting characters to choose from and customize as you play throughout the game.\r\n\r\nAdventure out into the New World and start recruiting family members to help you out along your journey. You are able to choose from more than 150 unique characters to take along with you. With so many characters you are able to choose from you should be able to control more than one at a time, Granado Espada offers just that with a chance to control up to three different family members at the same time.\r\n\r\nAs you recruit more and more family members you are going to want to do quests to raise your family’s fame to be able to acquire more gear and take on higher level quests. Raise your fame by discovering new locations, hard work, and constant questing to never fall behind the other players. Use your family in Colony Wars to defeat other players in PvP settings to increase your fame even more.','MMORPG','Windows','T3Fun','IMC Games Co. Limited','2007-07-10','Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8',' Intel Pentium 4 3 GHz or AMD equivalent','2 GB','GeForce 6600 GT / ATI X1600 Pro 256 MB','10 GB'),(292,15,'Crossfire','A first person tactical shooter with a huge selection of game modes!','Crossfire is a first person tactical shooter that has a huge selection of game modes to try out, a decent amount of character customization, and loads of weapons for every situation you could find yourself in. Crossfire features two groups, Blacklist and Global Risk, that are constantly at odds with one another. Players must join an online team and participate in various game modes with their selected faction to destroy their enemies.\r\n\r\nNever fear about running out of game modes to try out, Crossfire boasts 19 different game modes that you can play through time and time again. Team Deathmatch, Destruction Mode, Elmination, Ghost Mode, Free for All, Mutation Mode, Escape Mode, Hero Mode, Zombie Apocalypse, Hero Mode X, Bounty Mode, Wave Mode, Shadow Mode, Ghosts vs. Mutants, Soccer mode, RPG Mode, Super Soldier TDM, Rapid Surge Mode, and Zombie Knight Mode.\r\n\r\nPlayers get to create their own unique characters that represent them in game. They can choose from tons of different cosmetic items that make their characters one of a kind. As players compete in Crossfire they level up and unlock more weapons and character customization options.','Shooter','Windows','Neowiz Games','SmileGate','2007-05-03','Windows Vista, And Windows 7','Pentium 4 - 1.5GHz','512mb','GeForce 5600','1.7GB'),(293,313,'Teeworlds','A free to play retro multiplayer online shooter where you can even design your own maps!','Teeworlds is a free to play retro multiplayer online shooter with side-scrolling combat like that of Smash Bros., and the ability to edit the maps for custom mods. It’s easy to see why Teeworlds is a popular MMO shooter. As an open source game, Teeworlds lets players shape and run the maps however they want.\r\n\r\nThe gameplay of Teeworlds is simple: collect buffs and weapons to go smash, destroy, and obliterate any enemies in the path to victory. From melee weapons to high-powered guns, there’s no shortage of fun weapons to use in Teeworlds.\r\n\r\nCombat in Teeworlds makes use of a fluid system that negates the need to mash buttons like other games. Additionally, the maps can be navigated quickly with strategic use of the double-jump ability and the grappling hook.\r\n\r\nBut it’s the map editing where Teeworlds really shines. Players can customize their own maps and make them as difficult or simple as they want. Players can torment one another with troll maps that feel more like a puzzle than a combat map.\r\n\r\nWith so much free will and editing available, Teeworlds makes for an interesting addition to sidescrolling shooters.','Shooter','Windows','Teeworlds Team ','Teeworlds Team ','2007-05-27','Microsoft® Windows® XP or newer ','1.4GHz or faster ','512 MB RAM ','?','10 MB available space'),(294,337,'Priston Tale','A free to play action-oriented fantasy MMORPG!','Priston Tale is a free to play fantasy MMORPG released in 2001 by Trglow Pictures. Welcome to the Continent of Priston, where its inhabitants settle in one of the two major towns. The reason for this is in between both towns, an absurd amount of monster live in that area, and only the bravest of souls would dare travel through it. You being one of those souls, will spend plenty of time slaying those monsters for items and to gain power by completed an array of quests, or just slaying them for personal amusement.\r\n\r\nThere are ten different character classes to choose from, including Pikeman, Shaman and mechanician. If you are looking for a simple MMORPG that focuses on the grinding aspect, then Priston Tale is right up your alley. Along with Skill based combat, which forces you to attack and use items by actively pushing the buttons, Priston tale provides engaging gameplay alongside the constant grind.\r\n\r\nIf you are looking for a change of pace, Priston Tale also offers unique game modes like Beliatra, Bless and Ghost Castle. With 14 years to hone the content provided to you, Priston Tale is a great MMORPG to sink your time into, and once you master the core gameplay, you can work on mastering your skills in PVP combat.','MMORPG','Windows','Suba Games','Trglow Pictures','2007-05-17','Windows 98/ME/2000/XP',' 600 MHz Pentium 3 or equivalent','256 MB','Any 32 MB card','1 GB available space'),(295,314,'Audition Online','A 3D rhythm MMO, Compete against other players in dance competitions.','Audition Online is a 3D rhythm MMO published by Redbana (T3Fun). Compete against other players in dance competitions by performing hip-hop and pop dance moves to a great recognizable library of songs. Live out your dream of becoming an amazing pop artist in Audition Online.\r\n\r\nCompete in competitions against other players and win by performing crazy button combinations to pull off the sickest hip-hop and pop dance moves the world has ever seen. Dance to some of the most recognizable hip-hop and pop music out there and strut your stuff to victory. Dance in various game modes, most of which require more than one person to dance with you, and compete in the regularly scheduled tournaments and competitions that the game offers.\r\n\r\nAudition Online offers a strong emphasis on the social aspect of the game. Most different dance game modes require two if not more people to dance with. Join, or create, a guild and meet new people to pull off crazy dance moves with. And with tons of character customizations you should have no trouble making your character unique and likable to the other players in Audition Online.\r\n\r\nAudition Online is a rhythm MMO that offers a great social experience and multiple game modes for you to choose from. Dance to recognizable hip-hop and pop songs and become a star in Audition Online.','Social','Windows','Redbana Corporation','T3 Entertainment','2007-04-02','Windows 2000 or later','Pentium 4 @ 1.4GHz+ ',' 512 MB RAM ','NVIDIA FX5200 128MB ','5 GB available space '),(296,16,'Roblox','A free to play sandbox MMO with lots of creation options.','Roblox is a free to play sandbox MMO. Imagine MineCraft with the option to take your creations, add story and other gameplay elements, turn it into a game and then post it for others to experience it. \r\n\r\nThere are even ways to earn money and create micro-transitions for other users to support your game-worlds if they enjoy them. That is Roblox for you in a nutshell. Since Roblox’s main appeal is the vast variety of games created by users, it will be near impossible to explain gameplay in Roblox, since it will be completely different depending on which world you are playing in. Along with the thousands of games you can play on Roblox, it also has a social platform to it. You can follow different content creators and even add users on your friend’s list and interact with them within the game.\r\n\r\nThere are many feature in place within the Roblox servers that are designed to keep children safe. All chat is moderated and parents can easily track their kid’s activity within the game. One of the major rules in Roblox is the no dating rule, which helps keep the focus on playing and building games instead of deep social interaction of questionable nature.The game development portion of Roblox is one of the strongest features it has to offer. \r\n\r\nWith nearly unlimited possibilities, and its own programming language that is designed for teens to understand and learn, Roblox is an amazing engine for game programmers to hone their craft, along with making a couple bucks!','MMO','Windows','Roblox Corporation','Roblox Corporation','2006-12-22','Vista, Windows 7 and Windows 8/8.1 ','A recent processor (2005+) with a clock speed of 1.6 Ghz or better','1 GB','DirectX 9 minimum and Shader Model 2.0. ','20 Mb'),(297,315,'Voyage Century Online','A massive open world ship vs. ship combat game where players will take charge of their own vessel.','Voyage Century Online is a massive open world ship vs. ship combat game where players will take charge of their own vessel and make their way on the high seas.\r\n\r\nPlayers will start by choosing one of five classes, ranging from Royal Military Officer to Caribbean Pirate. Voyage Century Online allows players to customize their appearance in game as well as their skills (with 17 different skill sets to choose from).\r\n\r\nThough players can engage in the open world PvP combat of Voyage Century Online, they can also take advantage of city-to-city trading in order to build their fortunes. Combined with the possibility of finding treasure in the massive open world, and players will quickly get a taste for adventure on the high seas in Voyage Century Online.\r\n\r\nPlayers can also make use of the auto battle system in Voyage Century Online, allowing them to level up even when they’re not playing.\r\n\r\nSet in the age of fighting sail in the 16th Century, with vast oceans and an entire world to explore and battle on, Voyage Century Online is an exciting title in the MMORPG style of games.','MMORPG','Windows','IGG','Snail Games','2006-12-22',' Windows XP or later','Pentium 3 500 MHz or better','512 MB','GeForce 2 MX400 Series','4 GB Free Space'),(298,351,'Grand Prix Racing Online','A free-to-play web-based motorsport management game.','Grand Prix Racing Online Is a free-to-play web-based motorsport management game. Build and control a racing team of your very own, starting with a basic car and working your way through the ranks by winning races. Hire drivers and support, prepare your vehicle for qualification, manage staff, negotiate with sponsors, and do everything else that would normally be done to assure success as a Formula 1 manager.\r\n\r\nGPRO features 17 races per season — two races per week. Players can spend as much time as they want managing their team, or they can just drop in for an hour a week. Of course, the more time put in, the better they will do.\r\n\r\nPlayers can watch races live while chatting with other managers. Talk strategy and plan ahead based on your performance and the weather.','Strategy','Web Browser','GPRO.net','GPRO.net','2006-08-01',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(299,429,'Astro Empires','A text-based sci-fi strategy and diplomacy MMO Game in a persistent universe.','Explore the farthest reaches of space in Cybertopia Studios’ Astro Empires, a free to play text-based space strategy MMO that gives you something you’ve always dreamed of: the chance to build your own galaxy-spanning empire among the stars.\r\n\r\nAs you start with your own planet in the farthest flung regions of unknown space in Astro Empires, you will learn to gather materials and develop new technologies to turn your previously unnoticed rock into a mighty empire befitting a galactic emperor.\r\n\r\nOnce you stand triumphantly in control of your world, Astro Empires unleashes you to wage war and trade among the cosmos, allowing you to build vast fleets of interstellar spacecraft that are ready to blast off and carry out your will.\r\n\r\nBut even an emperor needs allies, and it wouldn’t do to anger all of your nearby galactic neighbors. Astro Empires allows you to forge alliances with other players. Grow stronger together by combining fleets, trading resources, and defending one another from attacking hostiles.\r\n\r\nWith nearly two million players across the world, Astro Empires is by no means lacking in potential foes and allies alike. It requires no download and no cost. All you need is the internet and the will to take off into the stars can carve your empire among the planets and systems.','Strategy','Web Browser','Cybertopia','Cybertopia','2006-05-20',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(300,430,'Urban Rivals','A free to play browser based card-game with a high player base and comic-book inspired world!','Urban Rivals is a free to play browser based card-game MMO with a high player base and features a comic-book inspired world. Published by Boostr, the browser-based game calls for players to strategically build decks comprising peculiar characters, each with their own unique abilities. Use these characters to battle against fellow players and NPCs for in-game currency and additional cards.\r\n\r\nUrban Rivals features an immense pool of cards to choose from. The free-to-play game boats over 1,200 different cards and over 25 clans. Each clan offers special cards and unique abilities. The game offers multiple PvP and PvE playstyles including survival, tournament and mission. Enjoy comic-book inspired graphics and fast-paced games that usually take approximately five minutes. The game is available on the web, iOS and Android.','Card Game','Web Browser','Boostr ','Acute Mobile','2006-01-17',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(301,324,'Dream of Mirror Online','A free to play fantasy MMORPG with tons of social features.','Dream of Mirror Online is a free to play social MMORPG developed by Softstar Entertainment. The game is based on Chinese Mythology and players are able to socialize, form friendships, craft, and acquire jobs, all while trying to sole the riddles of the ancient myth of Kunlun Mirror.\r\n\r\nEnter the anime-styled fantasy world and choose one of the starting races: Human, Shura, Sylph, or Sprites each with their own unique customizations and abilities. After you have chosen your race you should pick a job class from the extensive list. You can pick from Commoner, Martial Artist, Wizard, Blademaster, Hunter, Thief, Doctor, Mercenary, Shaman, Fencer, Musician, Dancer, Merchant, and Witch Doctor.\r\n\r\nIf you don’t enjoy questing or would prefer a quieter activity take part in the crafting system that Dream of Mirror Online offers. You can select the mediation, mining, animal herding, farming, fishing, and forestry crafting skills and level them up to sell things on the economy or acquire them for yourself. You are also able to collect a wide variety of pets that you must raise and nurture to earn their loyalty.\r\n\r\nDream of Mirror Online is a free to play social MMORPG with tons of social aspects, a great selection of customizations, an enjoyable crafting system, and tons of pets to collect.','MMORPG','Windows','SubaGames','SoftStar','2005-09-03','Windows XP/Vista/2000/98','1000 Mhz Intel P3 or equivalent ','512 MB','GeForce2 MX/Radeon 7500 or equivalent 64mb VGA Card ','2 GB'),(302,431,'Imperia Online','A 2D free-to-play browser-based Medieval MMORTS, Train soldiers and raise an Empire.','Carve out your rightful place amongst the brutal warlords in Imperia Online, a 2D free-to-play browser-based MMORTS where you can take a once desolate spit of land and hammer it into an imposing empire that few but the most foolish would dare to attack.\r\n\r\nImperia Online makes use of traditional city-building and combines it with resource building as well as a realistic economic model. Everything takes place in real time so players must keep aware so that their growing empire is not swiftly trampled underfoot.\r\n\r\nThe customization options available within Imperia Online allow players to craft their kingdoms however they want them. The only limit is the player’s own ideas and resources. If a player can rein those in, then their reign as ruler of a mighty empire is all but assured.\r\n\r\nImperia Online also makes use of a comprehensive war model that mimics real life, offering a further immersive player experience. Players can also interact with one another in Imperia Online, ranging from simple alliances and trade agreements to full-on battles to claim one another’s kingdoms for their own, making this a game where socialization and communication are necessities.\r\n\r\nImperia Online will draw players in and keep them rooted to their seats in anticipation of what might happen to their rising empire next.','Strategy','Web Browser','Imperia Online Ltd.','Imperia Online Ltd.','2005-08-23',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(303,325,'MapleStory','A popular free-to-play 2D side-scrolling MMORPG with tons of quests, and a huge game world!','MapleStory is a popular free-to-play 2D MMORPG with cartoony graphics that was released in 2003 (in South Korea). Unlike most MMORPGs, MapleStory is a 2D side-scroller, however is very polished with hundreds of hours of gameplay and focus on combat and dungeon exploration. Players create characters by choosing between one of 32 playable classes: From Magicians and warriors to time travelers, there’s a class for every playstyle!\r\n\r\nAs with most free-to-play MMOs MapleStory features a cash shop where players can use real-world money to purchase avatars, pets, boosts and other in-game items. Most of these items have an expiration period, ensuring players will need to purchase more as they continue to play. It’s important to note that the game varies slightly depending on region, with some having less class options and slightly differing quests. The cash shop varies slightly as well.','MMORPG','Windows','Nexon','Wizet','2005-05-11','XP / Vista / 7 / 8',' Intel Pentium 4 or AMD Equivalent','2 GB','Any 128 MB Graphics Card','8 GB'),(304,327,'Everquest 2','A free to play 3D fantasy MMORPG and the sequel to EverQuest.','EverQuest 2 is a free to play 3D fantasy MMORPG from the same team at Daybreak Games, that brought you EverQuest, the popular MMORPG that started it all nearly two decades ago.\r\n\r\nEverQuest 2 features full support of different play styles from Solo, Groups, Raids and PVP. You will explore an enormous online world where you will come together with your friends and immerse yourself in the game’s exciting quests, intense PvP and PvE battles.\r\n\r\nWhen you play EverQuest 2, you will be playing through 90 levels. Choose from over 5,000 creatures to battle and more than 8,000 quests to complete, and hundreds of dangerous environments to explore! You will experience strong lore with game content spanning 7 years and 6 expansions.\r\n\r\nIn EverQuest, you will find a robust housing system, with dozens of styles, thousands of items, a House Rating System and an expansive in-­game marketplace containing potions, weapons, armor, classes, races, mounts and more! If you’re interested in buying special items and are willing to spend some real­ world cash, EverQuest even allows for optional content purchases in­-game; but don’t worry, it’s not at all required to play or enjoy the game to the fullest!\r\n\r\nYou will find a friendly community with thousands of guilds; if you’re having through finding somewhere to fit in, EverQuest 2’s Dungeon finder system helps you find and join groups!','MMORPG','Windows','Daybreak Games','Daybreak Games','2004-11-08','Windows 7','Intel Core 2 Duo E4400/AMD Athlon x2 4050e ','3 GB','Nvidia GeForce 8800/AMD Radeon HD 2600 XT ','17 GB'),(305,328,'Dofus','A 2D MMORPG with tons of different classes and a tactical combat system.','Dofus is a 2D MMORPG that has tons of different classes, a tactical combat system, and a profession system for those that just want to relax and make some gear. Dofus is set in “The World of Twelve”, named for the 12 gods that inhabit it. You will control 1 of 16 classes that each have unique sets of skills.\r\n\r\nThe 16 different classes represented in Dofus are: Ecaflip’s Coin, Enripsa’s Hands, Iop’s Heart, Cra’s Range, Feca’s Shield, Sacrier’s Blood, Sadida’s Shoe, Osamodas’ Whip, Enutrof’s Fingers, Sram’s Shadow, Xelor’s Sandglass, Pandawa’s Pint, The Rogue Ruse, Masqueraider Mystique, Foggernaut’s Steam, Eliotrope’s Portal, and Huppermage’s Rune. All of these classes have unique abilities that you can only learn if you pick that specific class.\r\n\r\nThe combat in Dofus is very tactical, while you can rush in it is more practical for you to think about it as a chess match and determine your moves on a turn by turn basis. You will gain experience and level up your characters by defeating monsters and completing quests. If the casual gameplay of the normal servers doesn’t do it for you, go to the Heroic Servers that the game offers where death is permanent but experience is multiplied.\r\n\r\nIf you would prefer to not join in on the combat, choose one of the non-combat related professions and go around collecting goods and crafting items for other players to use.','MMORPG','Windows','Ankama Games','Ankama Games','2004-09-01','Windows Vista/7','Celeron D 352 or Sempron 64 LE-1100','1 GB GB RAM','GeForce 7050 or Radeon HD 2350 Pro','4 GB Free Space'),(306,190,'Ryzom','An MMORPG where players are immersed in a massive sandbox world.','Mixing elements of science and fantasy Ryzom (also known as The Saga of Ryzom) is a 3D MMORPG where players are immersed in a massive sandbox world where they can focus in on one set of skills or choose to mix abilities together.\r\n\r\nInstead of classes, Ryzom makes use of four different schools: Magic, Combat, Harvesting, and Crafting. What abilities a player gets will depend on which school they chose and how much effort they put into training. Players will also have the ability to choose one of four races and personalize their character to suit their preferred aesthetics.\r\n\r\nThe world of Ryzom is open for players to shape however they want. The in-game world is massive, also featuring a day & night cycles as well as various weather conditions that can aid or hamper players in their quests.\r\n\r\nPlayers in Ryzom can also customize their skills however they want, focusing in on particular strengths and methods of play if they should so choose.\r\n\r\nRyzom is a game just waiting for players to make their mark on it, even if the weather inside may seem inhospitable.','MMORPG','Windows','Winch Gate','Nevrax','2004-09-19','XP / Vista / 7 / 8','Pentium 4 2.0GHz or Sempron 2200+','1 GB','GeForce 6100 or Radeon X1200 128mb',' 7 GB'),(307,329,'Kal Online','A Korean Fantasy MMORPG developed by Inixsoft.','Kalonline is a hardcore Korean Fantasy MMORPG developed by Inixsoft. Based on Korean mythology, the game is a standard MMO wherein players can choose between one of four character classes as their character. These classes are then leveled up via the slaying of monsters. Each class has 6 jobs (or government positions) that players can work their way through — each with their own skills. Unlike other MMOS, players are encouraged to change jobs several times in order to build the best skill set — rather than choosing one and sticking with it.\r\n\r\nIn addition to regular quests, Kalonline also features varying types of PvP, including: Castle Siege, tower defense, and more. Players can join guilds, which require six players to create.\r\n\r\nKalonline was originally released in 2004 and was made available via Steam July, 2016.','MMORPG','Windows','Inisxoft','Inisxoft','2004-06-11','Windows XP or above','Core2duo E6300 1.86GHz','1 GB','VGA 128 MB or above','2400 MB'),(308,330,'Lineage 2','A 3D fantasy MMORPG with a strong emphasis on PvP.','Lineage 2 is a 3D fantasy MMORPG with a strong emphasis on PvP allowing it to happen almost anywhere in the world. Join one of the three kingdoms with one of the thirty different classes and battle to put your kingdom on top. Published by NCSoft, Lineage 2 is a prequel to the original Lineage and is set 150 years prior to the events in Lineage. It is still centered around the PvP aspects that were present in the original Lineage.\r\n\r\nThe world spans over two continents that are ravaged by war and are in a constant struggle for power between three kingdoms. Choose from over 30 different classes that can be upgraded multiple times and customized to no end to attempt to win the war for your chosen kingdom. As you level up your class you can choose to specialize into a single class, take on a sub class, or even dual class by the end of the game.\r\n\r\nOpen world PvP allows you to choose to duel or player kill at nearly anytime. You see someone out questing killing monsters and seems unprepared for a random player ambush then you can choose to do just that and ambush them earning a bit of fame, or infamy if for the other faction, and having the satisfaction that you just bested another player.','MMORPG','Windows','NCSoft','NCSoft','2004-04-27','Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8','Intel Pentium 4 3.0 GHz / AMD Sempron 3600+','1 GB','Nvidia GeForce 6600 / ATI Radeon X 1050','20 GB'),(309,332,'Red Stone Online','A free to play 2D old school isometric MMORPG similar to Diablo.','Similar in many respects to the vaunted Diablo series, Red Stone Online is an example of classic top down isometric 2D fantasy MMORPGs. It may look out of date, but Red Stone Online still has much to offer to those who will give it a chance.\r\n\r\nPlayers in Red Stone Online are given access to over 21 playable classes along with a transformation system that gives them the opportunity to change classes whenever the mood strikes them. Combined with an extremely high level cap (over 1000), and it’s easy to see why Red Stone Online has kept running for so long.\r\n\r\nIn addition, Red Stone Online also features a rebirth system for high level players who wish to challenge themselves again. After Level 600, players have the choice of resetting back to Level 1. But this time, they’ll be equipped with bonus stats.\r\n\r\nAs for combat, Red Stone Online makes use of charge points, which can be collected while a battle is in progress and can be used to activate abilities.\r\n\r\nIt may not be the most innovative or best looking game in the MMORPG market, but Red Stone Online has made it clear that it isn’t leaving anytime soon.','MMORPG','Windows','L＆K CO., LTD','L＆K CO., LTD','2003-10-06','Windows 7, Windows XP, Windows Vista ','Pentium 3 600MHz ','1 GB RAM','compatible with Direct X 9.0 or above ','2 GB available space'),(310,432,'Habbo','One of the largest and most popular Social MMO.','Of all the social MMOs out there, Habbo is easily one of the largest and most popular. Set in the titular Habbo Hotel, teenagers the world over can connect with one another with customized avatars that speak towards their personalities.\r\n\r\nPlayers in Habbo are encouraged to personalize their in-game avatars however they want, from the design of their faces to the color of their hair and even the clothes they wear. Habbo wants players to feel like they’re expressing themselves.\r\n\r\nHabboalso features countless mini-games and quests that not only give players more customization options, but also unlock in-game pieces of furniture and other items that players can then use to customize their hotel room in the game. In-game pets complete the scene and help players mark themselves as individuals.\r\n\r\nWith over 300 million avatars representing people from more than 150 nations around the globe, Habbo has shown since 2001 that players will always have the company of others in the in-game world.','Social','Web Browser','Sulake Corporation','Sulake Corporation','2001-09-26',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(311,336,'Anarchy Online','A free to play Sci-Fi MMO that has withstood the test of time.','Anarchy Online is a Sci-Fi MMO developed by the Norwegian video game company Funcom. The game was released back in 2001 but has survived to this day making it one of the oldest surviving games in its’ genre, even if it does have a few bugs.\r\n\r\nWhen you being your adventure you start on the planet Rubi-Ka and you must choose which faction, Omni-Tek Corporation or The Clans, to back or you can just decide to stay Neutral.  You will be adventuring out into the Shadowlands to fight legendary monsters and defend the world against Alien Invasions, if you want.\r\n\r\nYou have tons of customization that you can do with your character. Give your character futuristic implants and crazy nanotechnology and after all of that then add the normal gear to your character. Instead of gear being equipped based on levels it is based on stats enabling you to create crazy amounts of combinations using nanotechnology, implants, gear and buffs to become extremely powerful.\r\n\r\nIf PvP is more your style join the fight for the planet by controlling the Tower Fields. Defend your faction’s territory, if you have a faction, and then wage war for your faction as well. You can even travel to the stars and fight aboard the Battle station, or attempt the PvP Dungeon.\r\n\r\nAnarchy Online is a game that has withstood the test of time and has a company that continues to support it and try new things. Customize your character for any situation either PvE or PvP and take the fight to the stars.','MMORPG','Windows','Funcom','Funcom','2001-06-27','Windows XP / Vista',' 2.0 GHz Pentium 4 or better','1 GB RAM','Videocard with 512 MB of VRAM','10 GB');
